\id JHN - Glavda
\toc3 JHN
\toc2 JHN
\toc1 JHN
\mt1 JHN
\c 1
\s1 Əlbǝg nalnǝg kǝ uuda
\p 
\v 1 Bamma zunngwura ndza mǝng nǝ ǝlbǝga, ǝlbǝgna ndza ǝmtaɗ dǝ Daadamazhigǝla, ǝlbǝgna Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 2 Iin wandza ǝmtaɗ dǝ Daadamazhigǝl bamma zǝnngwura.
\v 3 Baɗǝm nǝ dǝgitah ɓaggava ba tǝdvad iina. Maay nǝ dǝgitahi ɓagavnan kwal tǝdvad iin biya.
\v 4 Əlbǝgǝn iin gyigyiya shifǝga, shifǝgna iin wa vǝlgar parakrakǝr kǝ uudah baɗǝmma.
\v 5 Kwanǝn kǝ parakka ba parakrak ma gurtla, gurtlǝn tsǝgarva bi kǝ parak kǝ ɓa parakrakǝr biya.
\v 6 Ndza mǝng nǝ uuda nǝ iin ɗahav dǝ Yuhwana kwa ɓǝladi Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 7 Sahi sa taggar ǝlbǝg jiir kǝ uudah tǝghǝr kǝ parakna, aɗaba maraa fǝdghǝrǝt nǝ uudah baɗǝmma tǝdvad iina.
\v 8 Yuhwan bi nǝ parakǝn biya, sahi kwakyarvad tagtǝr kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ parakǝn kǝ uudaha.
\v 9 Tagatǝrdagag nǝ Yuhwan taakiya, Parak jiijiira da sii sa ma duniya da vǝltǝr kǝ parak kǝ uudah baɗǝma.
\p 
\v 10 Kwanǝn kǝ uuda iin parakka ndza bamma duniya, virɗyava tǝdvad iin nǝ duniya, bakǝvakwaha sǝraraaka bi nǝ-uudah biya.
\v 11 Sǝghǝv ba nǝ iin savak uudahaana, larwalǝg nǝ uudahaan kǝ dlǝghǝggaana.
\v 12 Aiciya, baɗǝm nǝ uudahi dlǝgharadlǝghǝg kǝ iina, dlaɓa ar fǝdghǝrǝt tǝ iina, vǝlatǝrvǝlǝg kǝ ndzǝɗɗa nǝg kǝ zarha Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 13 Naral bi kǝ zarha Daadamazhigǝl tǝdvad uuda dǝgshig biya, bi tǝdvad camarakǝv biya, bi tǝdvad dzamaghǝra uud biya, bamma yavva tǝdvad naaga Daadamazhigǝla.
\p 
\v 14 Kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga nalnǝg kǝ uuda, ndzaandzǝg mataatakamiyama. Nǝghamndanǝghǝg kǝ ndanngǝraana, Ndangǝra Zǝraan pal ba nǝ iin kwa sahi vak Daada, righarighan dǝ hɛrrǝr ǝmtaɗ dǝ jiira.
\v 15 Tagadatag nǝ Yuhwan kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ iin vak kǝ uudah bad halavuwa ndzǝɗaan taakiya, “Kwanǝn kǝ uud wa tagaan nai kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr taakiya, ‘Kwada sagau tǝhalara jakwaarajig dǝ ɗyakǝr ba vaivaiya, aɗaba lakuti kǝskaiya ba mǝng nǝ iina.’ ”
\v 16 Tǝdvad ɗyakǝra hɛrǝraan wa tlǝyamkǝna nǝmyam kǝ hɛrǝr tǝghǝr kǝ hɛrǝra.
\v 17 Vǝlada tǝdvad Muus nǝ Daadamazhigǝl kǝ adzahadzaha, dlaɓa vǝlada hɛrǝr ard jiir tǝdvad Yesu Kristi.
\v 18 Maay nǝ uudi tapghanitapǝg kǝ nǝghǝgga Daadamazhigǝl dǝ gyi biya, bamma Zǝriin palla, kwa ghǝravaan ndakwi Daadamazhigǝla. Kwa cǝhurga ǝmtaɗ dǝ Daadamazhigǝla iinwa marakiyamnda iina, dlaɓa kaa fǝkiyamafǝg kǝ sǝrgasǝrg kǝskǝmyam kǝ iina.
\s1 Tagadatag nǝ Yuhwan kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 19 Wan nǝ ǝlbǝgi tagada nǝ Yuhwan masarta kwa bǝlartǝrǝt nǝ maalah Yahudah kǝ zhiila kǝssa-uufah ard lii fa hyimi tǝ vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl kwa saral ma Wurshalima sa ndavgaru taakiya, “Agha war nǝngi?”
\v 20 Ɓalla bi nǝ Yuhwan kǝ agajau biya, tagadatag bat ɓalaɓal taakiya, “Kai bi nǝ Kristi biya”.
\v 21 Kaa ba ndavgarundavǝg kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Agha war nǝngi? Kǝgh nǝ Iliya?” Ngal ba ngutǝrangug kǝ iin taakiya, “Kai biya.” “Kǝgh tlayangǝn kǝm pakǝg nǝmndna?” “Kai bi, awarama.”
\v 22 Tǝhala kwaha, am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Agha war kaci nǝnngi? Tagkǝmndtag magha war nǝnnga aɗaba kǝm sǝra kǝ dǝgiti kǝmnda tagtǝr nǝmnd kǝ liiya ɓǝla kǝmnda. Agha ɗaag dǝ war kaci nǝnng kǝ ghǝraghi?”
\v 23 Ngwatǝrangwug nǝ Yuhwan tǝdvad ǝlbǝgaha tlayang Ishaya taakiya, “Kai nǝ ghai kwa ɓǝla tlǝhǝg ma tǝghala, ‘Ɓadlamarnaɓadlǝg kǝ ɗuulan kǝ Yaazhǝgǝla!’ ”
\v 24 Kyalma lii ɓǝlavtǝrǝtɓǝlgna ndzar Farisiyaha.
\v 25 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ iitǝr kǝ Yuhwan taakiya, “Akwama kǝgh bi nǝ Kǝristi biya, kǝgh bi nǝ Ili biya, dlaɓa kǝgh bi tsau nǝ Tlayangǝn biya, Kwar kǝ ndzǝɗ kaci wagha dǝ vakai nǝng agha ɓagtǝr tsuufǝg kǝ-uudahi?”
\v 26 Ngal ngutǝrangug Yuhwan taakiya, “Ən ɓagtǝr dǝ yu nai kǝ tsuufǝg kǝ uudaha, bandakwan bamma taatakaruwa mǝng nǝ daddakwam sǝrga bi nǝ uuram biya.
\v 27 Iin wa taggan nai taakiya da sagau tǝhalara, kwa tlanal bi nai kǝ pǝla zauwa kimmbakaan biya.”
\v 28 Baɗǝm wanahaan dzǝghaar ma Betani, kilga zaagha Yudan, vakavaki ɓagatǝr nǝ Yuhwan kǝ tsuufǝg kǝ uudaha.
\s1 Yesu iin Zǝr tuugha Daadamazhigǝla
\p 
\v 29 Dlakaduraana, kaa nǝghganǝghǝg Yuhwan kǝ Yesu da vakaan amaa, “Wayam, nǝ Zǝr tuugha Daadamazhigǝl kwada kǝsa haipa uudaha duniya
\v 30 Kwanǝn wa taggan nai kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr taakiya, ‘Mǝng wa da saggau tǝhalara kwa jakwarajig kǝskaiya, aɗaba mǝng nǝ iin lakwti yikwayig nǝ uuda.’
\v 31 Dzan sǝrgabi ghǝravar kǝ iin wur biya. Tsuufǝgǝn ɓagan nai dǝ yu na, ɓaggan mbakyarvad marǝvtǝrda nǝ iin kǝ uudaha yaa Israˈal bat ɓalaɓala.”
\v 32 Kaa tagdatag kǝ Yuhwan kǝ shiid tǝghǝr kǝ iin taakiya, “Nǝghananǝghǝg kǝ Shǝɗǝkw Daadamazhigǝl band garava kakur sii ma ghǝrazhigǝl, ngal tsǝgwatsǝgw tǝghǝr kǝ iina.
\v 33 Ndzan sǝrgai nai kǝ iin wur biya, bamma Daadamazhigǝli ɓǝllakut kai da ɓa tsuufǝg dǝ yu, iinwa taghwatag taakiya, ‘Uudi agha nǝghǝgga nǝng kǝ shǝɗǝkw sii sa tǝghǝr kǝ-iin dlaɓa ndzan tǝghǝr kǝ iina, iin dadda ɓa tsuufǝg dǝ Shǝɗǝkw Daadamazhigǝla.’
\v 34 Ba kai dǝ ghǝrara nǝghananǝghǝg kwana, ǝn tagkurtaga, kwanǝn kǝ uuda zǝra Daadamazhigǝla.”
\s1 Mbǝrzaha zǝnngwa Yesu
\p 
\v 35 Wurga kǝsaana, Yuhwan ghacǝgan vaaakwahiina ǝmtaɗ dǝ mbǝrzahaan buwa.
\v 36 Kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iin kǝ Yesu ghuda dagala, amaa, “Vazamvazǝga, wayam nǝ Zǝr mbaklaka Daadamazhigǝla!”
\v 37 Cinngara ba nǝ mbǝrzahaan buna kǝ Yuhwan taa ghaiya, kaa gata Yesu kǝ iitǝr dagala.
\v 38 Ɓǝlaa ba nǝ Yesu kǝ gyi dat hala, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iitǝr ar gatǝgaana, kaa ndavtǝrundaavǝg taakiya, “Awam gatǝg nǝ uurami?” Aiyam nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Rabbi” iin taaki dadda tsaga dǝgita, “Agha ndzǝga mǝri?”
\v 39 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Asamasǝga am da nǝghǝganǝghǝga.” Kaa dagal kǝ iitǝr ar vazzǝna kǝ vakavaki ndzǝga nǝ iina, ar cahwaran ǝmtaɗ dǝ-iin vaakwahiina. Kwan kǝ dǝgita dzǝghaar kalkala karfi uufaɗa hwasa.
\v 40 Pal nǝ Andrawus zǝra babba Siman Bitrus ma uudahaan buwǝn gatar Yesu tǝhala kwa cinngara nǝ iitǝr kǝ ǝlbǝga vak Yuhwan tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu.
\v 41 Dǝgiti ɓagaa nǝ Andrawus ba zǝnngwa fǝgharzh gata zǝra babbaan Siman, amaa taa kǝ iina, “Tlamndkǝnatlǝg kǝ Tlǝkatǝgna,” Iin nǝ Kristi.
\v 42 Sǝdǝv kǝ-iin kǝ Siman da vak Yesu. Kaa vazǝggaan nǝ Yesu kǝ Siman amaa taa kǝ-iina, “Kǝgh nǝ Siman zǝra Yuhwana? Da ɗahak dǝ Kefas nǝ-uuda.” (Dǝgiti tuuk vakai nǝ Kefas ard Bitrusa ba dǝgit palla, iin na akura).
\s1 Ɗahghantɗahǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ Filigus ard Nataniyal
\p 
\v 43 Dlakaduraana fadǝmfǝg nǝ Yesu ma ǝrviɗmahuɗaan dagal damma Galili. Kaa tlǝgaratlǝg kǝ iin kǝ Filigus taakiya, “Gatkwagatǝga.”
\v 44 Filigus uuda kǝsa Betsaid nǝ iina, vakavaki saral nǝ Andrawus ard Bitrusa.
\v 45 Tlǝghara ba nǝ Filigus kǝ Nataniyela, amaa taa kǝ iina, “Tlamndkǝnatlǝg kǝ uudanǝn kwa vinda nǝ Muus ma kakaɗa adzahadzah taakiya da saaya. Dlaɓa vindaravindǝg nǝ tlayangngah kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr band kwaha. Iin nǝ Yesu Uuda Nazarat, Zǝra Isuvu.”
\v 46 Kaa tagaan kǝ Nataniyel taakiya, “Nazarata? Sǝgalsǝg dǝgit maraw ma Nazarata?” Aiyam nǝ Filgus taa kǝ-iina, “Saw na vaznavazǝgga.”
\v 47 Nǝgha ba nǝ Yesu kǝ Nataniyel sagau sa vakaana, aiyama, “Wayam nǝ uuda jiijira yaa Israila, kwa maay nǝ fiid ma ghaiyan biya.”
\v 48 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg nǝ Nataniyel kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Sǝrghkwa ndari?” Ngal ngugara-nggug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Nǝghankak bamma sartǝn ndza agha miizhangyil kǝ uufa ghǝgyivvǝna, lakwti ɗahakɗahǝg kǝ Filigusa.”
\v 49 Am Nataniyel taa kǝ Yesu, “Dadda tsagga dǝgita, kǝgh Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla! Kǝgh nǝ Tlǝksa Israila!”
\v 50 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ Nataniyel taakiya, fǝghdǝghǝrǝt mbakyarvad tagankak taakiya nǝghankak miizha ghǝgyivva? Agha da nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ dǝgiti juujig kǝ kwaha.
\v 51 Kaa gwiya tagtǝrtag kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Ən tagkurtag kǝ jiira, am da nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ ghǝrazhigǝl wurawurana, Zarha ɓǝlga Daadamazhigǝla ar dagat ar saay tǝ Zǝra uuda.”
\c 2
\s1 Hwaɗaga kǝsuus ma Kana kwama Galili
\p 
\v 1 Daghuvala hǝnnga hǝkǝrɗa, ndza mǝnng nǝ hwaɗaga kǝsa uus ma Kana kwama Galili. Babba Yesu ndakwi ndza ba vaakwahiina.
\v 2 Baz Yesu ard mbǝrzahaan ndakwi ɗahavtǝrǝɗahǝg da vaka hwaɗaga kǝsa uusiina.
\v 3 Ghyǝnnga ba nǝ yuwa inabiya, kaa tagartag nǝ babbaan kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Maadlabi nǝ yuwa inabiyaatǝr biya.”
\p 
\v 4 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ babbaana, “Baaba, aujilbǝg agha taggǝwa kwan kǝskayi? Bagaa bi nǝ sartar ndan biya.”
\p 
\v 5 Am nǝ babba Yesu taa kǝ lii ɓa tlǝra, “Baɗǝm nǝ dǝgiti tagkur nǝ iina, ɓagamɓaga.”
\p 
\v 6 Vaakwahiina mǝnng nǝ ndǝghwah ǝngkwah kwa ndǝrava dǝ akura hulfa kwa ɗiyav nǝ yu mavakaiya, ar bara vǝghatǝr nǝ Yahudah dǝ yuwiin kwakyarvad dǝga daadijahaatǝra. Makwar kǝ ndǝghwa hǝɓa dǝfuu ǝnkwaha.
\p 
\v 7 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ lii ɓa tlǝrna, “Reghamantreghǝg kǝ ndǝghwahaana dǝ yuwa.” Kaa reghǝgantreghǝg kǝ iitǝr ba pɛkapɛkan.
\v 8 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Gahamgahǝg ci ndakwana, gamǝtgǝga damardadǝg kǝ zhiilghuu.” Kaa gǝtgǝg kǝ iitǝr ar dardana.
\v 9 Tapghana ba zhilghuu kǝ yuwǝn kwa gwiyavǝt damma yuwa inabi, sǝrghabi kǝ vakavaki tlavkǝna nǝ iin biya lii ɓa tlǝra ar sǝrgasǝrga. Ɗahant kǝ iin kǝ zhiila ghuul damma dlǝmmbaava.
\v 10 Amaa taa kǝ iina, “Abi, aanji ba war saggal dǝ yuwa inabi marawǝn ba zǝngwa, akwama tlatǝrtlǝg kǝ uudaha, kaa saggal kǝ uud dǝ dlǝmndalaana. Agha shǝɓna nǝng kǝ yuwa inabi marawǝn agha da sagal tǝhal nǝng dǝ vakaiya!”
\p 
\v 11 Kwan nǝ dǝga jappǝri ɓagaa nǝ Yesu ba zǝnngwa ma Kǝsa kana kwama haaya Galili. Marada ndkwan kǝ ndangǝrana, kaa fadghǝr kǝ mbǝrzahaan tǝ vakaiya.
\p 
\v 12 Tǝhala kwaha kaa di damma kǝssa Kafarnahum kǝ Yesu dǝ babbaana ard zarha babbaana ǝmtaɗ dǝ mbǝrzahaana. Ar gahha kǝ hǝnngah hǝɗiikǝn vaakwaha.
\s1 Lagwadalagw nǝ Yesu kǝ uudah ma gaagazaiya Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla
\p 
\v 13 Hǝrzǝt ba nǝ sarta haarakǝsa dzava hǝnnyaha Yahudaha, kaa dagat kǝ Yesu damma Wurshalima.
\v 14 Kaa daas kǝ-iin damma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla, tlǝtǝra kǝ uudah vǝlla tlaha, aagwaha, takalamasaraha. Dlaɓa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ kyalma uudah ar cihurgan tǝvǝgh kǝ tebǝrahaatǝr ar mbǝɗǝgar kwaɓ kǝ uudaha.
\v 15 Kaa ndǝrgandǝrǝg kǝ iin kǝ zauwa kiiɓa, lagwtǝrda dagal baɗǝm ma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla, baz tuughwaha baz tlaha. Tlagars kǝ teburaha lii mbǝɗa kwaɓa, kwaztǝrda kǝ kwaɓatǝr da tǝhaaya.
\v 16 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-lii vǝla takalamasarna, “Hutsamndahutsǝg kwanahaan dagal vaakwana! Lamdal bi kǝ vǝgya daadar kǝ kasukwa biya.”
\v 17 Dzǝghaar ba nǝ wanǝnna, kaa dzamnadzamǝg kǝ mbǝrzahaan kǝ dǝgiti vindava ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝl taakiya, “Waigǝn ǝn waig nai kǝ vǝgyaghna zǝkwazǝg tǝ ǝrviɗmahud band kaara”.
\v 18 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ tlǝvuukwaha Yahudah kǝ Yesu, taakiya, “Kwar kǝ dǝga jappǝr wagha da markǝmndada nǝng kwada mara taakiya agha dǝ ndzǝɗa ɓa kwanahaan kǝ dǝgitah baɗǝmmi?”
\v 19 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Dlagamnadlag kǝ Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝlna, ǝn ndǝrgaan nai bamma hǝngah hǝkǝrɗa.”
\v 20 Am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ Yesu, “Viig kul uufaɗ tar ǝnkwah kǝ uud ndǝra vǝgya Daadamazhigǝlna, aitsǝm ǝn ndǝrgandǝrǝg bamma hǝngngah hǝkǝrd amǝngnga?”
\v 21 Vǝgyǝn tag nǝ iin kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝrǝna, vǝghaana.
\v 22 Tǝhalakwa ciyavant nǝ Yesu ma gǝtlaha, kaa dzamnadzamǝg kǝ mbǝrzahaan kǝ dǝgiti tagga nǝ Yesu, kaa fadghǝr kǝ iitǝr tǝ ǝlbǝga Daadamazhigǝl vindavindana, ard ǝlbǝgahi taggada Yesu.
\s1 Sǝrgasǝrg Yesu kǝ dǝgiti ma ǝrviɗya uudaha
\p 
\v 23 Sarta kwandza ma Wurshalim nǝ Yesu mbakyarvad haarakǝssa dzava hǝnnyaha, uudaha baɗyaka fardǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ iin mbakyarvad garava dǝgaha jappǝri nǝghara nǝ iitǝr kwa ɓag nǝ-iina.
\v 24 Hayatǝrǝt bi nǝ Yesu dǝ iitǝr biya, aɗaba sǝrgasǝrg kǝ dǝgitahi ma ǝrviɗmahuɗa uudah baɗǝmma.
\v 25 Maay wa tagardatag kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ uuda dǝshig kǝ iin biya, aɗaba sǝrǝgasǝrǝg kǝ dǝgit ma ǝrivǝɗ uuda.
\c 3
\s1 Nikodimus ard Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Ndza mǝng nǝ zhiila Farisiyin ɗaagaan Nikodimus, pal ma tlǝvuukwa Yahudaha.
\v 2 Kwanǝn kǝ uuda sǝvsa vak Yesu kavǝɗɗa, amaa, “Dadda tsagga dǝgita, kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg taakiya agha dadda tsagga dǝgit kwa ɓǝladi nǝ Daadamazhigǝla, aɗaba maay wa ɓagnaɓag kǝ kwanahaan kǝ dǝgit biya bamma daddakwa ǝmtaɗ nǝ Daadamazhigǝl dǝvakaiya.”
\v 3 Kaa ngugarangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Bak jiira wan tagaktaga, maay wa dǝgaadǝg damma tlǝkǝssǝra Daadamazhigǝl biya, bamma gwiya yavayiga.”
\v 4 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg nǝ Nikodimus kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Da gwiya yaav ndar nǝ uud ma nalnǝg kǝ malahi? Gwiya daadamma huɗɗa babbaan da yiva kǝ dǝga bunii?”
\v 5 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Bak jiira, ǝn tagaktagga, maay wada dǝggaadǝg damma tlǝkǝssǝra Daadamazhǝggǝl biya, bamma gwiya yavayig tǝdvad yuwa ard shǝdkwa Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 6 Uuda dǝgshiga yaba uud nǝ-iin kalti, akwama yaayig nǝ shǝɗkwa Daadamazhigǝl kǝ uuda, kwah kǝ-uuda daba ǝmtaɗ dǝ shǝɗkwa.
\v 7 Aa nali kǝ dǝga jappǝr vakagh wanaa taggak nai taakiya, ‘Barari bamma gwiya yakurayig nǝ-uud biya.’
\v 8 Fǝɗa dagal da vavaki naag nǝ iina, agha cingaciing kǝ tlaavaana, bakǝvakwaha agha tagdai kǝ vakavaki aa sǝgga dǝ iin biya bi vavaki dagal nǝ-iin biya. Bandkwah dlaɓa agha tagdai kǝ ɗuuli yav nǝ uud tǝdvad shǝɗkwa Daadamazhigǝl biya.”
\p 
\v 9 Kaa ndavgaru ndavǝg nǝ Nikodimus kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Da dzǝggaar ndar wan kǝ dǝgitahi?”
\p 
\v 10 Ngal nguggarangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Kǝgh agha dadda tsagga dǝgit maamaala ma Israˈala, gwaastǝn nǝghaakai kǝ dǝgitahaan biya?
\v 11 Bak jiira ǝn tagaktagga, dǝgiti kǝm sǝrga nǝmnd wa kǝm tagkur nǝmnda, ard dǝ dǝgiti nǝghamnda nǝmnda, bakǝvakwaha lamwalǝg kǝ haigant dǝgiti tagamndkur nǝmnda.
\v 12 Tagankurtag kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ dǝgaha duniya, famdǝghǝrǝt biya, am da fǝdghǝrǝt ndar kaci akwama taggankurtag kǝ dǝggit tǝghǝr kǝ dǝgaha ghǝrazhǝggǝli?
\v 13 Maay wa tapghani dagat dama ghǝrazhǝggǝl biya ba Zǝra Uud pal wa sahi ma ghǝrazhǝggǝla.”
\v 14 Band kwa dzǝgghant nǝ Muus kǝ ghavala vǝrzhagan ma tǝghala, Zǝra-uud ndakwi barari dzǝgvanta.
\v 15 Baɗǝm dadda kwa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ-iina, tlǝkǝnatlǝg kǝ shifǝgga damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 16 “Waighantwaig Daadamazhigǝl kǝ duni ba vaivaiya vǝlda kǝ zǝraan pal ba nǝ iina, baɗǝm dadda kwa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ iina da maay ǝmtsǝg biya, da tlǝknatlǝg kǝ shifǝgga tangw damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 17 Ɓǝladi bi nǝ Daadamazhǝggǝl kǝ zǝraan damma duni kwakyarvad ghazǝna kǝ duni biya, ɓǝladi kwakyarvad tlǝkkǝna nǝ duni kǝ katǝg tǝdvad iina.
\v 18 Baɗǝm nǝ dadda kwa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla, maay da ghazav biya. Dlaɓa baɗǝm nǝ dadda kwa lawalǝg kǝ fadghǝr tǝ iina, ghazaghazana, aɗaba fadghǝrǝt bi nǝ-iin tǝ ɗaaga Zǝra Daadamazhigǝl pal ba nǝ-iinǝn biya.
\v 19 Kwakyarvad kwan wa tǝghara nǝ Daadamazhigǝl kǝ shari kǝ uudaha. Paraka sǝghawisǝg saama duniya, bakǝvakwaha uudaha ar waiya gurtl dlakulǝva paraka, aɗaba tlǝra kǝlaadǝr war ɓag nǝ-iitǝra.
\v 20 Baɗǝm nǝ dadda ɓa kǝlaadǝra naabi kǝ parakǝn biya, maay vaan sagau sa tǝvǝgh kǝ parakiin biya, haik kǝ marazha saggal kǝ tlǝrahaana.
\v 21 Dadda kwa ɓa dǝga jiira sagau savak kǝ parak, kiyava nǝghǝva-nǝghǝg bat ɓalaɓal taakiya dǝgiti ɓag nǝ-iina ɓag bad mǝlgarumǝlga Daadamazhigǝl.”
\s1 Əlbǝgi tagada nǝ Yuhwan tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 22 Tǝhala kwaha, kaa ba dagal kǝ Yesu ard mbǝrzahaan damma larda Yahudiya. Zǝlarmazǝlg ar ba ǝmtaɗ vaakwah ɓagtǝr tsuufǝg kǝ uudaha.
\v 23 Yuhwan dlaɓa ndza tsuufǝg ma Ainun hǝrǝz dǝ Salim aɗaba mǝng nǝ yu ba ɗyak vaakwaha. Uudaha ar sahasagawa sa vakaana kaa ɓagtǝrɓag kǝ iin kǝ tsuufǝga.
\v 24 Dzǝghaardzǝg nǝ wan lakuti ɓǝlav nǝ Yuhwan ma guda bǝrfina.
\v 25 Kaa ciigǝtciig ka gajau ma taataka mbǝrzaha Yuhwan ard zhiila Yahudaha tǝghǝr kǝ bara vǝgha lakwti kǝ ɓa kwatǝnahǝra.
\v 26 Kaa dagau kǝ mbǝrzahǝn da vak Yuhwan am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Dadda tsagga dǝgita, uudanǝn ndzam ǝmtaɗ nǝ uuram kilga zaagha Yudana, kwa ba kǝgh dǝ ghǝragh ndakwani vǝlghǝdavǝlǝg kǝ shiid tǝghǝr kǝ-iin taakiya iin Kǝristi, wai nǝ-iin ɓagar tsuufǝg kǝ uudaha, aanji ba war daggau da vakaana.”
\v 27 Kaa ngwanggug nǝ Yuhwana taakiya, “Maay wa tlǝknatlǝg aanji ndau biya, bamma vǝlgardi nǝ Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 28 Ghǝravaru ndakwani am shidahara aɗaba taganatag taakiya, ‘Kai bi nǝ Kǝristi biya, ɓǝlakutɓǝlǝg nǝ uud lakuti saay nǝ iina.’
\v 29 Daddakwa kǝsguu ghuula, iin nǝ zhiila ghuula. Tsaghwa zhiila ghuula paka ba taakiya maa cinnga kǝ kungya zhiila ghuula. Dlaig ba vaivai akwama cingngacing kǝ ghaiya zhiila ghuula. Mbakyarvad kwana reghǝt-reghǝg nǝ dlaigara aɗaba sahisǝg nǝ zhiila ghuula.”
\v 30 Mbakyarvad kwaha barari kǝ uudanǝn fǝgara ba ndangǝra, kai dlaɓ ǝn gulǝg dǝ gulǝga.
\s1 Uudi sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝla
\p 
\v 31 “Uudi sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝla juujig kǝ uudah baɗǝmma. Uudi sal ma duniya ba dǝga duniya, dlaɓa tag band uudi aasǝgal ma duni kǝ ǝlbǝga. Uudi sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝla juujig kǝ uudah baɗǝm.
\v 32 Taa dǝgitahi cinngha nǝ iin ard dǝgiti nǝgha nǝ iina, bakǝvakwaha maay wa haighanthaig dǝ ǝlbǝgaan biya.
\v 33 Baɗǝm daddakwa haighanthaig kǝ ǝlbǝgaana, haighanthaig taakiya dadda jiir nǝ Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 34 Aɗaba kwa ɓaladi nǝ Daadamazhigǝlna, ǝlbǝga Daadamazhigǝl wa tagga nǝ-iina, aɗaba vǝlgharvǝlǝg nǝ Daadamazhigǝl kǝ shǝɗkwaan kwa maay nǝ ghalaan biya.
\v 35 Waigaan nǝ Daad kǝ Zǝraana, vǝlgharvǝlǝg kǝ dǝgitah badǝm damma dǝvaana.
\v 36 Baɗǝm dadda kwa fadghǝrǝfǝg tǝ Zǝriina, dǝ shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra. Baɗǝm daddakwa naay kǝ zǝriin biya, tlǝkna bi kǝ shifǝg biya. Da ɗiigaan Daadamazhigǝl kǝ ǝrviɗmahudaan tǝ iina.
\c 4
\s1 Tagaatag nǝ Yesu kǝ ghai dǝ uusa yaa Samariya
\p 
\v 1 Sǝrghaakasǝrǝg nǝ Yesu taakiya cinngaracinng nǝ Farisiyah taakiya ɓagtǝr tsuufǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ-uudaha, dlaɓa tlǝkkǝnatlǝg kǝ mbǝrzah juujig dǝga Yuhwana.
\v 2 (Bakǝvakwaha, Yesu kataghǝraan bi wan ndza ɓagatǝr tsuufǝg kǝ uudah biya, ndza mbǝrzahaana.)
\v 3 Aɗabadkwaha, kaa ɗugarsɗuug nǝ Yesu kǝ haaya Yahudi, kaa gwiya damma haaya Galili kǝ-iina.
\p 
\v 4 Nalnǝg kǝ barari kǝ Yesu ta haaya Samariya.
\v 5 Kaa daas kǝ-iin damma kǝsiin ma Samariya kwa ɗahav dǝ Saikar. Kwanǝn kǝ kǝsa ba hǝrz dǝ guhǝn vǝlghar nǝ Yakub kǝ zǝraan Isuvu ba wura.
\v 6 Uuva Yakuba ndza vaakwaha, dlaba kuɗɗalkuɗǝg nǝ Yesu mbakyarvad dǝ dagala, cǝhura kǝ iin tǝ ghaiya uuviina. Kwanǝnna dzǝghaar dǝ vaci tǝghǝra.
\p 
\v 7 Kaa sagau kǝ uusiina, dǝghwa Samariyah sa ga yuwa. Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ uusiina, “Kwats yagh kǝ yuwa hǝɓǝga.”
\v 8 Makwahiin kǝ sarta, mbǝrzaha Yesu daral bawur da sǝgwa dǝgzǝg ma huɗa kǝsa.
\p 
\v 9 Aiyam nǝ uusa Samariyahǝn taa kǝ Yesu, “Kǝgha agha zhiil Yahuda, kai kwana ǝn uusa Samariyah agha ghallǝg ndar kaci kǝ yuwa hǝɓɓǝg vakari?” Aɗaba Yahudah ard Samariyaha ar nahakǝv biya.
\p 
\v 10 Ngugharangug nǝ Yesu amaa, “Akwamaghaa sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ gyagyaana na Daadamazhǝggǝla, ard daddakwa ghala yuwa hǝɓǝg vakaghǝna, maa ghalǝghaghallǝg kǝ iina, da vǝlakakvǝlǝg kǝ yu kwa da vǝlak shifǝga.”
\p 
\v 11 Aiyam nǝ uusǝn taa kǝ Yesu, “Dadda ndannga, tiidl ndakwi maay vakagh biya, uuvǝn ndakwi ba tlaɗɗa, agha da tlǝkkǝna mǝr kaci nǝng kǝ yuwǝn kwa vǝla shifǝg ni?
\v 12 Jighaarajig nǝng kǝ daadamnd Yakuba, kwa ɗuwakǝmndars uuviina? Ba iin dǝ ghǝraana, ard zarhaan, baz almanahaan hǝɓaruhǝɓɓǝg kǝ yu ma vakaiya?”
\p 
\v 13 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Baɗǝm dadda kwa hǝɓǝguu kwanǝn kǝ yuwa, gwiya tsǝgaan nǝ andǝla
\v 14 Aɗaba baɗǝm dadda kwa hǝɓǝguu yuwi ǝn da vǝlgar naiya, maadlai gwiya tsǝgaan nǝ andǝl ba dǝm biya. Yuwǝn ǝn da vǝlgar naina da ndzǝga bamma vǝghaan band njamar kwada za vukw dǝ kǝlga, nal kǝ shifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝr kǝ-iina.”
\p 
\v 15 Aiyam nǝ uusǝn taa kǝ iina, “Dadda ndannga, kwats kǝ yuwiina, haik gwiya njikwanjiig andǝl kǝskaiya, dlaɓa haik gwiya saggau kǝskai da gayu vaakwana.”
\p 
\v 16 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Dǝg ɗahantɗahǝg kǝ zhiilagh sa vaakwana.”
\p 
\v 17 Kaa ngwangug kǝ uusiin aiyama, “Maay nǝ zhiilar biya.”
\p Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Bak jiira agha maay dǝ zhiil biya,
\v 18 dǝgiti agha tagda nǝnngna ba jiira, aɗaba zaalah dlǝɓ wa kǝsghu nǝnnga, kwam ǝmtaɗ nǝ uuram ndakwana zhiilagha biya.”
\v 19 Aiyama taa kǝ Yesu, “Dadda ndannga, man tlǝg nai agha tlayannga.
\v 20 Daadijahamnd ɓagararnǝsɓag kǝ kwatnahǝr kǝ Daadamazhigǝl tǝ kwanǝn kǝ aghwna. Kuram Yahudaha am taakiya bamma ɓagvar ma Wurshalim kwatnahǝr kǝ Daadamazhigǝla awaram nǝ uurama.”
\v 21 Kaa ngwarangug nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Uusǝn, fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ dǝginǝn ǝn tagak naina, aɗaba da sagau nǝ sart kwada maadlai ɓagvar nǝ kwatnahǝr kǝ Daada tǝ kwanǝn kǝ aghwǝn aanji ma Wurshalim biya.
\v 22 Kuram uudaha Samariya am ɓagar kwatnahǝr kǝ dǝgiti am sǝrga bi nǝ-uuram biya, kǝmnd Yahudaha, kǝm ɓagar kǝ Daadamazhigǝli kǝm sǝrga nǝmnd kǝ kwatnahǝra, aɗaba katǝg sǝghal tǝdvad Yahudaha.
\v 23 Mǝng sart da sagauwa, bandakwan ndakwani ɓagaaɓaga, lii ɓa kwatnahǝra jiira arda ɓaggar kwatnahǝr kǝ Daad ma Shiɗǝkw Daadamazhigǝla ard jiira, aɗaba, hwulfaatǝr wa gatǝg nǝ Daad kǝ ɓagarnǝs kwatnahǝra.
\v 24 Daadamazhigǝl Shiɗǝkw nǝ-iina, lii ɓagar kwatnahǝr dlaɓa barari ar ɓagar ma Shiɗǝkwa ard jiira.”
\v 25 Am nǝ uusiin taa kǝ Yesuwa, “Ən sǝrgasǝsǝrg taaki da saay nǝ Tlǝkatǝg kwa ɗahav dǝ Kǝristi. Akwama da sahisǝga da tagkǝmndtag kǝ dǝgitah baɗǝmma.”
\v 26 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ uusǝna, “Kaiyin ǝn taaghai dǝ kǝghna, ba kai nǝ iina.”
\p 
\v 27 Bad ghyǝngaghyǝngaan kǝ taa ghaiya, kaa sǝgaasǝg kǝ mbǝrzahaan, kaa ɓa jappǝr kǝ-iitǝr aɗaba tlarara taaghai dǝ uusa. Maay wa ndavgharu kǝ uusiin taakiya, “Auwagha naag nǝng biya?” Bii kwa ndavgharu kǝ-iin taakiya, “Aujilbǝg kǝskǝgh taaghai dǝ uusǝn biya?”
\p 
\v 28 Tǝhala kwah kaa ɗuugarsɗuug nǝ uusǝn kǝ tǝfuwa yuwan vaakwaha, kaa daas kǝ iin damma huɗɗa kǝssa da tagtǝr kǝ uudah taakiya,
\v 29 “Sawam na vazamvazǝg kǝ uudi aa taguwa dǝgitahi ɓagana naiya baɗǝmma. Mbatak ɓagaɓag iin nǝ Kǝristina?”
\v 30 Kaa ba sahasagal kǝ uudah ma huɗɗa kǝss da vakavaki dǝ Yesuwa.
\v 31 Tǝghǝrdǝga ɓa kwan nǝ uuda, kaa ghalla Yesu kǝ mbǝrzahaan taakiya, “Dadda tsagadǝgita, zǝg kaffa.”
\v 32 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Mǝng nǝ dǝg zǝg vakar kwam sǝrgai nǝ uuram kǝ dǝgit tǝghǝr biya.”
\v 33 Kaa ndavǝg kǝ mbǝrzahaan ma taatakaatǝr taakiya, “Mǝng nǝ daddakwa sǝgardǝv dǝga zǝg nii?”
\v 34 Aiyam nǝ Yesu, “Kaffar iin taakiya ǝn ɓagna kǝ dǝgiti naag daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya, dlaɓa ǝn ghyǝngna kǝ tlǝraana.
\v 35 Abi am tagaan taakiya, tǝmma kyil uufaɗ lakuti kǝ saa dǝ dǝgwai? Wan tagkurtag ciya, vazamvazǝg kǝ dǝgwai tǝhaltǝhǝga, dlaɓa tlaral tlǝg kǝ ghudǝga.
\v 36 Dadda ghudǝgaana tlǝkǝnatlǝg kǝ dǝg shǝgaana, dzahgaan dlaɓ kǝ dǝgwai kiyava shifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝr, kiyava hwaɗag kǝ dadda riig ǝmtaɗ dǝ dadda ghudǝggaana.
\v 37 Kwakyarvad kwaha, bak jiir nǝ ǝlbǝg dǝghurǝn kwa taga taakiya, ‘Shah dadda kwan riiyaariiga, shah nǝ dadda ghudgaana.’
\v 38 Ɓǝlankurǝt da ghuda dǝgiti hǝɓamuubi nǝ uuram kǝ dlaɗa riigaan biya. Uudahi tlǝrǝn wa hǝɓaru dlaɗa, kuram wa za dlaiva dlaɗaatǝra.”
\v 39 Baɗyak nǝ uudaha yaa Samariya ma kwahiin kǝ kǝsa, fardǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Yesu mbakyarvad ǝlbǝgǝn kwa tagga nǝ uusǝn taakiya, “Taghwatag kǝ dǝgitahi ɓagana nai baɗǝmma.”
\v 40 Saral ba nǝ uudaha Samariyah da vak Yesu, kaa ghalgaan kǝ iitǝr maa ndzan vakaatǝra. Kaa ndzanganzǝg kǝ hǝng buwa.
\v 41 Uudah baɗyak fardghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Yesu mbakyarvad ǝlbǝgahaana.
\v 42 Tǝhala kwaha kaa tagartag kǝ uudaha Samari kǝ uusǝn taakiya, “Ndakwana famdǝghǝrǝtfǝga, aanji mbakyarvd dǝgiti taghǝda nǝngǝn biya, kǝmnd ndakwi cinngamndacinng bad hyǝmiyamnda, dlaɓa kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg ba pakat taakiya kwanǝn kǝ uuda, iin wada kata uudaha duniya.”
\s1 Mbǝghanimbǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ zǝra dadda kwa ɓagar tlǝr kǝ tlǝkǝsa
\p 
\v 43 Tǝhala hǝnng buwa, kaa ciya dagal damma haaya Galili kǝ Yesu.
\v 44 Aɗaba ndza tagadatag nǝ Yesu bad ghǝraan taakiya, “Tlayangnga maay dǝ ndang ma kǝssaan biya.”
\v 45 Dagha ba nǝ iin damma haaya Galili, kaa ba dlǝghga-dlǝghǝg kǝ lii ma Galili bad dǝva buwa aɗaba ghǝravaatǝr ndakwani daral da vakka hwaɗaga haara kǝssa dzava hǝnnyah ma Wurshalima, nǝghara nǝghǝg kǝ dǝgitahi ɓagaa nǝ Yesu baɗǝmma.
\p 
\v 46 Kaa gwiya daas kǝ Yesu damma Kana ma Galili, vakavaki gwighant nǝ iin kǝ yu damma yuwa inabi. Vakwahiina ndza mǝng nǝ uudaniina kwa ɓagar tlǝr kǝ tlǝkǝsa ma Kafarnahum yang bi nǝ zǝraan biya.
\v 47 Cinngha ba nǝ uudanǝn taakiya gwiya saghasǝg nǝ Yesu saama Yahudiya damma Galili, kaa dagau kǝ iin da vak Yesu da ghalgaan taakiya maa dagau maa mbǝna kǝ zǝraan kwa tǝ ghǝrdǝgga ǝmtsǝga.
\v 48 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Akwama nǝghamabi kǝ dǝga sǝrǝg ard tlǝraha jappǝr biya, am maay fadghǝr aanji hǝɗikǝn biya.”
\v 49 Am nǝ daddakwa ɓagar tlǝr kǝ tlǝkǝsǝn taa kǝ Yesu, “Asǝg naji dagal lakuti ǝmtsǝg kǝ zǝrraa.”
\v 50 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Dǝgaa, da mbǝg nǝ zǝriina.” Fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg nǝ uudanǝn dǝ dǝginǝn taghar nǝ Yesuna, kaa ba daasan kǝ-iina.
\v 51 Tǝghǝrdǝga daas nǝ iin da hǝnnyaha, kaa fadzaghǝr kǝ iin dǝ kyalǝma kwatnahaana, am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Mbaambǝg nǝ zǝriina.”
\v 52 Kaa ndavgaan kǝ iin kǝ kalkala sarti fǝgharzha nǝ iin kǝ ngulmǝga. Kaa tagartag kǝ iitǝr taaki, “Dahukwa kalkala karfi palla faciya wa ɗughars fǝɗiina.”
\v 53 Kaa nǝghǝgaakanǝghǝg kǝ dadda zǝriin taakiya ba kalkala kwahiin kǝ sart wa tagghar nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Da mbǝg nǝ zǝragha.” Ngal fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg nǝ ghwalvǝn ard yahaan baɗǝmma tǝ Yesu.
\v 54 Kwana iin nǝ tlǝra jappǝra buwa kwa ɓagaa nǝ Yesu tǝhala kwa ɗughars nǝ-iin kǝ Yahudi kǝ dagal damma Galili.
\c 5
\s1 Mbǝghǝnambǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ uud ghurɗika daghuvala ɗiya kuɗǝga
\p 
\v 1 Tǝhala kwaha, kaa dagat kǝ Yesu damma Wurshalima davaka hwaɗaga haarakǝsa Yahudaha.
\v 2 Ma Wurshalima, tǝvǝgh kǝ ghaiya guda tughwaha, mǝng nǝ dǝlva kwa ɗahav dǝ Betasda ma ghaiya Yahudaha, tsavarvaara dǝ tsakwamah dlǝɓa.
\v 3 Ma tsakwamahaan mǝng nǝ lii yang biya narǝtnǝg kǝ hǝnnga mavakaiya ndǝ gulfaha, ard ghurɗikaha ard lii ǝmtsaǝmtsan nǝ vǝgha. Ar paka uushvant nǝ yuwa,
\v 4 aɗaba kǝ sart kǝ sart sahasagau nǝ zǝr ɓǝlga Yaazhigǝl da uusha yuwiina. Baɗǝm nǝ dadda kwa dǝhi zǝngw damma yuwǝn tǝhala uushgaana, da mbǝg aanji tuuk kwar kǝ kuzahi njǝkǝnjiig baɗɗǝmma.
\p 
\v 5 Mǝng nǝ uuda nǝ iin ndza vaakwaha, viigaan kulhǝkǝrɗ tar tǝhǝs ba yang biya.
\v 6 Nǝgha ba nǝ Yesu hǝnngan vaakwahiina, nǝghaakanǝghǝg taaki zǝlamazǝmǝg tuuk kǝ kwanǝn kǝ kuza, aiyama taa kǝ iina, “Agha naagaan kǝ mbǝga?”
\v 7 Am nǝ dadda kuzzǝn taa kǝ iina, “Dadda ndannga, ǝn maay dǝ daddakwa da mǝlgwadmǝlǝg kǝ di damma dǝlvǝn ma sartǝn uushivant nǝ yuwǝn biya. Ma sartǝn ǝn ɓag nai kǝ kǝlla ndzǝɗar kǝ daay damma vakaiya, ba jǝkwaara nǝ uuda.”
\v 8 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Ciiga, kǝssant kǝssǝg kǝ kǝjagh, dǝg dagalagha.”
\v 9 Bat vakaitǝvakai, kaa mbǝgambǝg kǝ uudanǝn, kaa kǝsgantkǝsǝg kǝ iin kǝ kǝjaana kaa farzha kǝ dagala. Kwanǝn kǝ dǝgita dzǝghaar davala faciya ngiiga Yahudaha.
\v 10 Mbakyarvad kwaha am nǝ maalaha Yahudah taa kǝ daddakwa mbavnambǝgna, “Hinana faciya ngiiga kalkalbi kǝskǝgh ɓa tlǝr biya, haiyakant bi nǝ adzahadzah kǝsa kǝjagh biya.”
\p 
\v 11 Kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ uudanǝn taakiya, “Daddakwa mbǝkwii kai wa taggwa taaki kǝssǝg kǝ kǝjagha dǝgdagala.”
\p 
\v 12 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Kwar kǝ-uud wa tagak taaki kǝsǝg kǝ kǝjagh dǝgdagalni?”
\p 
\v 13 Uudanǝn mbavnanǝn sǝrgabi kǝ daddakwa mbǝghani-mbǝg biya, aɗaba mǝng nǝ uudah baɗǝyaka vaakwahiina, zǝgharaazǝg nǝ Yesu ma taataka uudaha.
\p 
\v 14 Tǝhala zǝlam hǝɗiikǝna, kaa tlǝgaratlǝg nǝ Yesu ma vǝgya Daada ma zhigǝla, amaa taa kǝ-iina, “Agha, yagh mbǝghambǝga. Gwiyarzharabi kǝ ɓa haip biya, aɗaba aa gwiya tlǝka bi nǝ dǝgiti ghwaɗ kwa juujig kwanǝn biya.”
\v 15 Kaa dagal kǝ uudanǝn tagtǝr kǝ maalaha Yahudah taakiya, “Yesu wa mbaghanimbǝga.”
\s1 Ndzǝɗa Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla
\p 
\v 16 Mbakyarvad ɓag daghuvala faciya ngiig nǝ Yesu kǝ kwanahaana, kaa fǝgarzhafǝg kǝ maalaha yaa Yahudah kǝ pǝcca ghaiyaana.
\v 17 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Daadar ba kǝlaa hǝng ɓa tlǝra, ghǝravar ndakwi ǝn ɓag band kwaha.”
\v 18 Kwakyarvad kwanǝn wa fatǝra kǝ maalaha yaa Yahudah kǝ zavukw dǝ gata ɗuula tsa Yesu. Am nǝ iitǝra, “Aɗuug yagh kǝ adzahadzaha ngiigǝn kǝlada nǝ iinǝn biyin ndakwani, ɗa Daadamazhigǝla dǝ daddaana, aɗabad kwaha gǝrra ghǝraan kalkal dǝ Daadamazhigǝla.”
\p 
\v 19 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Bak jiira wan tagkurtaga, maay nǝ dǝgiti ɓagnaɓag nǝ zǝriin dǝ ndzǝɗa ghǝraan biya, bamma dǝgiti nǝghǝga nǝ iin kǝ daddaan ɓagaan kalti. Aɗaba baɗǝm nǝ dǝgiti ɓag nǝ daadiin, iin wa ɓag nǝ zǝriina.
\v 20 Aɗaba waigaan nǝ daadiin kǝ zǝrana, dlaɓa marghardamarg kǝ dǝgitahi ɓag nǝ iin baɗǝmma. Dlaɓa, da margarmarg baz tlǝrahi juujiig kwanahaan kiyava ɓa jappǝr kǝskurama.
\v 21 Bandkwa ciig nǝ daad kǝ uudah ma gǝtlaha vǝltǝr kǝ shifǝga, band kwah dlaɓ nǝ zǝriin vǝlgarvǝlǝg kǝ shifǝg kǝ daddakwa waig nǝ iina.
\v 22 Daad dǝ ghǝraan maay tǝgar shari kǝ uud biya. Vǝlgharvǝlǝg kǝ ndzǝɗa ta shari baɗǝmma damma dǝva zǝraana.
\v 23 Kiyava fǝgaarafǝg kǝ uudah baɗǝm kǝ zǝriina, bandkwar fǝgaara nǝ iitǝr kǝ Daadiina. Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa fǝghaarabi kǝ Zǝriin biya, fǝghaarabi kǝ Daadi ɓǝladi iin biya.
\p 
\v 24 “Bak jiira, wan tagkurtaga, baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa cinnga ǝlbǝgara, fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg dlaɓ dǝ daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya, dǝ shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra. Maay da tǝvar shari biya, dzǝvaadzǝvǝg kǝ ǝmtsǝg damma shifǝgga.
\v 25 Bak jiir wan tagkurtaga, mǝng sart da sagauwa, bandakwan ndakwi ɓagaaɓaga, lii ǝmtsaharaǝmtsahǝg arda cinnngacinnng kǝ ghaiya Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla, lii cinngaracinnga arda tlǝkǝnatlǝg kǝ shifǝga.
\v 26 Bandkwa gyigyiya shifǝg nǝ Daadna nǝdal dlaɓ kǝ gyigyiya shifǝg kǝ zǝraana,
\v 27 Vǝlgharvǝlǝg dlaɓ kǝ ndzǝɗa ta shari aɗaba Zǝra Uud nǝ iina.
\v 28 Ɓagambi kǝ ajappǝra kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝg biya, aɗaba da sagau nǝ sarta, baɗǝm nǝ lii ma gǝtlaha ar da cinngacinng kǝ ghaiyaana,
\v 29 ar da sagal ma gǝtlaha. Lii ɓagaraɓag kǝ dǝgitah marawa ar da ciiga ar tlǝkǝna kǝ shifǝg damma zǝrazǝra. Lii ɓagara dǝgitahi ghwaɗa, da ghudǝvtǝrda nǝ shariya.
\v 30 Ən maay ɓa dǝgit tǝdvad ghǝrar biya, ǝn taa shari kǝ uudah bandkwa tagghwa nǝ Daadamazhigǝl taaki ɓaga. Mbakyarvad kwaha shariyara ba kalkala, aɗaba naaga ghǝrarbi wan ɓag nai biya, naaga daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\p 
\v 31 “Akwama kai wan taa ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ ghǝrara, ǝlbǝgara da haivant biya.
\v 32 Mǝng nǝ daddakwa taa dǝgit tǝghǝr kǝskaiya, ǝn sǝrgasǝrǝg dlaɓ taakiya dǝgiti tag nǝ iin ba jiira.
\v 33 Am ɓǝlant kǝ uudah davak Yuhwana, iin dlaɓa tagakurtag kǝ jiira.
\v 34 Bakǝvakwaha, ǝn maay nai fadghǝr dǝ shiida uuda dǝgshig biya. Ən tagkur mbakyarvad am tlǝkna kǝ katǝga.
\v 35 Yuhwana ndza kaara jahuramb kwa mbiig ba parakaraka, haiyamanthaig nǝ uuram kǝ cinnga ǝmtakǝra parakaan kǝ dǝga sart hǝɗiikǝna.
\v 36 Ən mǝng nai dǝ shiid kwa juujig kǝ dǝgiti tagaa Yuhwan tǝghǝr kǝskaiya. Tlǝrahi vǝlghwa nǝ Daadar mana mbasnana, iin wan ɓag naiya. Iitǝr shiidar taakiya Daada wa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\v 37 Dlaɓa Daadi ɓǝlakwadi kaiya ba iin dǝ ghǝraan shidara. Tapamnabi kǝ cinnga ghaiyaan biya, dlaɓa tapamnabi kǝ nǝghǝga ndzǝgana huɗvǝgaan biya.
\v 38 Əlbǝgaan dlaɓ ndzaabi ma ǝrviɗmahuɗaharu biya, aɗaba famdghǝrǝtbi tǝ dadda kwa ɓǝladi nǝ iin biya.
\v 39 Am hǝgaan kǝ shiga ǝlbǝgaha Daadamazhigǝl vindavindana, mam tlǝg nǝ uuram am da tlǝkkǝnatlǝg kǝ shifǝg damma zǝrazǝr ma iitǝra. Kwan kǝ ǝlbǝgaha iin shiid tǝghǝr kǝskaiya.
\v 40 Bakǝvakwaha lamwalǝg kǝ sa vakar am tlǝkkǝna kǝ shifǝga.
\p 
\v 41 “Maay nǝ lambar dǝ galga uudah biya.
\v 42 Ən sǝrkursǝrga, am maay nǝ uuram waiya Daadamazhigǝl ma ǝrviɗyaharu biya.
\v 43 Sanhi ma ɗaaga Daadara dlǝghamkwi biya, akwama sǝgǝv ma ɗaaga ghǝraan nǝ uudanna, am dlǝghgaan ba dǝ ǝrviɗmahuɗ pala.
\v 44 Am da fǝdghǝrǝt ndarndar kaci tǝ kaiyi am haigara ba dlǝbǝg mataatakaruwa. Am naay kǝ dlǝbgǝn kwa sagal vak Daadamazhigǝl kwa pal ba nǝ iinǝn biya?
\v 45 Tlatlam bi taaki ǝn da kǝla ghunnjaru vak Daad biya. Mǝng wada kǝla ghunnjaruwa, iin nǝ Muusa, kwam tlǝg nǝ uuram da mǝlkurumǝlga.
\v 46 Akwama famdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Muusa, maa famdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya, aɗaba vindavindǝg Muus tǝghǝr kǝskaiya.
\v 47 Haiyamant bi tsau kǝ dǝgiti vinda nǝ iin biya, am da haigant ndar kaci kǝ ǝlbǝgari?”
\c 6
\s1 Gǝlatǝrǝtgǝlǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ uudah alfu dlǝɓa
\p 
\v 1 Tǝhala kwanahaana, kaa dzǝva yuwa haiya Galili kǝ Yesu, kwa ɗahav dǝ Tibariya.
\v 2 Kaa gatǝgaan kǝ uudah baɗyaka, aɗaba ar nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ dǝgaha jappǝri ɓagtǝr nǝ-iin kǝ lii yang biya.
\v 3 Kaa dagat kǝ Yesu ard mbǝrzahaan damma aghwa ar cahwarana dǝ mbǝrzahaana.
\v 4 Hǝrzǝt ba nǝ sarta haarakǝssa dzava hǝnyaha yaa Yahuda.
\p 
\v 5 Dzǝghant ba nǝ Yesu kǝ ghǝra kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iin kǝ dzahava uudah sagau sa vakaana, kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ iin kǝ Filigusa, “Kiyam da sǝgwdaa mǝr kǝ bruudi kwada tlǝtǝrara kǝ uudahaani?”
\v 6 Ndava kiyava fǝsha Filigus nǝ Yesu, aɗaba sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ dǝgiti da ɓag nǝ iina.
\p 
\v 7 Ngugharangug nǝ Filigus taakiya, “Aanji bruudiya kwaɓa hǝngah tlǝra bariyam dǝrmǝk buwa, tlǝgǝti bi tǝ iitǝr aanji ba hǝɗikǝn hǝɗikǝn biya.”
\p 
\v 8 Aiyam pal ma mbǝrzahaan kwa ɗahav dǝ Andrawus, zǝra babba Siman Bitrus taa kǝ Yesu,
\v 9 “Mǝng nǝ zǝriin vaakwan dǝ ɗummba bruudi dlǝɓa kwa ɓagava dǝ ahupiya bale ard kilf buwa. Da tlǝtǝraara mǝr kaci kǝ uudah ɗyak ǝndkwani?”
\p 
\v 10 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ mbǝrzahaana, “Tagamtǝrtag kǝ uudah taaki aa cahwararacahwarga.” Mǝng nǝ kazhakwa ba ɗyak vaakwahiina. Kaa cahwargacahwarǝg kǝ uudaha, ghwalvahi ndzar vaakwaha ar mǝng damma alfu dlǝɓa.
\v 11 Kaa kǝsgantkǝsǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ ɗuumbaha bruudiina, tǝhala tagar uus kǝ Daadamazhigǝla, vǝlatǝrvǝlǝg kǝ digiti da tlǝtǝraaratlǝga. Ɓagaa band kwah dlaɓ dǝ kilfa.
\v 12 Tǝhalakwa zaru nǝ uudah dlaɓa tlatǝrtlǝga, amaa taa kǝ mbǝrzahaana, “Dzahamantdzahǝg kǝ ghwadgahaan kwa tǝmgatǝmgani aada badzalbi bagya biya.”
\v 13 Kaa dzahghantdzahǝg kǝ mbǝrzah kǝ tǝmga ghwadgahaa bruudi dlǝɓǝn kwa jatruu kǝ zǝga kwa ɓagava dǝ ahupiya bale, kaa righantrighǝg kǝ iitǝr kǝ alǝghw kǝlawa tar buwa.
\p 
\v 14 Nǝghara ba nǝ-uudah kǝ dǝga jappǝra sǝrgǝn ɓagaa nǝ Yesu na, aiyam nǝ iitǝra, “Ba pakat iin nǝ tlayangǝn kwa kiyam pakkǝg nǝmyam kǝ saayan sama duniya.”
\v 15 Nǝghaaka ba nǝ Yesu taaki ar na ɓa dabariya nǝdal kǝ tlǝkǝs bad ndzǝɗa, kaa ghǝlvalghǝlǝg kǝ iin ba daghuvaan damma aghwa.
\s1 Yesu da dagal tǝghǝra yuwa
\p 
\v 16 Ɓagaa ba nǝ hwaasa, kaa sii samma dǝlva kǝ mbǝrzaha Yesu.
\v 17 Ma kwahiina kǝ Sarta dǝmdǝg nǝ gurtla, Yesu dlaɓa sǝvbi sa vakaatǝr ndan biya. Kaa dǝgǝmdǝg kǝ mbǝrzah damma pɛra yuwa kiyava dzǝva dagal damma Kafarnahum.
\v 18 Kaa fǝgarzhafǝg kǝ fǝɗ ɓǝlǝg bad ndzǝɗa, kaa ghubǝɗǝg kǝ yuwa.
\v 19 Tǝhalakwa darant nǝ iitǝr kǝ dǝga mil hǝkǝrɗa bi uufaɗa, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iitǝr kǝ Yesu dagal tǝ yuwa sagau sa tǝvǝgh kǝ pɛra yuwiina, Kaa gǝdzǝgǝtgǝdzǝg kǝ iitǝra
\v 20 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Gǝdzam biya, ba kaiya.”
\v 21 Kaa haiganthaig kǝ iitǝr ar ɓǝlarna kǝ damma pɛrayuwa caaricaari kaa tsugwatsugw kǝ pɛrayuwǝn vakavaki ar dagal nǝ iitǝra.
\s1 Gatargatǝg nǝ uudah kǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 22 Cagaa ba nǝ kǝsa kaa nǝghǝgaakanǝghǝg nǝ kyalǝma uudahaanǝn ndzar faɗǝga tǝghaiya gardza dǝlva taakiya mbats ndza ba pal nǝ pɛrayu ndza vaakwaha, dlaɓa nǝgharaakanǝghǝg taakiya dagha bi nǝ Yesu damma pɛrayu ǝmtaɗ dǝ mbǝrzahaan biya, daral ba daghuvaatǝr nǝ mbǝzahaana.
\v 23 Ndza mǝng nǝ pɛrayuwah kwa saragha ma Tibariya ar ghacan hǝrǝz dǝ vakavaki zar nǝ uudah kǝ bruudi tǝhala kwa taghar nǝ Yesu kǝ uus kǝ Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 24 Nǝgharaaka ba nǝ uudah taakiya Yesu ard mbǝrzahaan ar maay vaakwah biya, ka dǝgǝmdǝg kǝ iitǝr damma pɛrayuwah kaa dagal kǝ iitǝr damma Kafarnahum da gata Yesu.
\s1 Yesu iin bruudi kwa vǝla shifǝga
\p 
\v 25 Tlararaa ba nǝ iitǝr tǝ ghyaba kwah kǝ ghaiya dǝlva, am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Dadda tsaga dǝgita, agha sǝgaa hǝr sa vaakwani?”
\v 26 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Bak jiira wan tagkurtaga, am gatǝkwa mbakyarvad dǝga sǝrgi ajappǝri nǝghama nǝ uuram biya, am gatǝkwa mbakyarvad zaamuzǝg kǝ bruudi tlakurtlǝga.
\v 27 Hǝɓam bi kǝ dlaɗ tǝghǝr kǝ gata kaf kwa badzǝg biya, hǝɓamhǝɓǝg kǝ dlaɗ tǝghǝr kǝ dǝgazǝg kwa zǝlmazǝlǝg tangw damma zǝrazǝra. Kwan kǝ dǝgazǝg wada vǝlkur nǝ Zǝra Uuda. Aɗaba Zǝra Uud wa vǝlghar nǝ Daad Daadamazhigǝl kǝ ndzǝɗa ɓa kwanahaana.”
\p 
\v 28 Kaa ndavgaru-ndavǝg nǝ uudah kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Auwa kǝmnda ɓag nǝmd kiyava ɓa tlǝrahi naag nǝ Daadamazhigǝli?”
\p 
\v 29 Kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Wan nǝ tlǝri naag nǝ Daadamazhigǝla, famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ daddakwa ɓǝladi nǝ-iina.”
\p 
\v 30 Kaa ndavgaru-ndavǝg nǝ uudahiin kǝ Yesu am nǝ-iitǝra, “Kwarci kǝ garava dǝgasǝrg wagha da ɓag nǝng kiyava fadghǝr kǝskǝmnd tǝ kǝghi? Au wagha da ɓag nǝngi?
\v 31 Daadijahamiyam zaruuzǝg kǝ manna ma tǝghala, band kwa vinndava ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝl taakiya, ‘Vǝlatǝrvǝlǝg kǝ dǝgazǝg siima ghǝra zhigǝl kiyava zǝgga.’ ”
\p 
\v 32 Tǝhala kwaha, kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Bak jiir wan tagkurtaga, Muus bi wa vǝlakurdi bruudi sii ma ghǝrazhigǝl biya, Daadar wa vǝlakurdi bruudiya jiir sii ma ghǝrazhigǝla.
\v 33 Aɗaba bruudiya Daadamazhigǝl iin bruudi kwa saay ma ghǝrazhigǝla vǝlgar shifǝg kǝ duniya.”
\v 34 Kaa am nǝ-iitǝr taa kǝ-iina, “Dadda ndangnga, ndzaa ba vǝlkǝmnd-vǝlǝg kǝ bruudiyin bakǝlaa hǝngnga.”
\v 35 Kaa ngutǝraangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Kai nǝ bruudiya shifǝga, dadda kwa sǝgǝv sa vakar maadlai wai da njǝkǝn-njiig biya. Dadda kwa fadghǝr tǝ kaiya maadlai nǝ andǝl da njǝkǝn-njiig biya.
\v 36 Bandkwa tagankur naiya, nǝghamkwanǝghǝga, bakǝvakwaha am lǝwa kǝ fadghǝr tǝ kaiya.
\v 37 Baɗǝm lii vǝlgwa nǝ daada, ar da sagau sa vakara, daddakwa sǝgǝv sa vakara dlaɓa, ǝn maay lagwan biya.
\v 38 Sanhi sa ɓa dǝgiti naag ghǝrar bi nai mazhigǝl biya, sanhi mbakyarva ɓa dǝgiti naag daddkwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\v 39 Naaga daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kai iin takiya, aa zannai aanji pal mali vǝlghwa nǝ-iin biya, ǝn ciitǝrǝt davala ghyǝngnga duniya.
\v 40 Aɗaba kwan nǝ naaga Daadar taakiya, baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa vazza dat Zǝrna, dlaɓa fadghǝr tǝ iina, da tlǝkkǝnatlǝg kǝ shifǝga damma zǝrarǝra, kai dlaɓa ǝn da ciigaan davala ghyǝngnga duniya.”
\p 
\v 41 Kaa zavaghai kǝ Yahudah tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu aɗaba tagada taakiya, “Kai nǝ bruudiyin sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝlna.”
\v 42 Am nǝ-iitǝra, “Abi Yesu, zǝra Isuvu, bakwa kǝm sǝrga nǝmnd kǝ daddaana ard babbaanǝn ɗang? Tag ndar kaci taaki, ‘Sanhi ma ghǝrazhigǝli?”
\p 
\v 43 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iintǝra, “Ɗuwamarsɗuug kǝ zavaghai ma taatatakaruwa.
\v 44 Maay wa dzǝgwantdzǝgw sa vakar biya, bamma sǝdda nǝ Daad kwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya, ǝn da ciyant nai kǝ uudanǝn davala ghyǝgnga duniya.
\v 45 Vinndava-vinndǝg ma kakkaɗa tlaiyangngah taakiya, ‘Baɗǝmaatǝr da tsagtǝr ba nǝ Daadamazhigǝla.’ Baɗǝm daddakwa cingngharnu-cingng kǝ Daadiina dlaɓa tsagaan vakaana, da sagau sa vakara.
\v 46 Maay wa ɗǝyit gi tǝ Daad biya bamma daddakwa sahi vak Daadamazhigǝla, ba iin pal wa nǝghgha Daadiina.
\v 47 Bak jiir wan tagkurtagga, baɗǝm daddakwa fadghǝrǝt-fǝga, mǝng dǝ shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 48 Kai nǝ bruudiya shifǝga.
\v 49 Dadijaha dadijaharu zaruzǝg kǝ mana ma tǝghal, bakǝvakwaha ruwararuuga.
\v 50 Wan nǝ bruudi kwa sii ma zhigǝla, baɗǝm dadda kwa zǝguu bruudina, maay ǝmtsǝg biya.
\v 51 Kai nǝ bruudiya shifǝg kwa sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝla. Baɗǝm dadda kwa zǝguu bruudina, tlǝknatlǝg kǝ shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra. Kwan kǝ bruudiya vǝghara, kwan da vǝlda nai kiyava tlǝkkǝna shifǝg kǝ uudaha duniya.”
\p 
\v 52 Kaa fǝgarzhafǝg kǝ Yahudah kǝ ɓala agajau ma taatakaatǝr ba dladlaɗa, taakiya, “Vǝlkiyam ndar nǝ uudanǝn kǝ tluwa vǝghaan kiyava zǝggi?”
\p 
\v 53 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitera, “Bak jiijiira ǝn tagkurtaga bamma zamuzǝg kǝ tluw Zǝra Uuda, dlaɓa am hǝɓɓu kǝ avǝzaana, am maay dǝ shifǝg ma kuram biya.
\v 54 Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa zǝguu tluwa vǝghara, hǝɓɓu dlaɓ kǝ avǝzara, mǝng dǝ shifǝgga damma zǝrazǝra, ǝnda ciigaan davala ghyǝngnga duniya.
\v 55 Aɗaba tluwa vǝghara iin nǝ dǝgazǝga jiirjiira. Avǝzar ndakwi iin nǝ dǝga hǝɓɓǝga jiirjiira.
\v 56 Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa za tluwa vǝghara, dlaɓa hǝɓɓǝgaan kǝ avǝzara, ndzǝga ma kaiya, kai dlaɓ ma vǝghaana.
\v 57 Bandkwan ndzǝgan nai mbakyarvad Daada dadda shifǝg kwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya, bandkwah dlaɓ nǝ daddakwa zǝg tǝ kaiya, da ndzǝga mbakyarvad kaiya.
\v 58 Kai nǝ bruudiyin sahi ma ghǝrazhigǝlna. Daadijaha daadijaharu zaruzǝg kǝ mana, bakǝvakwaha ruwararuuga, baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa zǝguu kwanǝn kǝ bruudiya da ndzǝga bad shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra.”
\v 59 Tagada ma Kafarnahum nǝ Yesu kwan kǝ ǝlbǝg ma sarta kwandza tsaga dǝgit ma guda dzǝgwazhigǝl Yahudaha.
\s1 Əlbǝgaha Yesu sa dǝ shifǝga damma zǝrazǝra
\p 
\v 60 Cinngara ba nǝ-iitǝr ndǝkwana, kaa ba taggaan kǝ kyalǝma mbǝrzahaan taakiya, “Kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga mblemlen kǝ nǝghǝgaakanǝhǝga, warwa haiganthaigi?”
\v 61 Nǝghǝghaaka ba nǝ Yesu taakiya zavaghai nǝ mbǝrzahaan tǝghǝr kǝ ǝlbǝgna, kaa amaa taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Badzakurda-badzǝg kǝ ǝrviɗy nǝ wanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga?
\v 62 Da ndzǝga ndar kaci nǝ ǝrivǝɗmahuɗaru akwama nǝghamanǝghǝg kǝ Zǝra uuda dagat da vakavaki sahi nǝ-iini?
\v 63 Shiɗǝkw iin wa vǝla shifǝga. Maay nǝ vǝgh dǝ ndzǝɗa ɓa aanji ndau biya. Əlbǝgahaan tagankur naina sǝghal vak Shiɗǝkwa dlaɓa vǝla shifǝga.
\v 64 Mǝng nǝ kyalmaruwi fardghǝrǝt biya.” Bamma facta sǝrgasǝrg nǝ Yesu kǝ lii fardghǝrǝt bi tǝ-iin biya, sǝrghasǝrǝg dlaɓ kǝ daddakwa da vǝlgaana.
\v 65 Kaa gwiya tagaan kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Iin wa tagankur naiya, ‘Maay wa dzǝgwantdzǝgw sa vakar biya, bamma vǝlgharvǝlǝg nǝ Daad kǝ ndzǝɗa.’ ”
\p 
\v 66 Tǝhala ǝlbǝgahaan taga Yesu na, kaa gwiya dat hal kǝ mbǝrzahaan ba ɗyak ar ɗuwars dlaɓa ar lǝwa kǝ gwaiyav ǝmtaɗ dǝ-iina.
\v 67 Kaa ndavtǝrundavǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ kǝlawa tar buna taakiya, “Baz kuram ndakwani amnaa dagalaruwa?”
\v 68 Kaa ngwangug nǝ Siman Bitrus taakiya, “Yaazhigǝla, kǝmnda vak wari? Kǝgh wagha taa ǝlbǝga vǝla shifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 69 Famdghǝrǝtfǝg nǝmnd dlaɓa kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg taakiya, kǝgh Caccuwanacaccuwananǝn kwa sahi vak Daadamazhigǝla.”
\v 70 Kaa ngngwagug nǝ Yesu amaa, “Dzǝrankuraakadzǝrga baɗǝmaru kǝlawa tar buna, bakǝvakwaha pal ma kuram shatanaha uuda.”
\v 71 Tag tǝghǝr kǝ Yahuda, zǝra Siman Iskariyoti, aɗaba iin wada vǝla Yesu, bakǝvakwaha pal nǝ-iin ma lii kǝlawa tar buna.
\c 7
\s1 Fardghǝrǝt bi nǝ zaraabaha Yesu tǝ iin biya
\p 
\v 1 Tǝhalakwaha kaa gwaivagwaig kǝ Yesu ma haaya Galili, naha bi kǝ damma haaya Yahud biya, aɗaba ar gata ɗuula tsǝgaan nǝ maalaha Yahudah vaakwaha.
\v 2 Hǝrzǝt ba nǝ sarta haarakǝssa taha babramaha yaa Yahuda,
\v 3 kaa tagartag kǝ zaraabahaan kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Marawuraana magha dagal damma Yahudiya, kiyava nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ mbǝrzahaghi vaakwah kǝ dǝgaha jappǝri agha ɓag nǝnga.
\v 4 Abi lii naa sǝrvtǝr ar maay shǝɓa dǝgiti ar ɓag nǝ-iitǝr biya. Nalnǝg tsau taaki agha ɓagaan kǝ kwanahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, agha margaan kǝ ghǝragh kiyava sǝraksǝrg kǝ duniya.”
\v 5 Aɗaba aanji zarha babbaan kǝ Yesu ndakwi fardghǝrit bi tǝ iin biya.
\p 
\v 6 Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Ɓagaa bi sartar ndan biya, vakaruwa aanji kwar kǝ sarta, ba kalkala.
\v 7 Da ɗuukurǝs bi nǝ duni kǝskuram biya, kai wa ɗuukus nǝ iina. Aɗaba ǝn tagar tlǝraha kǝladǝri ɓag nǝ iina.
\v 8 Damdǝg nǝ uuram dagal da vaka haarakǝssiina, ǝn maay nai dagal biya, aɗaba ɓagaa bi nǝ sartar ndan biya.”
\v 9 Tǝhalakwa tagatǝrda nǝ Yesu kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa ndzǝgandzǝg kǝ iin ndan ma Galili.
\s1 Dal nǝ Yesu da vaka haarakǝssa
\p 
\v 10 Daral ba nǝ zarha babba Yesu da vaka hwaɗaga haara kǝsna, kaa ba dagal kǝ Yesu tǝhalaatǝr kwal sǝrgasǝrgaatǝra, kwal nǝghǝga kǝ uudaha.
\v 11 Kaa gatǝgaan kǝ maalaha Yahudah vaka haara kǝssǝna, ar ndava taaki, “Mǝr nǝ uuda nǝ iini?”
\p 
\v 12 Kaa ba ɗung kǝ uudah mataatakaatǝr vaka dzahavǝn tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu. Kyalǝm ar taakiya, “Uuda jiijiir nǝ iina.” Kyalǝm dlaɓ ar taakiya, “Maaya, abi vala ba uudaha.”
\v 13 Maay wa shughana gyi kǝ taaghai tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu tǝ ɓalaɓal biya, aɗaba ar gǝdza maalaha Yahudaha.
\s1 Yesu tsagtǝr dǝgit kǝ uudah vaka haara kǝssa
\p 
\v 14 Davǝm ba damma ghadghada haara kǝsna, Kaa daas kǝ Yesu damma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl kaa farzha kǝ tsagtǝr dǝgit kǝ uudaha.
\v 15 Kaa ɓa jappǝr kǝ Yahudahi ndzar vaakwah ar ndava taakiya, “Tsaguu ndar nǝ uudanǝn kǝ dǝgit ǝndkwan bakwal dǝgal damma makaranti?”
\p 
\v 16 Kaa ngwangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Dǝginahaan ǝn tsag naina, dǝgar biya dǝga daddakwa ɓǝlakwaadi kaiya.
\v 17 Baɗǝm daddakwa kǝsghaakakǝsǝg kǝ ɓa dǝgiti naag Daadamazhigǝla, da nǝghǝgaakanǝghǝg taakiya tsagaanara sǝghawi vak Daadamazhigǝla, vakar biya.
\v 18 Daddakwa tsaga dǝga ghǝraana, tsag mbakyarvad faara kǝ ghǝraana. Daddakwa naa fǝgaara kǝ daddakwa ɓǝladi iina, taa ba jiira, maay nǝ fiid ma ghaiyan biya.
\v 19 Abi Muus wa vǝlakur adzahadzah? Bakǝvakwaha maay ma kuram wa tsuufǝghant adzahadzahiin biya. Aujilbǝg ci kǝskuram am naa tsakayi?”
\p 
\v 20 Kaa ngwangug kǝ uudah taakiya, “Mǝng nǝ shatanah ma vǝghagha. Yaar dlaɓ wanaa tsakǝghi?”
\p 
\v 21 Kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Ba dǝga jappǝr pal wa ɓagana nai davala ngiiga, baɗǝmmaru ɓagamaɓag kǝ ajappa.
\v 22 Vǝlakurvǝlǝg nǝ Muus kǝ adzahadzaha ɓa guvaca, bakǝvakwaha iin bi wa fǝgharzhafǝg biya, fararzha daadijaha daadijaharuwa. Am ɓagaan kǝ aguvac aanji daghuvala ngiiga.
\v 23 Akwama ɓagvaraɓag nǝ aguvac kǝ zǝr daghuvala faciya ngiigga kiyava tsuufa tsagaana Muusa, aujilbǝg ci kǝskuram am nguɗa ǝrivǝɗ dǝ kai mbakyarvad uudi mbanna nai daghuvala ngiigi?
\v 24 Ɓagam bi kǝ shari nǝgha gyi biya, ɓagamɓag kǝ shariy tǝdvad jiirjiira.”
\s1 Yesu iin nǝ Kǝristi
\p 
\v 25 Makwahiin kǝ sarta, kaa ndavǝg kǝ kyalǝma uudahi kwar ndzǝga ma Wurshalima taakiya, “Abi, kwan kǝ-uud war naa tsǝg nǝ-iitǝr?
\v 26 Iin ɗang wan taaghai bat ɓalaɓalǝn? Tagarar bi aanji ndau biya. Nii mbatak hayaranthaig maalah taakiya iin Kǝristiyin hii?
\v 27 Ghwalvǝn kiyam sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ vakavaki sǝghsal dǝ iina, akwama da sǝghawisǝg nǝ Kǝristi jiirjiira, maay wada sǝrgasǝrg kǝ vakavaki sǝghal dǝ-iin biya.”
\p 
\v 28 Ba ndzǝgaan ba tsagtǝr dǝgit nǝ Yesu kǝ uudah ma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla, kaa dzǝgantdzǝg kǝ iin kǝ kunngy amaa, “Aana am sǝrkwasǝrga, am sǝrgasǝrǝg dlaɓ kǝ vakavaki sanal naiya. Sanhi dǝ ndzǝɗa ghǝrar biya, aɗaba Daadamazhigǝli ɓǝlakwadi kaiya dadda jiir nǝ iina, kuram am sǝrgabi nǝ uuram kǝ-iin biya.
\v 29 Ən sǝrgasǝrǝg nai kǝ-iina aɗaba sanhi vakkaana, iin dlaɓa wa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝlǝga.”
\v 30 Tagada ba nǝ Yesu kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa gata viigaan kǝ uudaha. Maay wa fǝt dǝv tǝ vakai biya aɗaba ɓagaa bi sartaan biya.
\v 31 Bakǝvakwaha uudah ba baɗyaka ma dlammakǝlaw fardghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Yesu, ar taakiya, “Aitsaa, ma sartǝn da saay nǝ Kǝristiyin tsaa, da ɓagaan ni kǝ dǝga jappǝrah kwa juujig kwa ɓagaa nǝ ghwalvǝna?”
\p 
\v 32 Cinngaraba nǝ Farisiyah kǝ uudah taa ghaiy tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu ma haay ma haaya, Kaa ɓǝlgantɓǝlǝg kǝ maalaha Zhilla kǝsuufah ard Farisiyah kǝ lii uufa vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl da viigaana.
\p 
\v 33 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Tǝmma ba hǝɗiikǝn sarta ndzǝganar vakaru, tǝhala kwaha ǝn da gwiya daas da vak dadda kwa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝlga.
\v 34 Am da gatkwagatǝgga am da tlǝkwi biya. Vakavaki dǝ kai am da sǝgǝv biya.”
\p 
\v 35 Aiyam nǝ Yahudah ma taatakaatǝra, “Naa da dagal da vaakwar nǝ uudanǝn kwada tlǝvaraa bi ni? Mbatak da dagal da vak Yahudahǝn kwazaral ar ndzǝgan dǝ Helenahǝn kiyava tsagtǝr kǝ Helenah vaakwah hi?
\v 36 Auwa tlatlǝg nǝ-iin dǝ taakiya, ‘Am da gatkwagatǝg, am da tlǝkwi bi ni’? Au dlaɓ wa tlatlǝg nǝ-iin taakiya, ‘Vakavaki dǝ kai am da sǝgǝv bi nii’?”
\s1 Taatǝg nǝ Yesu kǝ langyiya yu kwa vǝla shifǝga
\p 
\v 37 Daghuvala ghyǝngnga haara kǝssa, iin faci kwa juujig baɗǝmma, kaa ghacigaghacig kǝ Yesu dzǝgant kǝ ghaiyaan amaa, “Baɗǝm daddakwa njikǝn nǝ andǝla aa sasǝg sa vakar da hǝɓuwa.
\v 38 Baɗǝm daddakwa fadghǝr tǝ kaiya, bandkwa taga nǝ ǝlbǝga Daadamazhigǝl vinda-vinndana taakiya, njamara yuwa kwa vǝla shifǝga da kǝla sagal ma ǝrviɗyana.”
\v 39 Tag tǝghǝr kǝ Shiɗǝkwa Daadamazhigǝl nǝ Yesu, kwada dlǝghǝg lii fadghǝr tǝ iina, aɗaba ma kwanǝn kǝ sarta vǝlavda bi nǝ Shiɗǝkw Daadamazhigǝl ndan biya, aɗaba favvaara bi nǝ Yesu ndan biya.
\v 40 Cinngara ba nǝ kyalǝma uudah kǝ ǝlbǝgǝn tagaa nǝ Yesu na, kaa am nǝ-iitǝra, “Ba pakat kwanǝn kǝ uuda Tlayanga.”
\v 41 Am nǝ kyalma, “Iin nǝ Kǝristi.” Gwastǝna kyalǝm ar ndava taakiya, “Ɓaga ndar nǝ Kǝristi sagal ma Galili?
\v 42 Abi tagatag nǝ ǝlbǝga Daadamazhigǝl vindavindan taakiya Kǝristi da sagal ma kuɗiga Dauda? Dlaɓa ma Bitalahami kǝssǝn kwa ndzaa nǝ Daudǝn biya?”
\v 43 Aɗabad kwaha, kaa tagwvǝmtagw nǝ araja uudah tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu.
\v 44 Kyalǝm nahar viyarviiga, bakǝvakwaha, maay wa fǝt dǝv tǝ-iin biya.
\s1 Fardǝghǝrǝtbi nǝ maalaha yaa Yahuda tǝ Yesu biya
\p 
\v 45 Gwiyara ba nǝ lii uufa vǝgya Daadamazhigǝlǝn daada vak maalaha zhiila kǝssauufah ard maalaha Farisiyaha, kaa ndavtǝruundavǝg nǝ maalahaan taakiya, “Aujilbǝg samdaabi?”
\v 46 Am nǝ-lii uufǝgǝna, “Maay nǝ uudi tapghana taaghai ndǝ ghwalvǝn biya.”
\v 47 Am nǝ Farisah taa kǝ-lii uufǝgǝna, “Caa, baz kuram ndakwani valakurda valǝga?
\v 48 Nii mǝng ha nǝ uud maamal ma uudah bi ma Farisiyah kwa fadǝghǝrǝt tǝ-iin hii?
\v 49 Maaya, bamma uudahaan kwar sǝrgai kǝ dǝgit tǝghǝr kǝ tsaga Muus biya. Tlafatǝratlafǝg nǝ Daadamazhigǝla.”
\v 50 Nikodimus kwandza dal da vak Yesu wura, dlaɓa palma dakwalaatǝra, kaa ndavǝg kǝ-iin taakiya.
\v 51 “Tagadai kwan nǝ adzahadzaha miyam taakiya, kimya maay tǝgar shari kǝ uud, bamma cingngavacing nǝ dǝgit ɓaga nǝ iin ma ghaiyaan biya?”
\v 52 Kaa ngugarangug kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Kǝgh ndakwi agha uuda Galiliya? Hahǝg dan kǝ shigaan ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝl vinnda-vinndana, aghada nǝghǝgaaka-nǝghǝg taakiya maay nǝ tlayangngi sǝghal ma Galili biya.”
\v 53 Kaa daas kǝ uudah da vǝgyahaatǝra.
\c 8
\s1 Uus kwa viyavǝt ɓa gwaragwara
\p 
\v 1 Kaa dagal dat gavala uufaha zaitun.
\v 2 Dlakadur bawura kaa daas kǝ Yesu damma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla. Kaa dzahvǝtdzahǝg kǝ uudah vakaana, cǝhuran kaa tsagtǝrtsagga.
\v 3 Kaa sǝdǝvsǝg kǝ lii tsaga adzahadzaha muus ard Farisah kǝ uusiin kwa viyavǝt ɓaa gwaragwara, ar ghacinan mataatakatǝra.
\v 4 Kaa tagartag kǝ iitǝr kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Dadda tsaga dǝgit, uusǝn aa vivǝt ɓa gwaragwara.
\v 5 Tagakǝmndatag nǝ adzahadzaha Muus taakiya aa ɗawalav-ɗawalǝg nǝ hulfa kwan kǝ uudah da akura bamma ǝmtsara-ǝmtsǝgga. Auci amǝng?”
\v 6 Ɓagar kwakyarvad ar ngarant kǝ dlǝgǝd nǝ-iitǝr kǝ ndavǝgna, dlaɓa maraa tlǝkǝna kǝ haipani ar da ɗiig nǝ-iitǝr kǝ ghunnjana.
\p Kaa ngǝghǝrangǝg kǝ Yesu farzha kǝ vindǝg tǝ haay dǝ zǝra dǝva.
\v 7 Mbǝraras ba nǝ iitǝr kǝ Yesu dǝ ndavǝgaha, kaa cigǝtciig kǝ iin ghacan amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa maay dǝ haip ma kuram biya aa farzhafǝg kǝ ɗuulǝgaan da akura.”
\v 8 Kaa gwiya ngǝghrangǝg kǝ Yesu, ngal vindǝg tǝ haaya.
\v 9 Cinngara ba nǝ iitǝr ǝndkwaha, kaa fǝgarzhafǝg kǝ iitǝr ciyadagal vaakwahiin ba da palapala, ciggǝt tǝ maalatǝr dat lii ngyikwah ngyikwaha, tǝmma ba nǝ Yesu ard uusǝn ghaciga tǝvuukwana.
\v 10 Kaa cigǝtciig kǝ Yesu ghacan, ndavaru kǝ uusǝn amaa, “Uusǝn ar mǝr nǝ iitǝri? Maay wa ghaza kǝgh biya?”
\v 11 Kaa ngwangug kǝ uusǝn taakiya, “Daada ndangnga, maay aanji ndǝwar biya.” Kai ndakwani ghazanka biya, “Dǝga gwiyarzhara bi kǝ ɓa haip biya.”
\s1 Yesu nǝ paraka duniya
\p 
\v 12 Tǝhala kwaha kaa gwiya tagtǝrtag nǝ Yesu kǝ ǝlbǝg kǝ uudaha amaa, “Kai nǝ paraka duniya. Baɗǝm daddakwa gata kaiya tapnai kǝ dagal ma gurtl biya, da tlǝkǝnatlǝg kǝ paraka shifǝga.”
\v 13 Am nǝ Farisiyah taa kǝ Yesu, “Agha ɓagar shiid kǝ ghǝragha, shidaghǝn maay wa haiganthaig biya.”
\p 
\v 14 Ngwatǝrangug nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Aanji ǝn ɓaga kǝ shiid tǝghǝr kǝ ghǝrara, shidar ba jiira, ǝn sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ vakavaki sanal naaya ard vakavaki ǝnda gwiya daas naiya, aɗaba am sǝrgai nǝ uuram kǝ vakavaki sanal nai ard vakavaki ǝnda gwiya daas nai biya.
\v 15 Am taa shariya nǝgha gyiya nǝ uurama. Ən maay nai tǝgar shari aanji kǝ war biya.
\v 16 Aanji mana da tǝgaan kǝ shariya, shariyara ba jiijiira, aɗaba kai pal biya, kǝm ǝmtaɗ dǝ Daadar kwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\v 17 Ma dzahadzaharuwa vindavavindǝg taakiya akwama tagaratag shidah bu kǝ dǝgit palla, barari dlǝghav nǝ shidaatǝra.
\v 18 Kaiya ǝn shiida ghǝrara, dǝga buwa iin nǝ Daadari bǝlakwadi ɓǝlga.”
\p 
\v 19 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ itǝr taakiya, “Vaakwar nǝ Daadaghini?” Kaa ngutǝrngug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Am sǝrkwa bi kǝskai biya, Daadar ndakwi am sǝrga biya. Akwamammaa sǝrkwasǝrga, mammaa sǝrgasǝrg kǝ Daadara.”
\v 20 Tagada ma sarta kwandza tsag nǝ iin kǝ dǝgit tǝvǝgh kǝ vakavaki ɗiyav nǝ kwaɓa baiko ma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla. Bakǝvakwaha maay wa viyitviig biya, aɗaba ɓagaa bi nǝ sartaan ndan biya.
\s1 Ɓalaraɓalǝg nǝ uudah kǝ agajau tǝghǝr kǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 21 Kaa gwiya tagtǝrtag Yesu kǝ uudahaan dzaharvǝtǝn taakiya, “Ən da dagalara, am da gatkwagatǝga, am da ǝmtsǝg ma haipaharuwa. Vakavaki ǝn da dagal naiya, am da dǝgal biya.
\p 
\v 22 Mbakyarvad kwan wa tagar nǝ maalaha Yahudah taakiya, “Da tsa ghǝran ni kwa taga nǝ iin taakiya, ‘Vakavaki ǝn da dagal naiya, am da dǝgal bina’?”
\v 23 Ka zavukw kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Kurama am dǝga duni nǝ uurama, kai sanhi maghǝrazhigǝla. Kuram am dǝga duunina, kaiya ǝn dǝga duuniyin biya.
\v 24 Iinwa tagankur nai taaki am da ǝmtsǝg ma haipaharuna. Aɗaba akwama famdǝghǝrǝt bi taakiya, kai wa tagankur nai taaki kaiyin nǝ iin biya, bak jiirjiir am da ǝmtsǝg ma haipaharuwa.”
\p 
\v 25 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ-iitǝr kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Agha war nǝngngi?” Kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Ba kai wandza tagankur nai bawur taakiya, bakaiya.
\v 26 Mǝng nǝ dǝgitah baɗyak kwan tagdatag nai tǝghǝr kǝskurama, dlaɓa ǝn tǝkura kǝ shari tǝghǝra. Daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya, ǝlbǝgaana tlaltlǝg fǝvdǝghǝrǝta. Dǝgiti cingananai vakaana, iin wan tagtǝr nai kǝ uudaha duniya.”
\v 27 Nǝgharaakai nǝ uudah taakiya tag tǝghǝr kǝ Daddaan kǝ ǝlbǝg biya.
\v 28 Iin wa nǝ iin tagatǝr nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Sartǝn am da kapgant nǝ uuram kǝ Zǝra Uuda, am da nǝghǝgaaka sartaan taakiya kai nǝ-iina, dlaɓa maay nǝ dǝgiti ǝn ɓag nai kataghǝrar biya, ǝn taa ba dǝgiti tsagghwad nǝ Daadar kaltiya.
\v 29 Daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya ǝmtaɗ dǝ kaiya, ɗuwakus bi nǝ-iin daghuvar biya. Ən ɓa ba dǝgiti naag nǝ-iin ba kǝla hǝnnga.”
\v 30 Ma sarta taa kwanahaan kǝ Yesu uudah ba ɗyak fardghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ iina.
\s1 Kwaraghǝra jiira
\p 
\v 31 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ Yahudahǝn fardǝghǝrt tǝ-iinna, “Mam ba zǝgaan kǝ vukw dǝ hǝkya dǝgiti ǝn tsagkur naiya, am mbǝrzahara ba jiijiira.
\v 32 Am da sǝrgasǝrg kǝ jiira, kwanǝn kǝ jiira iin wada vǝlkur kwarga ghǝraruwa.”
\p 
\v 33 Kaa ngwangug kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Kǝm zhigha Ibrahim nǝmnda, tapamndnai kǝ nǝg kǝ ɛɛva aanji war biya. Aujilbǝg ci kǝskǝgh taaki kǝmnda tlǝkǝnatlǝg kǝ kwarga ghǝramndi?”
\p 
\v 34 Kaa ngutǝrangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Bak jiira wan tagkurtaga, baɗǝm daddakwa fadǝmfǝg kǝ ghǝraan ma ɓa haipa ɛɛva haip nǝ-iina.
\v 35 Maay nǝ ɛɛvǝ ndzǝga hǝnnyah tangw damma zǝrazǝr biya, zǝran kǝ dadda hǝnyaha, ǝndzǝgan ba hǝnyah tangw damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 36 Kwakyarvad kwaha, akwama tlamkǝnatlǝg kǝ kwargaghǝraru vak Zǝriina, am da tlǝkǝnatkǝg kǝ kwaraghǝra jiijiira.
\v 37 Ən sǝrgasǝrg taaki samal am kuɗiga Ibrahima, bakǝvakwaha am naa tsakai nǝ-uurama, aɗaba dlǝghamabi kǝ ǝlbǝgar ma ǝrviɗmahuɗaharu biya.
\v 38 Ən tagkur dǝgiti nǝghana nai vak Daadara, kuram am ɓa dǝgiti cingngama nǝ-uuram vak daadaruwa.”
\s1 Shatanah nǝ Daadaruwa
\p 
\v 39 Kaa ngwarangug kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Daadamnd nǝ Ibrahim.” Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝr, “Akwa mammaa zarha Ibrahim, maa ɓagamaɓag kǝ dǝgitahi ɓagaa nǝ Ibrahima.
\v 40 Kaiya ǝn taa ba jiira dǝgiti cinngananai vak Daadamazhigǝla, kuram ghulamvaghulǝg kǝ naa tsa kaiya. Abi ɓagaabi nǝ Ibrahim kǝ hulfa kwanahaan kǝ dǝgitahaan biya.
\v 41 Aɗaba am ɓa ba dǝgiti ɓag nǝ Daadaruwa.” Aiyam nǝ Yahudaha, “Kǝm masagwah bi nǝmnd biya. Daadamazhigǝl nǝ Daadamnda, ba iin dlaɓ pal nǝ Daadi kǝm dǝ vakai nǝmnda.”
\v 42 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Akwamaa Daadaru nǝ Daadamazhigǝla, mammaa waikwawaiga, aɗaba sanhi vak Daadamazhigǝl naiya. Kai wan kwan vaakwana, Daadamazhigǝl wa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝlga, sanhi dǝ ndzǝɗa ghǝrar biya.
\v 43 Aujilbǝg ci nǝghamaaka bi kǝ ǝlbǝgari? Aɗaba am dzǝgwantbi kǝ cinnga ǝlbǝgar biya.
\v 44 Am dǝga daadaru shatanaha, am naa ba ɓa ɗagiti naag daadaruwa. Dadda tsa shifǝg nǝ-iin bamma fakta, maay dlaɓ lammban dǝ jiir biya, aɗaba maay nǝ jiir ma ghaiyaan biya. Ba cukw sarti tag nǝ-iin kǝ fiida mara hǝnkalaana, aɗaba iin dadda taa fiid nǝ-iina, daada fiidah dlaɓa.
\v 45 Kwakyarvad ǝn taa jiira, famdǝghǝrǝt bi tǝ kai biya.
\v 46 Kwar ma kuram wa margwadamarǝg kǝ haipi tapannanai kǝ ɓaagaani? Akwama jiir wan tag naiya, aujilbǝg kaci famdǝghǝrǝt bi tǝ kai biyi?
\v 47 Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa dǝga Daadamazhigǝla, cinngaan kǝ dǝgit tag nǝ Daadamazhigǝla. Kuram haiyamant bi nǝ-uuram dǝ dǝgiti tag nǝ Daadamazhigǝl biya aɗaba am dǝga Daadamazhigǝl biya.”
\s1 Juujig nǝ Yesu kǝ Ibrahim
\p 
\v 48 Kaa ngugarangug nǝ Yahudah taakiya, “Mbats bak jiir wa tagamnd nǝmnd taakiya agha zhiil Samari dlaɓa shiɗǝkw ghwaɗ ma vǝghagh biya?”
\v 49 Aiyam nǝ Yesu, “Ən maay nai dǝ shiɗǝkw ghwaɗ biya. Daadar wan fǝgaara naiya, kuram lamwalǝg kǝ fǝkwaarafǝga.
\v 50 Kaibi wa gatgar ndangngǝr kǝ ghǝrar biya, mǝng wa gatgwagatǝga, iin dlaɓ nǝ dadda ta shariya.
\v 51 Jiir wan tagkur naiya, daddakwa fǝghaarafǝg kǝ ǝlbǝgara maay ǝmtsǝg badǝm biya.”
\p 
\v 52 Kaa am nǝ maalaha yaa Yahuda taa kǝ-iina, “Kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg ndakwanci taakiya bak jiir agha dǝ shiɗǝkw ghwaɗa. Abi ǝmtsaǝmtsǝg nǝ Ibrahim, bandkwah dlaɓ nǝ tlayangngah ǝmtsahara-ǝmtsahǝga. Bakǝvakwaha kǝgh agha taaki, ‘Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa fǝghaarafǝg kǝ ǝlbǝgagh da maay ǝmtsǝg badǝm biya.’
\v 53 Magha tlǝg nǝng jighaarajig nǝng kǝ daadamnd Ibrahima? Ghǝravaan ndakwani ǝmtsaǝmǝga, tlayangngah ndakwi ǝmtsaharaǝmtsǝhǝga. Magha tlǝg nǝng agha war nǝngi?”
\p 
\v 54 Ngwatǝrangug nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Akwama fanarafǝg kǝ ghǝrara, kwanǝn kǝ ndangngǝra maay tuuk ǝlbǝg biya. Daadari kwa kǝsamant nǝ-uuram taakiya iin nǝ Daadamazhigǝlaruwa iin wa fǝkwaraafǝga.
\v 55 Am sǝrgai nǝ uuram kǝ-iin biya, kaiya ǝn sǝgasǝrǝg kǝ-iina. Maa tagankur nai taaki ǝn sǝrga biya, maa nanalnǝg kǝ dadda fiid band kurama. Ən sǝrgasǝrg nai kǝ-iina, ǝn cingngarnucing dlaɓ kǝ dǝgit tag nǝ-iina.
\v 56 Daadaru Ibrahim dzamadzamǝg maa nǝghan kǝ zamanara, nǝghanǝghǝga dlaɓa dlaiyadlaiga.”
\p 
\v 57 Am nǝ Yahudah taa kǝ Yesuwa, “Kǝgh kwana gwastǝn ɓaghabi kǝ viig kuldlǝb ndan biya, agha gwiya taaki nǝghanǝghǝg kǝ Ibrahima?”
\p 
\v 58 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Bak jiir wan tagkur naiya, yavva bi nǝ Ibrahim ndakwani ǝn ba mǝng naiya,”
\v 59 Tagada ba nǝ Yesu kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga kaa cagantcag kǝ-iitǝr ka akur kiyava tsǝgaana. Shiɓvǝgha nǝ Yesu, kaa ba dagal kǝ-iin ma vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla.
\c 9
\s1 Mbaghanambǝg Yesu kǝ uudi yavva gulfa
\p 
\v 1 Tǝghǝrdǝga dagal Yesu, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ-iin kǝ uuda nǝ-iin kwa yavva gulfa.
\v 2 Ngal ndavgarundavǝg nǝ mbǝrzahaan taakiya, “Dadda tsaga dǝgit, haipa war wa nadal ghwalvǝn yavan gulfni? Haipaan nii, dǝga daddaan ard babbaanhi?”
\v 3 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Kwakyarvad haipa uudanǝn biya, bii haipa daddaana bii babbaan bi wa yavva nǝ-iin gulf biya, yavvayig nǝ-iin ǝndkwaha kwakyarvad marvda ndzǝɗa Daadamazhigǝl tǝ-iina.
\v 4 Badlaɓ tsaw faciya, barari kiyam zǝgaan kǝ vukw dǝ ɓa tlǝra daddakwa ɓǝlkwadiɓǝlga, aɗaba sagaw nǝ avǝɗa maay wa da ɓagaɓag aanji kwar kǝ tlǝr biya.
\v 5 Akwama ban ma duniya, ba kai paraka duniya.”
\v 6 Tagada ba nǝ-iin kwaha, kaa tǝffa kǝ-iin kǝ ashavai dat haaya, kǝɗant kǝ haay dǝ vakaiya, kaa ghudǝt kǝ-iin kǝ haayǝn kǝtghant nǝ-iin da ashavayǝna, masara tǝ gyiya kǝ uudanǝna.
\v 7 Amaa taa kǝ uudanǝna, “Dǝga, bardabarǝg kǝ gi ma dǝlva Siluwan.” Dǝgiti tuuk vakai nǝ Siluwana inn nǝ “Ɓǝlga”. Kaa dagau kǝ uudanǝn barda kǝ gyiyaana, sǝghaasǝg dǝ gyiyaan nǝghǝganǝghǝga.
\v 8 Kaa ndavǝg kǝ tlǝgharawakyaghahaan ard lii narǝtnǝg kǝ nǝghǝganǝghǝg ghalǝg taakiya, “Abi ba ghwalvǝn wandza cǝhurga vaakwan ghalgǝn?”
\v 9 Am nǝ kyalma “Iina.” Am nǝ kyalmaha, “Iin biya, dzakǝvaana.” Iina ǝmtsǝtǝmtsǝg taakiya, “Ba kaiyina.”
\p 
\v 10 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Mbaa ndar kaci giyaghi?”
\p 
\v 11 Ngwaangwug amaa, ghwalvǝn kwa ɗahav dǝ Yesuwǝn wa kǝɗghant haay maswadǝm ma gyiya. Amaa taa kǝskaiya, dǝg bardabarǝg ma dǝlva Siluwam. Danal ba naya ǝn bardana, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝskaiya.
\p 
\v 12 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ-iitǝra, “Mǝr nǝ uuda nǝ-iini?” Aiyama taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Ən sǝrga biya.”
\s1 Harhǝg nǝ Farisiyah kǝ shiga mbǝga gulfǝna
\p 
\v 13 Kaa langaan nǝ uudah kǝ ghwalviin kwandza gulf ba wurǝn davak Farisiyaha.
\v 14 Aɗaba ndza daghuvala faciya ngiig wa kǝɗghant nǝ Yesu kǝ haay mbǝna kǝ gyiya uudanǝna.
\v 15 Kaa ndavgarundavǝg nǝ Farisiyah kǝ ɗuuli mbaa gyiyaana. Aiyam nǝ uudanǝna, “Haay wa kǝɗghant nǝ-iin maswadǝm ma gyiya, kaa barda kǝskaiya, ndakwana ǝn nǝghǝganǝghǝga.”
\p 
\v 16 Kaa tagaan kǝ kyalǝma Farisiyah taaki, “Sahi vak Daadamazhigǝl bi nǝ ghwalvǝn biya, aɗaba maay tsuufa faciya ngiig biya.”
\p Ngal ndavǝg kǝ kyalǝmah taakiya, “Ɓagǝna dau nǝ dadda kwad haip kǝ hulfa kwanahaa kǝ dǝgaha jappǝrahi?” Buud taghwzhataghw kǝ dzamaghǝraatǝra.
\p 
\v 17 Kaa gwiya ndavgaruundavǝg kǝ-iitǝr kǝ uudanǝn taakiya, “Au kaci nǝ wagha nǝghǝgaaka nǝng tǝghǝr kǝ uudanǝn, iin tsau wa wurakant gi?” Kaa ngutǝrangug nǝ uudanǝn amaa, “Tlayang nǝ-iina.”
\p 
\v 18 Fardǝghǝrǝt bi nǝ maalaha Yahudah taakiya ndza gulf nǝ uudanǝn wura biya, ndakwana nǝghǝganǝghǝga. Aɗabad kwaha, kaa ɗahǝgantɗahǝg kǝ iitǝr kǝ daddaana ard babbaana
\v 19 Kaa ndavtǝru-ndavǝg kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Zǝraru wana? Ndza yavva gulf am nǝ uurama? Aaɓaga ndar kaci nǝghǝganǝghǝg ndakwani?”
\p 
\v 20 “Kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg taaki zǝramnd nǝ zǝrna, dlaɓa yavva gulfa.
\v 21 Kǝm sǝrgai kǝ ɗuuli nǝghǝga nǝ iin ndakwan biya, dlaɓa kǝm sǝrgai kǝ daddakwa mbǝghǝnimbǝg biya. Ndavamarundavǝga, zarh bi nǝ-iin biya, tagdatag nǝ iin bad ghaiyaana.”
\v 22 Tagardatag nǝ daddaan ard babbaan ǝndkwana, mbakyarvad ar gǝdza maalaha Yahudaha. Nguɗarant ba wur nǝ maalaha Yahudah kǝ ǝlbǝgaatǝr taakiya, baɗǝm daddakwa tagadatag taaki Yesu iin nǝ Kǝristi, ar lagwaan dagal ma guda dzǝgwazhigǝla.
\v 23 Iin wa tagar nǝ daddaana ar dǝ babbaan taakiya, “Zarh bi nǝ-iin biya, ndavamarundavǝga.”
\p 
\v 24 Kaa gwiya ɗaha uudanǝn ndza gulf wurǝn kǝ Farisaha, am nǝ-iitǝr taa kǝ-iina, “Tag kǝ jiira aɗaba agha faara kǝ Daadamazhigǝla, kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ uudanǝn dadda haipa.”
\p 
\v 25 Aiyama, “Aanji dadda haip nǝ-iin ǝn sǝrga bi nai biya. Dǝgiti pal ǝn sǝrga naiya, wura ndzan gulfa, ndakwana ǝn nǝghǝganǝghǝga.”
\p 
\v 26 Kaa gwiya ndavgarundavǝg kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Aukaci wa ɓagaka nǝ-iin? Wurakant ndarci kǝ gi?”
\p 
\v 27 Ngwatǝrangug amaa, “Tagankurdataga lǝmwalǝg kǝ cingngaana. Aujilbǝg kǝskuram naa gwiya cingngaani? Nii am naa nǝg kǝ Mbǝrzahaanhi?”
\p 
\v 28 Ngal ba ɗahgarv-ɗahǝg kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Kǝgh nǝ mbǝrzaana, kǝm Mbǝrzaha Muus nǝmnda.
\v 29 Kǝm sǝrgasǝrg taakiya tagaatag nǝ Daadamazhigǝl kǝ ghai dǝ Muusa, kiyava kwan kǝ uuda, kǝm sǝrgai vavvaan kǝ vakavaki sal dǝ-iin biya.”
\p 
\v 30 Kaa ngutǝrangug nǝ uudanǝn taakiya, “Wanam nǝ dǝga jappǝr haniina! Am sǝrgai kǝ vakavaki sal nǝ-iin biya, waici mbǝghwanimbǝg kǝ gyiyara,
\v 31 Kiyam sǝrgasǝrǝg maay Dadamazghigǝl cingtǝrnucing kǝ yaa dadda haipah biya. Cingtǝrnuciing kǝ lii ɓagarnǝs kwatǝnahǝra baɗǝmma, dlaɓa ar ɓa dǝgit naag nǝ-iina.
\v 32 Maay wa tapghanatapǝg ba dǝm kǝ cingaciing kǝ daddakwa wurgharant gyi uud yava gulf biya.
\v 33 Akwamaa sahi vak Daadamazhigǝl bi nǝ uudanǝn biya, maa ɓagna bi bandau biya.”
\p 
\v 34 Cinngaraba nǝ-iitǝr ǝndkwaha, aiyam nǝ-iitǝr taa kǝ-iina, “Dali kǝghii yakka bamma gyigyiya haip nǝ uud wagha naa tsagkǝmnd dǝgita?” Ngal lagwarslagw kǝ-iitǝra.
\p 
\v 35 Cinngha ba nǝ Yesu taaki lagwararslagw kǝ uudanǝna, ngal tlǝgaratlǝg kǝ-iina, ndavaru taakiya, “Fǝghǝdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Zǝra Uuda?”
\p 
\v 36 Kaa ngwangug kǝ uudanǝna, aiyama, “Dadda ndangnga, warwahiini? Tagwataga kiyava fadghǝr kǝskai tǝ-iina.”
\p 
\v 37 Ngugharangug nǝ Yesu, taakiya, “Nǝghǝghanǝghǝg ghǝravagha, abi iin wa taaghai dǝ kǝghǝna.”
\p 
\v 38 Aiyam nǝ uudanǝna, “Yaazhigǝla, fandǝghǝrǝtfǝga.” Kaa ɓagarnǝs kǝ-iin kǝ kwatnahǝra.
\p 
\v 39 Aiyam nǝ Yesu, “Sanhi mbakyarvda taa shari nai sama duniya, aɗaba gulfaha ar nǝghana, dlaɓa lii nǝghǝganǝghǝga ar da nal kǝ gulfa.”
\p 
\v 40 Cinngara ba nǝ Farisahǝn ndza tǝvǝgh kǝ-iinǝn ǝntkwana, aiyam am nǝ-iitǝr taa kǝ-iina, “Matlǝg-ghǝragh kǝmnd ndakwi, kǝm gulfaha?”
\p 
\v 41 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, “Akwa mammaa gulfa, mammaa maay dǝ haip biya, kǝm nǝghǝganǝghǝg tsau am nurama, haipaharuwa ndzǝga ba tǝghǝr kǝskurama.
\c 10
\s1 Dadda piig maraw ard agɛɛragɛɛra tuughwahaana
\p 
\v 1 “Bak jiir wan tagkurtag Farisiyaha, baɗǝm dadakwa dagha bi damma agɛɛragɛɛra dǝ ghaiy gud biya, bakǝvakwaha kaa tlǝlla ɗulla dass kǝ-iin tǝ kwatlǝrǝn kǝ ghyǝba, gǝlla dlaɓa gwarǝɗ nǝ-iina.
\p 
\v 2 “Dadakwa dǝgaa dǝ ghaiya wakyagha, iin dadda piiya tuughwaha.
\v 3 Dadda uufa ghaiya wakyagha wurgarwurǝgga kǝ-iina. Tuughwah dlaɓa ar cingarnucinga kǝ kungya dada piiga. Ɗahǝtǝrɗaga kǝ tuughwahaan dǝ ɗagahaatǝra, ngal langtǝrlang dagal da gyǝmǝlla.
\v 4 Tǝhala kwama dadal kǝ tuughwahaan baɗǝm da gyǝmǝlla, kaa dal kǝ-iin tǝvukwatǝra, tuughahah dlaɓa ar gatǝgaan tǝhaltǝhala, aɗaba ar sǝrǝgasǝrǝg kǝ ghaiyaana.
\v 5 Ar tapǝnaiy kǝ gata ghullab badǝm biya, ba kǝ jiirra ar hǝdla dagal vakaana, aɗaba ar dzǝgaakaiy kǝ ghaiya ghullab biya.”
\v 6 Tagatǝrdatag nǝ Yesu kǝ uudaha kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝg dǝghura, bakǝvakwaha nǝghǝnǝgharaakai kǝ dǝgit tagtǝr nǝ-iin biya.
\p 
\v 7 Aɗabadkwaha am Yesu kǝ-iitǝr gwiiyadalla, “Bak jiijiira, ǝn tagkurtaga, kaiy nǝ ghaiya gudlǝgha tuughwaha.
\v 8 Baɗǝm lii sarǝva lakwti ǝn sagau naiya ar gǝllaha dlaɓa ar gwarǝɗɗaha, tuughwahahin ndakwi ar cingtǝrnu biya.
\v 9 Kaiy nǝ ghaiya wakyagha, baɗǝm dadakwa dǝga tǝdǝvad kaiya da katava. Ar da saasa dlaɓa ar da dagala, ar da tlǝkǝnatlǝg vaka piig marawa.
\v 10 Gǝla sagau kwakyarvad ɓa gǝl kaltiya ard tsa shifǝga dlaɓa ard ghyǝhǝga, kaiya sanǝv taakiya ar tlǝkǝna kǝ shifǝga, dlaɓa ar tlǝkǝnan bajar righǝrighaana.
\p 
\v 11 “Kaiy nǝ dadda piig marawa. Dadda piig marawa iin wa vǝlla shifǝgaan kwakyarvad tuughwaha.
\v 12 Suuniya iin bi nǝ dadda piig biya, dlaɓa tuughwaha dǝgaan biya. Aɗabadkwaha bamma sarti ma nǝghǝghanǝghǝg kǝ ghǝygya tǝghal sagauwa, kaa ɗuwaras kǝ-iin kǝ tuughwaha ngal hǝdla dagalaana. Ghǝgya tǝghal da dǝtraadǝg kǝ giɗya tuughwaha dlaɓa kwazǝtǝrdana.
\v 13 Əmdǝradagala nǝ uuddanǝn aɗaba suuniya nǝ-iina ɓa tlǝra kwaɓa, maay lamban dǝ tuughwaha biya.
\p 
\v 14 “Kaiy nǝ dadda piiga marawa. Ən sǝrǝgasǝrǝg kǝ tuughwahara, tuughwahara ar sǝrkwasǝrǝga.
\v 15 Bandkwan sǝrkwa nǝ Daada, kai dlaɓ ǝn sǝrgasǝrǝga kǝ iina. Dlaɓa ǝn vǝlgaan kǝ shiifǝgara kwakyarvad tuughwahaha.
\v 16 Ən mǝng nai dǝ kyǝlǝma tuughwaha kwar dǝga kwanǝn kǝ agɛɛragɛɛra biya. Iitǝr ndakwi barari ǝn sǝtǝrddana. Ghǝravaatǝr ndakwi ar da ciingaan kǝ kungyara, ar da nal kǝ agɛɛragɛɛra palla, dadda piig palla.
\p 
\v 17 “Kwakyarvad kwah wa waikwa Daddara, aɗaba ǝn vǝldavǝlǝg kǝ shifǝgara, dlaɓa ǝn gwiidagwiiga.
\v 18 Maay nǝ dadakwa kǝsǝgwavakǝsǝg kǝ shifǝg biya, aɗaba kaiy wan vǝlǝgaan dǝ naaga ghǝrara. Ən dǝ ndzǝɗa vǝldavǝlga, ǝn ndzǝɗa gwiidagwiga sǝddan dlaɓa. Kwan kǝ dǝgit wa taghwa nǝ Daddara kǝ ɓagaana.”
\p 
\v 19 Kwakyarvad kwan kǝ ǝlbǝggǝn tagada nǝ Yesu, gwiya sadasǝg kǝ taagwavǝgh mataataka Yahudaha.
\v 20 Baɗyak ma iitǝra, ar taakiya, “Shatanaha wa ma vǝghaana, iin wa ɓag nǝ-iin kǝ valaagǝrna. Aaujilǝbǝg am ciingarnuciingi?”
\v 21 Bakǝvakwaha am kyǝlǝmaha, “Kwanahaan kǝ ǝlbǝga tagdai nǝ daddakwad shiɗǝkwa ghwaɗ mavǝghaan biya. Kats wurǝgarantwurǝg shiɗǝkwa ghwaɗ kǝ gyi kǝ gulǝfa?”
\s1 Fardǝghǝrǝt bi nǝ yaa Yahuda tǝ Yesu biya
\p 
\v 22 Masarta kwaha ndza akwhya vakka, ɓa hwaɗaga dzama hyaɗa vǝgya Dadamazhigǝl nǝ-uud ma wurushalima.
\v 23 Yesu ndza gwayav ma gagaazaya Sulemanu ma vǝgya Dadamazhǝgǝla.
\v 24 Kaa dzahvǝtdzahǝg kǝ Yahudaha tǝghǝr kǝ-iina, kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Agha ɗukǝmǝndars ndar ma dzamaghǝr tǝghǝr kǝskǝgh mbǝrdakwani? Maba kǝgh nǝ Kǝristi tagkǝmǝndtag bat ɓalaɓala.”
\p 
\v 25 Ngwatǝrangug nǝ Yesu kǝ iitǝra, “Tagankurdatag bawura, famdǝghǝrǝt biya. Tlǝrahaan ǝn ɓag naay ma ɗaaga Daadarna, iitǝr shidahara.
\v 26 Kurama famdǝghǝrǝt biya, aɗaba am tuughwahar bi nǝ-uuram biya.
\v 27 Tuughwahara ar cinngacinng kǝ ǝlbǝgara ǝn sǝrǝtǝrsǝrǝga, dlaɓa ar gatkwagatǝga.
\v 28 Ən vǝltǝr shifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝra, ar da tapǝnay kǝ ǝmǝtsǝg biya, maay dlaɓa wa da hutsǝrvahutsǝg sagal miizha dǝvvar biya.
\v 29 Daadara, kwa vǝlǝghwavǝlǝg kǝ tughwahaana jujig dǝ ndzǝd baɗǝma, maay wa da hutsǝtǝrdahutsǝg sagal miizha dǝva Daadar biya
\v 30 Kaiya ard Daada kǝmba palla.”
\p 
\v 31 Kaa gwiya cagantcag kǝ yaa Yahuda kǝ akurah kiyavva ɗawalǝgaana.
\v 32 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ-iitǝra, ɓagankuraɓag kǝ tlǝrah maraw baɗyak vak Daada, am da ɗawalkwa kwakyarvad kwar kaci nǝ-uurami?”
\p 
\v 33 Aiyam yaa Yahuda, kǝm ɗawalǝk kwakyarvad tlǝr marawǝn ɓagha nǝng biya, kwakyarvad badza ɗaaga Daadamazhigǝla. Kǝgha agha uud ba gyaagyaana a gǝra ghǝragh dǝ Dadamazhǝgǝla.
\v 34 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Vindavai kwan ma adzahadzhaharu taakiya, ‘Amaiya am ghǝlaha biya’?
\v 35 Am sǝrǝgasǝrǝg taakiya, ǝlbǝga Dadamazhǝgǝl vindavindana ndzǝga bat jiir ba kǝlaa hǝnga. Akwama ɗahavtǝr dǝ ‘Ghǝlaha’ nǝ lii cauwara ǝlbǝga Yaazhigǝla,
\v 36 aujilbǝgci kǝskuram am taakiya ǝn badza ɗaaga Daadamazhigǝl mbakyarvad naa tagda taakiya Kaiy nǝ zǝra Daadamazhigǝli? Maay ba wah ndakwi kai wa fakwi nǝ Dadda ba kǝrkangyakwa, dlaɓa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝllǝg sama duniya.
\v 37 Akwama tlǝra Daadar bi wan ɓag nai biya, famdǝghǝrǝt bi tǝ kaiy biya.
\v 38 Akwama iitǝr wan ɓag naiya, aanji famdǝghǝrǝt bi tǝ kaiy biya, famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ tlǝrahara, aɗaba am sǝrana, dlaɓa am nǝghǝghaaka taakiya, Daada ma kaiya, kaiy dlaɓa ma iina.”
\v 39 Kaa gwiya ɓaa kǝla ndzǝɗatǝr kǝ viigaana, bakǝvakwaha ngǝdlatǝrvangǝdlǝg nǝ Yesu ma dǝvvatǝra.
\p 
\v 40 Tǝhala kwaha kaa gwig kǝ Yesu damma hal dzǝva kǝ zaagha Urudun, da vavaki ɓaga nǝ Yuhwana kǝ tsuufǝg ba zǝngwa, ndza kǝ-iin vakwaha.
\v 41 Uudaha baɗyaka sarǝvǝsǝg sa vakaana, kaa ba tagaan kǝ-iitǝr taakiya, “Tapǝghanaiy nǝ Yuhwana kǝ ɓa dǝga japǝr biya, bakǝvakwaha baɗǝm nǝ dǝgiti taga nǝ-iin tǝghǝr kǝ uudanǝna ba jirra.”
\v 42 Lii ndzar vakwah dlaɓa baɗyaka fardǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Yesu.
\c 11
\s1 Əmtsǝga Liyazaru
\p 
\v 1 Ndza mǝng nǝ uuda nǝ iin ɗaagaan Liyazaru kwa ndza yanng biya, ndzǝga ma Betani, gǝdzǝr kǝsaatǝr kǝ Maryam ard dǝghwa babbaan Marta.
\v 2 Ba kwaniin kǝ Maryam wa yanng bi zǝra babbaan Lazarusa, iin wa ɗaighara wala tǝrshin bǝtbǝt tǝ shigahaha Yaazhigǝla, dlaɓa masardan dǝ guja ghǝraana.
\v 3 Kaa ɓǝlgantɓǝlǝg kǝ dǝghwaha babbaan buna kǝ ghai davak Yesu taakiya, “Yaazhigǝla, dadda kwagha waig nǝngna, yanng biya.”
\p 
\v 4 Cinngha ba nǝ Yesu ǝndkwaha, aiyama, “Kwan kǝ yanngbiyǝra da tsǝgabi kǝmtsǝg biya. Bakǝvakwaha, da saa dǝ ndanngǝr nǝ wan kǝ Dadamazhigǝla, dlaɓa fǝvvaara Zǝraana.”
\p 
\v 5 Waigaan nǝ Yesu kǝ Martla ard dǝghwa babbaan Maryama ard Liyazaru.
\v 6 Cinngha ba Yesu taakiya yanng bi nǝ Liyazaru biya, kaa gwiya gaha kǝ hǝngah bu vakavaki ndza dǝ iina.
\v 7 Tǝhala kwaha, aiyama taa kǝ mbǝrzahaana, “Gwiya jiyam daadama haaya Yahudiya.”
\p 
\v 8 Aiyam nǝ mbǝrzahaana taa kǝ iina, “Dadda tsaga dǝgita, bamma hǝnngahaan dalna, Yahudah ɓagarɓag kǝlaa ndzǝɗaatǝr kǝ ɗawala kǝgh da akur kiyava tsa kǝgha, aitsǝm agha naa gwiya daada vaakwaha?”
\p 
\v 9 Kaa ngutǝrangug Yesu taakiya, “Abi au kǝlaawa tarbu ma vanng pal? Baɗǝm daddakwa dagal dǝ vaciya, maay tsǝgaan nǝ mɓǝdǝg biya, kwakyarvad nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ paraka duniya.
\v 10 Daddakwa dagal kavǝɗa, tsǝgaan nǝ mbǝɗga, kwakyarvad maay nǝ parak vakaan biya.
\p 
\v 11 Tǝhala kwa tagada nǝ iin kwaha, kaa gwiya tagtǝrtag kǝ iin taakiya, “Tsaghwa miyam Liyazaru tsaatsǝg haara, ǝn dagal da ciigaana.”
\p 
\v 12 Aiyam mbǝrzahaan taa kǝ iina, “Yaazhigǝla, ma ba haara wa tsǝgatsǝga da mbǝga.”
\p 
\v 13 Taga taakiya ǝmtsaaǝmtsǝg Liyazaru nǝ Yesu, mbǝrzahaan tlatlar ba taakiya ba haara jiijiir wa hǝnng nǝ iina.
\p 
\v 14 Kaa ba tagtǝrdatag kǝ Yesu bat ɓalaɓal taakiya, “Əmǝtsaaǝmtsǝga Liyazaru.
\v 15 Ən dlaiga nai kwakyarvad kurama aɗaba ndzan maay vakwah biya, kiyava fadǝghǝr kǝskurama. Ciyamciiga, jiyam dagal da vakaana.”
\p 
\v 16 Am Toma, kwa ɗahav Didimus\f + \fr 11:16 \ft Didimus ma ghaiya Heleniyaha ard Toma ma ghaiya Aramiyaha ba bǝrkuɗatǝra, dǝgit tuuk vakai nǝ iina, iin ghwalaha\f* taa kǝ kyalǝma mbǝrzaha, “Jiyam dagal ghǝrava miyama, kiyam ǝmtsan ǝmtaɗ dǝ iina.”
\s1 Yesu nǝ ciig ma gǝdlaha ard shifǝga
\p 
\v 17 Tsǝgwa ba Yesu vaakwahiina, cinnghacinng taakiya, ǝmtsaaǝmtsǝg Liyazaru, hǝngaan uufaɗ ma gǝtla.
\v 18 Betani ndza ba hyɛf dǝ Wurshalima dǝt bi dat mil bu taatakatǝr biya.
\v 19 Baɗyak Yahudahi sarǝv saa tagar dzǝgwagh ǝmtsǝga zǝra babbaatǝr kǝ Martla ard Maryama.
\v 20 Cinngha ba Martla taakiya sagau Yesu, kaa dagal kǝ iin da tlǝgaraatlǝga. Maryam dlaɓa ndzǝga ma hǝnyaha.
\p 
\v 21 Aiyam nǝ Martl taa kǝ Yesu, “Yaazhigǝla, magha ndza mǝng nǝng vaakwana, maa ǝmtsa bi zǝra baabar biya.
\v 22 Aanji ba ndakwan ndakwi ǝn sǝrgasǝrga taakiya baɗǝm nǝ dǝgit agha ghalga nǝng vǝlakvǝlǝg Daadamazhigǝla.”
\p 
\v 23 Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Da gwiya ciig zǝra baabagha.”
\v 24 Kaa ngugarangug Martl taakiya, “Ən sǝrgasǝrga da ciig dǝ shiifǝg ma gǝtlah daghwvala ghyǝnga duniya.”
\p 
\v 25 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Kai ciig ma gǝtlah ard shiifǝga. Daddakwa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya, aanji ǝmtsana da ciig dǝ shiifǝga.
\v 26 Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa ndzǝgan tǝdvad fadghǝr tǝ kaiya, da tapnai kǝ ǝmtsǝg biya. Fǝghǝdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kwanna?”
\p 
\v 27 Aiyam Martla taa kǝ iina, “Aana, Yaazhigǝla, fandǝghǝrǝtfǝg taakiya kǝgh nǝ Kǝristi, Zǝra Daadamazhigǝl kwa da sii samma duniya.”
\s1 Tuwaatug nǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 28 Tagada ba Martl kwana, kaa daas kǝ iin ɗahant kǝ dǝghwa babbaan Maryam damma dlǝmmbaava, amaa, “Wa sǝghǝvsǝg dadda tsaga dǝgita, wai nǝ iin ndava kǝgha.”
\v 29 Bad cinngacinnga Maryam waha, kaa ciya dagal kǝ iin ba watswats da vak Yesu.
\v 30 Dagha bi nǝ Yesu damma gǝdzǝrkǝs ndan biya, ba ndzǝgaan vakavaki tlǝghara nǝ Martla.
\v 31 Yahudahi kwa ndzar ǝmtaɗ dǝ Maryam ma hǝnyah ar tagar dzǝgwagha, nǝghara ba nǝ iitǝr kǝ ciya dagala Maryam ba watswatsa, kaa gatǝgaan kǝ iitǝr dagala, matlǝg ghǝraatǝr ndakwi dagal damma gǝtlaha da tuug vakwaha.
\p 
\v 32 Dal ba nǝ Maryam da vakavaki dǝ Yesu, nǝghǝgha ba nǝ iina, kaa mbǝɗgambǝɗǝg kǝ iin tǝ vukwana, amaa taa kǝ iina, “Yaazhigǝla, magha mǝng nǝnga vaakwana, maa ǝmtsa bi nǝ zǝra baabaar biya.”
\p 
\v 33 Nǝghǝgha ba Yesu kǝ Maryam tuuga, ard Yahudahi salar ǝmtaɗ dǝ iin ndakwi ar tuuga, kaa ngǝrɗkǝngǝrɗǝg kǝ Yesu ma ǝrviɗyana ba vaivaiya.
\v 34 Kaa ndavtǝrundavǝg kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Hǝɗama vaakwari?”
\p Am nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Yaazhigǝla, aasǝg saa vazgaana.”
\p 
\v 35 Kaa tuug kǝ Yesu.
\p 
\v 36 Kwakyarvad kwaha, kaa tagaan kǝ Yahudah taakiya, “Vazamvazǝg kǝ ɗuuli waiga nǝ iina.”
\p 
\v 37 Aiyam kyalǝm ma iitǝr taa kǝ ghǝrahaatǝra, “Wurgharantwurǝg kǝ gyi kǝ gulfa. Maa tsǝgarvai dlaɓ kǝ uudanǝn kǝ ǝmtsǝg biya?”
\s1 Ciighantciig nǝ Yesu kǝ Liyazaru ma gǝtla
\p 
\v 38 Kaa gwiya mbǝkǝnmbǝg ma ǝrviɗan kǝ Yesu ba vaivaiya, ngal dagal kǝ iin damma gǝtliina. Gǝtliin huravna ma kura, kaa hǝɗvarduhǝɗǝg ghaiyan dǝ akura.
\v 39 Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Tlǝgamarwatlǝg kǝ akurna.” Aiyam Martla dǝghwa babba uudanǝn ǝmtsaaǝmtsǝgǝn taa kǝ Yesu, “Yaazhigǝla, abi shiig ndakwana, aɗaba hǝngaan uufaɗ hinanan ba vaakwaha.”
\p 
\v 40 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Tagan kaki taakiya akwama fǝghǝdǝghǝrǝtfǝga, agha da nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ ndangǝra Daadamazhigǝl biya?”
\p 
\v 41 Kaa tlǝgarwatlǝg kǝ iitǝr kǝ akurǝna. Kaa dzǝgantdzǝg kǝ Yesu kǝ ghǝran damma ghǝrazhigǝla amaa, “Ən tagak uusa, Daada, kwakyarvad cinnghwanacinnga.
\v 42 Ən sǝrgasǝrǝg agha cinngwanacinng ba kǝlaa hǝnga, na tagda kwakyarvad uudahaan ghacga vaakwanǝn ar fǝdghǝrǝt taakiya, kǝgh wa ɓǝlǝghkwadi kaiya.”
\v 43 Tǝhala kwa tagada nǝ Yesu kǝ kwaha, kaa dzǝgantdzǝg kǝ iin kǝ ghaiya baɗyakɗyaka amaa, “Liyazaru, asǝg sagala!”
\v 44 Kaa ba sagal kǝ uudanǝn ǝmtsaǝmtsanǝna, faɗafaɗan ma kǝlpakan baz dǝvvahaan ard shigahaana, huɗvǝgaan dlaɓa kutakutan ma kǝlpakanǝn hǝɗana dǝvakaina. Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Futamaarafutǝga, aa dǝg dagala.”
\s1 Nguɗavantnguɗǝg nǝ Sawariya tsa Yesu
\p 
\v 45 Aɗabad kwaha, baɗyak yaa Yahudah kwa salar sa nǝghǝgara kǝ Maryama, dlaɓa nǝghǝgharanǝghǝg kǝ dǝgit ɓagaa nǝ Yesu, kaa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg kǝ iitǝr tǝ iina.
\v 46 Bakǝvakwaha kaa dagal kǝ kyalmaatǝr davak Farisiha, ar tagtǝr kǝ dǝgit ɓagaa nǝ Yesu.
\v 47 Aɗabad kwaha, kaa ɗahgantɗahǝg kǝ maalaha zhiila kǝsauufah ard Farisih kǝ dzahava gyiɗya. Ar ndavaru kǝ ghǝrahatǝra am nǝ iitǝra, “Auwa kiyam da ɓag nǝ miyammi? Vazǝg kǝ uudanǝn za ba vukw dǝ ɓa dǝgaha ajappǝr baɗyaka!
\v 48 Akwama ɓǝlyamarnaaɓǝlg kǝ ɓa kwanahaana, baɗǝm nǝ uudaha ar da fadghǝr tǝ iina. Kaa da sagau kǝ Romah ar da kǝsuu kǝ Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla miyamma ard dlamaa kǝlaawa miyama.”
\p 
\v 49 Pal ma iitǝra kwa ɗahav dǝ Kayafa, kwandza maal ba tingting ma zhiila kǝsauufah ma kwaha kǝ viiga, amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Kuram am sǝrgai ba ndau biya.
\v 50 Nǝghamaaka biya, abi ngulǝm ǝmtsa nǝ uud pal kwakyarvad uudaha, tǝghǝr kwada ruuga nǝ dlamakǝlaaw baɗǝm?”
\v 51 Tagada dǝ naaga ghǝran bi nǝ Kayaf kǝ kwah biya, aɗaba ndza iin maal ba tingting ma zhiila kǝsauufah makwaha kǝ viiga, tagadatag kǝ tlayangǝr taakiya, da ǝmtsǝg Yesu kwakyarvad dlamaa kǝlaawa Yahudaha,
\v 52 mbakyarvad Yahudah kalti biya, dlaɓa kiyava dzaha zarha Daadamazhigǝl kwa kwazarakwazǝg aanji takwara, ar nal kǝ palla.
\v 53 Ciigǝt daghuvala kwahiin kǝ sarta, kaa ɗiya sawariya tsa shifǝga Yesu kǝ iitǝra.
\p 
\v 54 Kwakyarvad kwaha gwiya bi Yesu gwayav ma taataka dlamaa kǝlaawa Yahudah tǝ ɓalal biya, dlakulva kwaha kaa ɗuugharsɗug kǝ iin kǝ vakavakina, kaa ba dagal kǝ iin damma lard kwa hyɛf dǝ tǝghala, kaa daas damma gǝdzǝr kǝs kwa ɗahav dǝ Ifrayim, vakavaki ndza nǝ iin dǝ mbǝrzahaana.
\p 
\v 55 Hǝrzǝt ba nǝ Haarakǝsa Dzǝva Hǝnyaha Yahudaha, kaa dagat kǝ lii ma gǝdzǝrkǝs baɗyak damma Wurushalima kiyava pǝsha ghǝraatǝr lakwti kǝ haarakǝs bandkwa tagaa nǝ dǝga daadijahaatǝra.
\v 56 Tlatǝr ba gata Yesu, kaa daas kǝ iitǝr damma gaagazaiya Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl ar ghacan ar ndava zarabahaatǝr taakiya, “Au wam tlatlǝg nǝ uuram? Da ba sagau nǝ iin kwan damma haarakǝsa?”
\v 57 Aɗaba ndza tagardatag nǝ maalaha zhiila kǝsauufah ard Farisiyah ba wur taakiya, baɗǝm daadakwa sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ vakavaki dǝ Yesu, aa sasǝg sa tagaana, kiyava vigaan kǝ iitǝra.
\c 12
\s1 Masavaramasǝg wal bǝtbǝt kǝ Yesu ma Betani
\p 
\v 1 Tǝmma ba hǝnng ǝngkwah kǝ haarakǝsa Dzava Hǝnnyaha, kaa ba dagal kǝ Yesu damma Betani vakavaki dǝ Liyazaru, kwa ciighant Yesu dǝ shiifǝga.
\v 2 Kaa tǝvaratǝg kafa hwaas kǝ Yesu. Martl wa tagwa kafa, pal Liyazaru ma uudahi ndzar zaa kaf ǝmtaɗ dǝ Yesu.
\v 3 Kaa ba kǝsgantkǝsǝg kǝ Maryam kǝ ghǝndǝka sǝmtala tǝrshǝna nardi, kwaba pir ganana, ɗayarǝt tǝ shigaha Yesu, dlaɓa masaradan kǝ shigahaan dǝ guja ghǝrana. Kaa ba gǝgagǝg kǝ shiiga tǝrshinǝn kǝ hǝnyah baɗǝmma.
\v 4 Bakǝvakwaha, am Yahuda Iskariyoti, pal ma mbǝrzahaan kwa da vǝlǝgaana,
\v 5 “Auwjilbǝg maa vǝlavǝt bi nǝ tǝrshinǝn tǝ kwaɓ kwa tlǝkǝna nǝ bariyam ma vannga dǝrmǝk hǝkǝrɗ, tǝhala kwaha vǝlvtǝr kǝ talagah biyi?”
\v 6 Tagada kwakyarvad naa mǝltǝru kǝ talagah bi nǝ Yahud kǝ kwah biya, aɗaba gǝl nǝ iina. Dlaɓa iin dadda hǝkya kwaɓaatǝra, ɓaa gǝl sagal ma vakaiya.
\v 7 Aiyam nǝ Yesu, “Aɗuuga, ndza fa kwakyarvad daghuvali kwada hǝɗkwa nǝ uuda.
\v 8 Am ba kǝlaa hǝnng ǝmtaɗ dǝ talagaha, aɗaba am maay kǝlaa hǝnng ǝmtaɗ dǝ kai biya.”
\s1 Ɗiyavaɗiig sawariya tsa Liyazaru
\p 
\v 9 Ciingara ba dzahava Yahudah baɗyak taakiya vakwan Yesu, kaa sagau kǝ iitǝra, sarǝv kwakyarvad Yesu kalti biya, aɗaba ar vaznan baz Liyazaru kwa cighant Yesu dǝ shiifǝga.
\v 10 Kaa ɗiiya sawariya kǝ maalaha zhilla kǝsauufaha, kiyava tsǝgaan kǝ iitǝr baz Liyazaru,
\v 11 aɗaba tǝdvad Liyazaru wa ɗuwarars Yahudah baɗyak kǝ zhilla kǝsauufahaatǝr ar fadghǝr tǝ Yesu.
\s1 Dagha damma Wurshalim Yesu
\p 
\v 12 Wurga kǝsaana, cinngaracinng nǝ uudah baɗyak kwa sarǝv sa vaka Hwaɗaga Haarakǝsa Dzava Hǝnnyah taakiya, tǝghǝrdǝga dagat damma Wurshalim Yesu.
\v 13 Kaa cagantcag kǝ iitǝr kǝ apayapaya njuura, kaa dagal kǝ iitǝr da vakaana, ar dzǝgant kǝ ghai ar ɗiyaru kǝ cawa, ar taakiya, “Hosanna! Bark kǝ daddakwa sagauw ma ɗaaga Yaazhigǝla! Barka kǝ tlǝkǝsa yaa Israila!”
\v 14 Tlǝghaara ba Yesu kǝ zǝra aghyungwa, kaa ɗalgaan kǝ iina, bandkwa vindava taakiya,
\v 15 “Gǝdz bi Dǝghwa Sihiyon biya; vazǝg kǝ tlǝksagh saas cǝhurga tǝ zǝra aghyungwa”.
\v 16 Ba zǝngwa nǝgharaaka bi mbǝrzahaan kǝ kwan kǝ dǝgit biya, da nǝgharaaka tǝhalakwa favaara Yesu, kaa dzamgaan kǝ iitǝr taakiya, vindavavindǝg nǝ wan kǝ dǝgitaha tǝghǝr kǝ iina, dlaɓa dǝginahaan dzǝghaardzǝg bakalkalla bandkwa viindavana.
\v 17 Uudahi ndzar ǝmtaɗ dǝ iin masarta kwa ɗahghant nǝ iin kǝ Liyazaru sagal magǝtla, dlaɓa ciyan kǝ iin dǝ shiifǝga, kaa zavukw kǝ iitǝr dǝ tagtǝr dǝgitahi ɓagatǝra Yesu kǝ uudaha.
\v 18 Daral nǝ uudah baɗyak da dlǝgha Yesu kwakyarvad cinngaracinng kǝ dǝga ajapǝri ɓagaa nǝ iina.
\v 19 Aiyam Farisiyaha ma taatakatǝra, “Wayamciya, maay vakavaki langkiyam wan biya. Vazamzǝg kǝ ɗulli gatǝg duni kǝ iin baɗǝmma.”
\s1 Tagadatag Yesu kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ ǝmtsǝgaana
\p 
\v 20 Ndza mǝng kyalma Helenaha ma lii daral da ɓa kwatǝnahǝr ma sarta hwaɗaga haarakǝsa.
\v 21 Kaa sagau kǝ iitǝr sa vak Filigus uuda Betsaida ma haaya Galili, kaa ndavgarundavǝg kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Dadda ndanga, ma kǝmnda naagaan ma kǝmnda nǝghǝgha kǝ Yesu.”
\v 22 Kaa dagal kǝ Filigus da tagar kǝ Andrawus, kaa dagal kǝ iitǝr ba bǝrkuɗaatǝr ar tagar kǝ Yesu.
\v 23 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝr, “Ɓagaaɓag sart kwada fǝvaara Zǝra Uuda.
\v 24 Bak jiijiira, ǝn tagkurtaga, ma riiyava bi zǝra hǝi damma haay ǝmtsan biya, ndzǝga ba njakǝɗinjaana. Akwama ǝmtsaaǝmtsǝga, yiigaan kǝ zǝrh baɗyaka.
\v 25 Baɗǝm daddakwa waiya shifǝgaana da ɓǝlgaan dagala, baɗǝm daddakwa ɗuugant shifǝgaan ma duunina, da tlǝknatlǝg kǝ shifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 26 Baɗǝm daddakwa da ɓaguwa tlǝra, barari gatkwagatǝga. Baɗǝm vakavaki dǝ kaiya, da ndzǝga ba ǝmtaɗ dǝ kai nǝ daddakwa ɓaguwa tlǝra. Da fǝgaarafǝg Daadar kǝ daddakwa ɓaguwa tlǝra.”
\v 27 “Ndakwana mbakwambǝg ma ǝrviɗyara. Au ci wan da tag naiyi? Ən taakiya, ‘Daada, katkwakatǝg ma kwan kǝ sart nii?’ Maaya, sanhi ba kǝrkangyǝkw kwakyarvad kwan kǝ sarta.
\v 28 Daada, faarafǝg kǝ ɗaagagha.” Kaa sii kǝ ghai sii ma ghǝrazhigǝla amaa, “Fanaarafǝga, dlaɓa ǝn da gwiya fǝgaarafǝga.”
\v 29 Ciingara ba nǝ uudahaan ghacga vakwahǝn kǝ ghaiya, am nǝ iitǝra, “Karazhigǝl waa tlaava.” Am kyǝlǝm dlaɓa, “Zǝrɓǝlg waa tagar ghaiya.”
\v 30 Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Kwan kǝ ghai sahi kwakyarvad mǝlkuruwa, kwakyarvad kai biya.
\v 31 Da tǝvar ndakwan nǝ shari kǝ duniya, da lagwav ndakwan dlaɓ nǝ dadda kwara duunina.
\v 32 Mada tsǝgwakuttsǝgw nǝ uud ma duniya, ǝn da tǝɗda kǝ uudah baɗǝm sa vakara.”
\v 33 Tagada kwakyarvad marda nǝ Yesu kǝ hulfa ǝmtsǝgi da ǝmtsǝg nǝ iina.
\v 34 Aiyam nǝ uudah taa kǝ Yesu, “Tagakǝmǝndatag nǝ adzahadzah taakiya, da ndzǝga bad shiifǝg nǝ Kǝristi ba ɗǝmma. Agha tag ndandar kaci taakiya barari nǝ zǝr uuda da tsǝgwavi? War nǝ Zǝr Uudiini?”
\v 35 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Parakǝrǝn ǝmtaɗ dǝ kuramna, da zǝlma bi vaivai biya. Damdagal bamma sartǝn mǝng nǝ parak ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kurama, aa tlǝkuraa bi gurtl biya. Daddakwa dagal ma gurtla sǝrgai kǝ vakavaki dagal nǝ iin biya.
\v 36 Famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ parakǝna, bamma sarti am ǝmtaɗ dǝ iina, aɗaba am nal kǝ zǝrha paraka.” Tǝhala tagdatag kǝ Yesu kǝ kwan kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa dagal kǝ iin shǝɓvana.
\s1 Larwalǝg Yahudah kǝ fadghǝr tǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 37 Baaba dǝgaha jappǝrǝn ɓagaa Yesu tǝvukwatǝrna, bakǝvakwha larwalǝg kǝ fadǝghǝr tǝ iina.
\v 38 Dzǝghaar kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ dǝgit taga nǝ tlayang Ishaya wannǝn taakiya, “Yaazhigǝla, warwa fǝdghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ ǝlbǝgamndi, dlaɓa margharda kǝ war nǝ Yaazhigǝl kǝ dǝgiti ɓagaa nǝ dǝvaani?”
\v 39 Kwakyarvd kwan nǝ iin wa fardghǝrǝt bi nǝ iitǝr biya, bandkwa tagada nǝ Ishaya vakavaki tlǝrǝn taakiya,
\v 40 “Gulfǝghantgulfǝg kǝ gyiyahaatǝra, dlaɓa naatǝrdalnǝg kǝ ǝrviɗyatǝr ba dǝkdǝka, haik kǝ nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iitǝr dǝ gyiyahaatǝra, dlaɓa haik kǝ nǝghǝgaakanǝghǝg ma ǝrviɗyatǝra, haik gwiya sa vakar kǝ iitǝra, ǝn mbǝtǝranana.”
\v 41 Tagada kwakyarvad nǝghanǝghǝg nǝ Ishaya kǝ ndangǝra Yesu, dlaɓa tagda kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝ iina.
\v 42 Bakǝvakwaha, uudah baɗyak fardǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Yesu, baz maalahatǝr baɗyak fardghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ iina. Kwakyarvad gǝdza Farisiyaha, tagarai taakiya fardghǝrǝtfǝg biya, haik lagwtǝrlagw sagal ma guda dzǝgwazhigǝla.
\v 43 Aɗaba ar waiya ba galǝg vak uudaha tǝghǝr kǝ galǝg vak Dadamazhǝgǝla.
\s1 Əlbǝga Yesu da ghudgaan kǝ shariya
\p 
\v 44 Kaa dzǝgantdzǝg Yesu kǝ ghaiya, amaa, “Baɗǝm daddakwa fadghǝr tǝ kaiya, fadghǝr tǝ kaiy kalti biya, fadghǝr tǝ dadakwa ɓalakwadi kaiya.
\v 45 Baɗǝm daddakwa vaza dat kaiya, nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\v 46 Sanhi band parak nai samma duniya, aɗaba haik kǝ ndzǝgan kǝ daddakwa fadghǝr tǝ kai baɗǝm ma gurǝtla.
\v 47 Baɗǝm dadakwa cinnghacinng kǝ ǝlbǝgahara, dlaɓa tsuufghant biya, kai bi dadda tǝgar shari biya. Sanhi kwakyarvad tǝgar shari kǝ duni nai biya, aɗaba ǝn katant kǝ duniya.
\v 48 Daddakwa ɗuwakusɗuuga, dlaɓa haighant bi kǝ ǝlbǝgar biya, mǝng daddakwa tǝgar shariya, ǝlbǝgǝn taganda naina, iin wa da tǝgar shari daghuvala ghyǝnga duniya.
\v 49 Dǝginahaan ǝn tag nai sagal vakar biya, Daada kwa ɓǝlakwadi kai iin wa taghwatag kǝ dǝgiti ǝn da tag naiya.
\v 50 Ən sǝrgasǝrǝg dlaɓa shifǝga tangw dama zǝrazǝra tlǝvǝkǝna tǝdǝvad dǝgiti tag Daada. Kwakyarvad kwaha baɗǝm nǝ dǝgit naa tagda naiya, naa tagda ba kalkal bandkwa taghwa Daada taakiya aa tagantaga.”
\c 13
\s1 Baratǝrdabarǝg Yesu kǝ shig kǝ mbǝrzahaana
\p 
\v 1 Lakwti ɓag sarta Hwaɗaga Haarakǝsa Dzǝva Hǝnnyaha, sǝrghaakasǝrǝg Yesu taakiya ɓaagɓag sartaan kwada ɗuug nǝ iin kǝ duni kiyava gwiya daas da vak Daada. Waighantwaig tsau Yesu kǝ uudahaan ma duniya, dlaɓ maratǝrdamarǝg kǝ waiyakǝvaan tangw dat ghaalaana.
\v 2 Lakwti za kafa hwaas kǝ Yesu ard mbǝrzahaana, fagharafǝg Shatanah kǝ Yahuda, zǝra Saminu Iskariyoti kǝ vǝla Yesu.
\v 3 Sǝrgasǝrǝg Yesu taakiya, fadǝmfǝg Daad kǝ dǝgitah miizha dǝvaan baɗǝmma, dlaɓa sǝrgasǝrǝg sahi vak Daadamazhigǝla, da gwiiya daas da vak Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 4 Ma sartǝn ar za kafna, kaa ciigǝtciig Yesu, tsugda kǝ sǝɗavaani gyimala, kǝsant kǝ patkara sǝɗav nguɗǝs tǝ ngyilaana.
\v 5 Tǝhala kwaha gǝt kǝ iin kǝ yu ma kuwa, farzha kǝ bara shigaha mbǝrzahaana, dǝrda kǝ shigahaatǝr dǝ patkara sǝɗav kwa nguɗǝs nǝ iin tǝ ngyilaanna.
\v 6 Kaa sagauw kǝ Yesu da vak Bitrus. Am Bitrus taa kǝ iina, “Yazhǝgǝla, kǝgh wa da bargwa shigahara?”
\v 7 Kaa ngugangug Yesu taakiya, “Agha sǝrga bi kǝ dǝgit ǝn ɓag nai ndakwan biya, agha da nǝghǝgaaka tǝ hala.”
\v 8 Aiyam Bitrus taa kǝ iina, “Maaya! agha tapna bi kǝ bargwa shigahar biya.” Kaa ngugarangug kǝ Yesu, amaa, “Ai ciya, akwama barankada biya, agha maay ǝmtaɗ dǝ kai biya.”
\v 9 Aiyam Bitrus taa kǝ iina, “Yazhigǝla, aa ɗuug kǝ shigahar kalti biya, baz dǝvvahara ard ghǝrara.”
\v 10 Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Akwama baraabarǝg nǝ uuda, baɗǝm nǝ vǝghaan ba cuwaɗaɗɗa. Madlai lambaan dǝ barg biya, bamma barda kǝ shigahaan kaltiya. Aɗaba am ba cuwaɗaɗɗa, bakǝvakwaha, ɗǝmaru biya.”
\v 11 Aɗaba sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ daddakwa da za langyiyaana, iinwa tag nǝ iin taakiya, “Kuram ɗǝm bi\x + \xo 13.11 \x* wa cuwaɗaɗ biya.”
\v 12 Ghyǝnnga ba nǝ iin bartǝr shiggahatǝra, kaa gwiya tsǝgwǝv kǝ sǝɗɗavaana, kaa gwiiya kǝ iin davak ndzǝggaanana. Kaa ndavǝtǝrndavǝg kǝ iina amaa, “Nǝghǝghamakanǝghǝg kǝ dǝgit ǝnna ɓagkur naiya?
\v 13 Am ɗaa kai dǝ dadda tsaga dǝgita, dlaɓa Yazhǝgǝla. Ba kalkalla, aɗaɓa ǝn band kwaha naiya.
\v 14 Ən Yazhǝgǝlaruwa ard Daddatsaga dǝgitaru tsauwa, barrankurdabarǝg kǝ shiga, kats kuram ndakwi barari am barrgarbarrǝg kǝ shig kǝ zaraabahaaruwa.
\v 15 Marankurdamarǝg kǝ garav kǝyavva ɓagaan kǝskuram band kwana ɓakura naiya.
\v 16 Bak jiijiira ǝn tagkurtaga, kwatnaha jigubi kǝ daddahǝnǝhya biya, zǝrɓǝllǝg dlaɓa jiguwi kǝ daddakwa ɓǝllǝgaan biya.
\v 17 Ndakwanna am asǝrgasǝrg tsau kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, akwaman ɓagaana am da dǝ barka.
\v 18 Ən tag tǝghǝr kǝsskuram ɗǝm biya. Ən sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ uudahi dzǝrantǝraaka naiya. Kwannǝn dlaɓa kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ dǝgit ma kakaɗa Dadamazhǝgǝla taakiya, ‘Daddakwa kǝm zaa kaf ǝmǝtaɗa nalnǝg kǝ tlǝghumara.’
\v 19 Ən tagkurtag ndakwana lakuti dzǝgaadzǝga, aɗaba ma da dzǝghaardzǝga, famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg taakiya ba kaiyina.
\v 20 Bak jiijiira ǝn tagkurtaga, daddakwa dlǝghadlǝg kǝ daddakwana ɓǝlgant nai bad rivǝɗmahuɗ palla, dlǝghaakwidlǝg kǝsskaiya. Dlaɓa daddakwa dlǝghaakwidlǝg kǝsskaiya dlǝghaadlǝg kǝ daddakwa ɓallakwadi kaiya.”
\s1 Za lanngyiya Yesu
\p 
\v 21 Tǝhala tagdataga Yesu kwanen kǝ ǝlbǝga, mbakǝnmbǝg ma ǝrivɗyana. Kaa tagaan kǝ iin bat ɓallaɓal taakiya, “Bak jiijiira, ǝn tagkurtaga, pallaruwa da vǝlkwavǝlǝga.”
\v 22 Kaa vazakǝv kǝ mbǝrzahaan mataatakaatǝra, aɗaba ar sǝrgai kǝ mbǝrzi tag nǝ Yesu kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr biya.
\v 23 Pal ma mbǝrzahaana, kwa waig nǝ iina, ndzǝgaan bahyǝf dǝ inna,
\v 24 Wiika am nǝ Bitrus dǝ dǝv taa kǝ mbǝrzǝna, ndavarundavǝg kǝ Yesu tag tǝghǝr kǝ warra.
\v 25 Kaa dǝngzharva kǝ mbǝrzǝn tǝvǝgh kǝ Yesu ndavaruwa amaa, “War wahiin, Yazhigǝli?”
\v 26 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Ən da hǝgaan kǝ ghudǝga bruudi damma taasa. Dadakwan da vǝlga naiya, iin nǝ uuda nǝ iina.” Kǝssghant ba nǝ Yesu kǝ ghudǝga bruudin hǝdǝmma, kaa vǝlla kǝ iin kǝ Yahuda zǝra siman Iskariyoti.
\v 27 Cauwa ba nǝ iin kǝ ghudǝga bruudi kaa dass kǝ shatanah dama vǝghaana bawatswatsa. Kaa am Yesu kǝ Yahuda, “Dǝginǝn aghanaa ɓag nǝngnaa ɓag bawatswatsa.”
\v 28 Maay ma lii za kafǝn wa nǝghǝghakanǝghǝg kǝ dǝgit tuuk vakaiy wa taghar nǝ Yesu kǝ iin biya.
\v 29 Yahuda tsau wa hǝkya ambǝlla kwaɓatǝra, kyǝlǝma mbǝrzaah tlatlar ba taakiya tagghar aa sǝgwasǝgw kǝ dǝgit naahaava kwakyarvad haarakǝssa nǝ Yesu, bi vǝllǝtǝr kǝ dǝgit kǝ talaggaha.
\v 30 Cauwa ba nǝ iin kǝ ghudǝga bruudina, kaa dagalaana. Masarta kwaha ndza avǝɗ vakka.
\s1 Dalla adzahadzaha
\p 
\v 31 Tǝhala kwa dagal Yahuda, am Yesu, “Aa fǝvvaara ndakwan nǝ Zǝr Uuda, dlaɓa faavaarafǝg nǝ Dadamazhǝgǝl tǝdǝvad iina.
\v 32 Akwama fǝvaarafǝg nǝ Dadamazhǝgǝl tǝdǝvad iina, Dadamazhǝgǝl da fǝgaarafǝg kǝ zǝraan bad ghǝraana, dlaɓa da fǝgaarafǝga bawatswatsa.
\p 
\v 33 “Kuram Zarhara, tǝmma bahǝɗiikǝn nǝ ndzǝgana ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kurama. Am da gatkwagatǝga, bandkwa tagantǝr nai kǝ yaa Yahud taakiya, ‘Ən tagkurtag bandakwanna, Vakavaki ǝn da dagal naiya am da sǝgǝv biya.’
\p 
\v 34 “Dalla adzahadzah wan vǝllǝkur naiya, waiyamwaig kǝ uuda. Bandkwan waiyankurǝt naiya, kuram ndakwi waiyamwaig kǝ uudaha.
\v 35 Tǝdǝvad kwamam waigaan kǝ uuda da sǝrǝggasǝrǝg aanji war taakiya am mbǝrzahaara.”
\s1 Da ɓalgaan nǝ Bitrus agajawa sǝrga bi kǝ Yesu.
\p 
\v 36 Ndavǝgharundavǝg Siman Bitrus kǝ Yesu amaa, “Yaazhigǝla, agha da dagal da vakwari?” Ngughaarangug nǝ Yesu amaa, “Ndakwana vakavaki ǝn da dagal naiya agha da gatkus biya, tǝhala agha da gatkusgatǝga.”
\v 37 Aiyam Bitrus taa kǝ iina, “Yazhigǝla, aujilbǝg ǝn gatkǝsi ndakwan biyi? Ən da vǝlgaan kǝ shifǝgar kwakyarvad kǝgha.”
\v 38 Aiyam nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Aaya, agha da vǝlgaan kǝ shifǝgagh kwakyarvad kaiya? Bak jiijiira, ǝn tagkataga, lakwti wiig ghwatkal agha da ɓalgaan kǝ agajauwa sǝrkwa bi shig hǝkǝrɗa.”
\c 14
\s1 Yesu nǝ ɗuula daa da vak Daada
\p 
\v 1 “Ndavǝm biya, famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ Dadamazhǝgǝla, dlaɓa famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya.
\v 2 Ma vǝgya Daadara mǝng nǝ vaka ndzǝgaan baɗyaka. Akwamaamaay ndkwaha biya manaa maay tagkurtag kwan biya. Ən dagal da vakwaha kwakyarvad ǝn ɓadlkurnan kǝ vakavaka.
\v 3 Akwama danǝt ɓadlankurnaɓadlǝg kǝ vaka, ǝn da saaya ǝn dǝkurda da vakara, aɗaba kuram ndakwi am ndzan vavaki dǝ kaiya.
\v 4 Ghǝravaru ndakwi am sǝrǝggasǝrǝg kǝ ɗuula daa da vakavaki ǝn dagal naiya.”
\v 5 Am Toma taa kǝ Yesu, “Yaazhigǝla, kǝm sǝrǝgai kǝ vavaki agha dagal nǝng biya, kǝm da sǝrga ndandar kaci kǝ ɗuuli?”
\v 6 Ngugharangug nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Kai ɗuula, kai jiira, kai dlaɓa ǝn shiifǝga. Maay wa dǝgaadǝg da vak Daada biya bamma tǝdǝvad kaiya.
\v 7 Akwama maa sǝrkwasǝrga, mammaa sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ Daadara. Ma ndakwanǝrna ndakwana am sǝrgasǝrǝga, dlaɓa nǝghǝghamakanǝghǝg kǝ iina.”
\v 8 Aiyam Filigus taa kǝ iina, “Yazhigǝla, akwama marghǝkǝmdadamarǝg kǝ Daadiina, tsǝghatsǝg kǝ puutamnda.”
\v 9 Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Zǝlanmazǝlmǝg ǝmtaɗ dǝ kurama, gwastǝn agha sǝrkwa bi Filibus biya? Baɗǝm daddakwa nǝghakwanǝghǝga, nǝghǝghanǝghǝg kǝ Daadiina. Agha tag ndarndar kaci, ‘Marwadamarǝg kǝ Daadiini’?
\v 10 Fǝghǝdǝghǝrǝt bi taakiya kai ǝn ma Daada, dlaɓa Daada ma kaiy biya? Əlbǝgahahaan ǝn tagkur naina dǝ ndzǝɗa ghǝrar biya, Daadǝn ndzǝga ma kai na iin wa ɓa tlǝrahaaana.
\v 11 Famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya masartǝn ǝn tag nai ǝn ma Daadna, Daadiin dlaɓ ma kaiya, aanji ba kwakyarvad tlǝraha japǝrǝn ǝn ɓag naiy na famdǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya.
\v 12 Bak jiijiir ǝn tagkurtaga, baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa fadǝghǝrǝtfǝg tǝ kaiya, da ɓagaan kǝ tlǝrahaan ǝn ɓag naiyna. Da ɓagaan baz kwa jujig kǝ kwannahaan kǝ tlǝraaha aɗaba ǝn daa da vak Daada.
\v 13 Baɗǝm nǝ dǝgiti am ghalǝg nǝ uuram ma ɗagara ǝn ɓagkurɓaga, aɗaba Daadina fǝvaaran tǝdǝvad Zǝra.
\v 14 Aanji aau wam ghallǝg nǝ uuram ma ɗagara, ǝn ɓagkurɓaga.
\s1 Langiya saaya shǝɗkwa Dadamazhigǝla
\p 
\v 15 “Akwama mam waikwawaiga, gatamgatǝg kǝ adzahadzahara.
\v 16 Ən da ghalgaan kǝ Daada, iin dlaɓa da vǝlkurvǝlǝg kǝ daddakwa da mǝlkurmǝlǝg ndzan ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kuram tangw damma zǝrazǝra.
\v 17 Iin shǝɗkwa jiijiira, kwa lawa duni kǝ tlǝghǝgaana aɗaba nǝghǝghǝga biya bi sǝrǝga kǝ iin biya. Kurama am sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ iina, aɗaba ndzǝga ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kurama, dlaɓa da ndzǝga ma ǝrivɗyaruwa.
\v 18 Ən ɗukurǝs bi ǝnd taaghah biya, ǝn da sagau sa vakaruwa.
\v 19 Gǝɗya ba sart hǝɗikǝna da madlai duni nǝghǝkwanǝghǝg biya, amaa kurama am da nǝghkwanǝghǝga. Aɗaba ǝn dǝshiifǝga, kuram dlaɓa am da bad shiifǝga.
\v 20 Daghuvala kwaniin kǝ faci wam da sǝrga nǝ uuram taakiya kaiya ǝn ma Daad, kuram dlaɓa am ma kaiya, kaiya dlaɓa ǝn ma kurama.
\v 21 Baɗǝm nǝ dadakwa sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ adzahadzahara, dlaɓa gatǝgaana, iin wa waiya kaiya. Daddakwa waikwawaiga dlaɓa, Daadara da waiyǝgaan kǝ iina, kaiy dlaɓa ǝn da waigaan kǝ iina ǝn marda kǝ ghǝrar vakana.”
\v 22 Am Yahud taa kǝ iina, kwa Yahuda Iskariyoti biya, “Yazhigǝla, aaujilǝbǝg da mara ghǝragh vakamǝnd, kwal margar kǝ duuniyi?”
\v 23 Kaa ngugwarangug kǝ Yesu amaa taa kǝ iina, “Baɗǝm nǝ daddakwa waikwawaiga, da tsuufǝgaan kǝ ǝlbǝgara, Daada dlaɓa da waiyǝgaan kǝ iina, kǝm da sagau saa vakana kǝm ndzan ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ iina.
\v 24 Daddakwa maay waiya kaiy biya, maay tsuufa ǝlbǝgar biya. Əlbǝgǝn am cinng nǝ uuramǝna dǝgar biya, dǝga Daddakwa ɓǝlakwadi kaiya.
\v 25 Tagankurdatag kwanahaan kǝ digitah bama sartǝn ndzan ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kurama.
\v 26 Dadda mǝlgaru kǝ uuda, Shǝɗkw Daadamazhigǝla, kwa da ɓǝllǝg nǝ Daada ma ɗagara, iin wa da tsakur dǝgit baɗǝma, dlaɓa da dzamkurǝs baɗǝm kǝ dǝgit tangaankurda naiya.
\v 27 Gabǝrǝr wanaa ɗukurǝs naiya, vǝllankurvǝllǝg kǝ gabǝrara. Ənna vǝllǝkur ndǝkwa vǝllǝkur nǝ duni biya. Ndavambiya, dlaɓa gǝdzam biya.
\v 28 Cinngamacinng nǝ uuram kǝskai taakiya ǝn dagata, ǝn da gwiiya saay da vakaru dlaɓa. Akwamamma waikwawaig mamma dlaig kwakyarvad ǝn daddavak Daada, aɗaba Daadara jakwarajiga.
\v 29 Ndakwanna tagankurdataga lauti da dzǝgardzǝga, aɗaba mada dzǝghaardzǝga famdǝghǝrǝtfǝga.
\v 30 Ən da madlai gwiiya taaghaiy ɗyak biya, aɗaba dadda kwara duunina sagauwa, maay dǝ ndzǝɗ tǝghǝr kǝskai biya.
\v 31 Ən ɓa dǝgit ba kalkal kwa taghwa Daada ǝn ɓagaan aɗaba sǝran nǝ duni taakiya ǝn waigaan kǝ Daada. Ciiyamciiga ɗuyamantɗug kǝ vavakǝna.”
\c 15
\s1 Yesu nǝ vizhvizha uuffa inabi
\p 
\v 1 Kaiy nǝ gyigyiya uuffa inabi, Daadar dlaɓa iin dadda uusǝga.
\v 2 Aanji kwar kǝ dǝv uuf tǝ kai kwa maay yaa zǝr biya, ghudarsa. Aanji kwar kǝ dǝva uuf kwa yaayig kǝ zǝra gwiya ɓadlav kiyavva gwiya yigaan kǝ zǝr baɗyaka.
\v 3 Aanji bandakwan am ba cǝwaɗaɗa kwakyarvad ǝlbǝgǝn tagaankurda naina.
\v 4 Ndzamandzǝg ma kaiya, kai dlaɓa ma kurama. Bandkwa yiga bi nǝ dǝva uufa inabi kǝ zǝr dǝ ghǝran biya, bamma ndzǝga tǝ uuffa inabi, ghǝravaru ndakwi bandkwah am yiga bi kǝ zǝr biya, ba mam ndzǝga tǝ kaiya.
\v 5 Kai ǝn uuffa inabi, kuram nǝ dǝvvahana. Daddakwa ndzǝga ma kaiya, kai dlaɓa ma iina, iin wa da ya zǝr baɗyaka. Aɗaba mam maay ǝmtaɗ dǝ kai biya, am ɓaga bi aanji ndau biya.
\v 6 Baɗǝm daddakwa ndza bi ma kaiy biya, band dǝva uuf kwa ɓǝlavdan ghulal, hulfakwah kǝ dǝva uufa dzaavanta ɗiivǝdǝm damma kaara, dlaɓa zuu.
\v 7 Ma ndzamandzǝg ma kaiya, ǝlbǝgar dlaɓa ndzandzǝg ma kurama, am da ghalǝgaan baɗǝm kǝ dǝgit am naag nǝ uurama, am da tlǝkǝnatlǝga.
\v 8 Ndzamandzǝg dǝ hǝnkala marawa kwada mardamarǝg taakiya kuram am mbǝrzahaara, band uuff kwa ya zarh marawa, aɗaba kwannahaan wa fǝgaara Daadara.
\v 9 Bandkwa waiyakut nǝ Daada, ǝn waiykur band kwah dlaɓa naiya. Ndzamandzǝg ma waiyavǝr bandkwa marankur da naiya.
\v 10 Kaiya fanaarafǝg kǝ adzahadzaha Daadara, dlaɓa ǝn ndzǝga ma waiyavaana. Bandkwah dlaɓa, akwamamam fǝgaarafǝg kǝ adzahadzara am ndzǝga ma waiyavara.
\p 
\v 11 “Tagkurdatag kǝ kwanna kwakyarvad dlaig ǝrviɗmahuɗara aa ndzandzǝg ma kurama, dlaiga ǝrivɗmahuɗaru dlaɓa aandz ba righǝgharighana.
\v 12 Kwanǝn iin na adzahadzahara, waiyamwaiyig kǝ zaraabahagh band kwa waiyankurǝt naiya.
\v 13 Maay nǝ waiyavi jujig kǝ kwanǝn biya, taaki uuda vǝllada kǝ shiifǝgaan kwakyarvad tsaghwaana.
\v 14 Am tsaghwahahara akwama ɓagaan kǝ dǝgit tag naiya taakiya ɓagamɓaga.
\v 15 Ən madlaiy gwiiya ɗakurɗag dǝ kwatanah biya, aɗaba kwatǝnaha sǝrǝgai kǝ dǝgiti ɓag nǝ daada biya. Dlakulǝva kwaha ǝn ɗakur dǝ tsaghwahaha aɗaba tagaankurtag kǝ dǝgiti cinngana naiy baɗǝm vak Daadara.
\v 16 Kurambi wa kǝssamkwakǝssǝg biya, kai wa kǝssankuraakǝsǝga ǝn fankura kǝ dagal da yaa zǝr maraw kwa da zǝlmazǝlmǝga. Tǝhala kwaha da vǝllǝkurvǝllǝg Daad kǝ dǝgiti am ghalga nǝ uuram ma ɗagaan baɗǝmma.
\v 17 Kwanna iin nǝ adzhadzahara waiyamwaig kǝ zaraabaha.
\s1 Duni naa bi kǝ mbǝrzah biya
\p 
\v 18 “Akwama ɗuwakursɗuug duniya, sǝramasǝrǝg taakiya ɗuwakwi kaiya lauti ɗuwa kurama.
\v 19 Akwamamma dǝga Duniya, duni ma waigaan kǝ dǝgaana, aɗaba am dǝga duni biya, dlaɓa kǝsankurakakǝsǝg ma duniya, iin wa nǝ iin ɗuuwakursɗug duniya.
\v 20 Dzamamdzamǝg kǝ ǝlbǝgahi tangankur naiya, ‘Kwatǝnah jigu bi kǝ dadda hǝnnyahaan biya.’ Akwama mbarkwambǝga, kuram ndakwi arda mbkurmbǝga. Akwama faraarafǝg kǝ tsagaanara, ar da fǝgaarafǝg kǝ ǝlbǝgaru dlaɓa.
\v 21 Ar da ɓagkurɓag kǝ kwanahaana kǝ dǝgit baɗǝmma kwakyarvad ɗaagara, aɗaba ar sǝrǝga bi kǝ dadakwa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝlǝg biya.
\v 22 Akwama ndza sanhi bi ǝn tagtǝr kǝ ǝlbǝg biya, maraa ndzaa maay dǝ haip biya. Amaa ndakwanna, am maay dǝ ɗuula kyavaɗǝgv tǝghǝr kǝ haipahaatǝr biya.
\v 23 Daddakwa ɗuwakwiɗuuga ɗuugharsɗug kǝ baz Daadara.
\v 24 Bagannaɓag kǝ tlǝrah baɗyak ma iitǝra maay daddakwa tapghanitapǝg kǝ ɓagaan biya. Akwama ndza ɓaganna bi kǝ tlǝrahaan biya, maraa ndza maay dǝ haip biya. Ndakwanna nǝghǝghaaranǝghǝg kǝ dǝgit ǝn ɓaga naiya, bakǝva kwaha ɗuuwarkwiɗuga, dlaɓa ɗuuranɗug kǝ Daadara.
\v 25 Dzǝghardzǝg wanǝn kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ ǝlbǝgǝn viindavan ma adzahadzah taakiya, ɗuuwarkwiɗug bagyaana.
\v 26 Mada sǝghawisǝg nǝ dadda mǝlkurmǝlǝga kwan da mǝllǝg naiya davakruwa vak daada, shǝɗkwa jiira, kwa sagal vak daada iin wa da ɓa shiid tǝghǝr kǝskaiya.
\v 27 Kuram ndakwi am shiidaha, aɗaba bama daa zǝnngwa am ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kaiya.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 “Tagaankurtag kǝ kwanahaan kǝ dǝgitah baɗǝma haik da mɓǝg kǝskuram ma fadghǝraruwa.
\v 2 Ar da lagwkurlagw sagal ma guda dzahavaha. Bak jijirra sagau nǝ sarta baɗǝm daddakwa tsa kurama da tlatlǝgaan taakiya ǝn ɓa kwatǝnahǝr kǝ Dadamzhigǝla.
\v 3 Ar da ɓagkurɓag nǝ nndah kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitah aɗaɓa ar sǝrǝgai kǝ Daada bi kaiya biya.
\v 4 Tagankurdatag kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, aɗaba mada ɓagaɓag nǝ sarta, am da dzamnan taakiya tagankurdataga. Tagaankurdai kwan ma daa zǝngw biya aɗaba ndzan ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kurama.
\s1 Tlǝra shiɗkwa Daadamazhigǝla
\p 
\v 5 “Amaa ndakwanna ǝn dagat davak daddakwa ɓǝlakwadiɓǝlga. Bakǝvakwaha ma kurama maay nǝ daddakwa ndavghwadndavǝg taakiya, ‘Agha dagal da vakwar biya?’
\v 6 Aɗaba naa tagankurdatag kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, kaa badzaǝrivǝɗ kǝskurama.
\v 7 Bak jiir wan tagkur naiya, daasar wa maraw kǝsskurama, aɗaba ma danagha biya, maay da saay nǝ dadda kwada mǝlkurumelgǝn biya. Akwama danaghana ǝn da ɓǝllǝgaan saavakaruwa.
\v 8 Mada sǝghawisǝg nǝ dadda mǝlkurmǝlǝgna, da margarmarǝg kǝ duni taakiya kalkal bi nǝ dzamaghǝraatǝr tǝghǝr kǝ haip, jira, ard tǝghǝr sharriya.
\v 9 Dzamaghǝraatǝr tǝghǝr kǝ haipa kalkal biya aɗaba larwalǝg kǝ fadǝghǝr tǝ kaiya.
\v 10 Dzamaghǝraatǝra kalkal bi tǝghǝr kǝ jir biya, aɗaba ǝn daa da vak Daadara, dlaɓa am da madlai gwiiya nǝghǝghkwanǝghǝg biya.
\v 11 Dzamaghǝraatǝr tǝghǝr kǝ sharriya, aɗaba ɓagavaraɓag nǝ sharri kǝ dada kwarra kwan kǝ duni bawurra.
\v 12 Mǝng nǝ dǝgitah ǝn naa tagkur nai baɗyak ndana, am da dzǝgwanti ndakwan biya.
\v 13 Mada sǝghawisǝg nǝ shiɗkwa jijiira, da mǝlkurumǝlǝg baɗǝm ma jiira, aɗaba da taa ǝlbǝga ghǝraan biya, da taa ba dǝgita aa ciingga nǝ iin kaltiya, dlaɓa da tagkurtag kǝ dǝgitah da dzǝgaaradzǝga.
\v 14 Da fǝkwarafǝg kǝskaiya, aɗaba da dlǝghgaan kǝ ǝlbǝgara dlaɓa da tagkur kǝskurama.
\v 15 Baɗǝm nǝ digiti dǝvakai nǝ Daada ba dǝgara, kwakyarvad kwah wanaa tag nai da dlǝghgaan nǝ shǝɗkw vakara da markurdana.
\s1 Badzǝg ǝrviɗmahuɗa da nǝg kǝ dlaiga
\p 
\v 16 “Tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝna am da madlaiy nǝghkwanǝghǝg biya, tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝn dlaɓa am da nǝghkwanǝghǝga.”
\v 17 Am kyǝlǝma mbǝrzah taa kǝ ghǝrahaatǝra, “Au nǝ dǝgiti tuuk vakai wa tag nǝ iin, ‘Tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝn am da madlai nǝghǝghkwanǝghǝg biya, tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝn dlaɓa am da gwiiya nǝghǝghkwanǝghǝgi?’ Dlaɓa au wa tlatlǝg nǝ iin dǝ taakiya, ‘Aɗaba ǝn daa da vak Daadarni’?”
\v 18 Kaa zavukw kǝ iitǝr dǝ ndavǝg taakiya, “Aauw wa tlatlǝg nǝ iin dǝ taakiya, ‘tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝni’? Kiyam sǝrgai kǝ dǝgit tlatlǝg nǝ iin biya.”
\v 19 Sǝrghaakasǝrǝg Yesu taakiya ar naa ndavagarundavǝg mbǝrzahaan tǝghǝr kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Am ndavǝgaru kǝ ghǝraharu kǝ dǝgiti ǝn tlatlǝg nai dǝ taakiya, ‘Tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝna am da nǝghǝghkwa biya, tǝhala sart hǝɗikǝn dlaɓa am da nǝghǝghkwanǝghǝga’?
\v 20 Bak jiijiira ǝn tagkurtaga, sarti am da tuug dǝ badzǝga ǝrivǝɗmahuɗna, iin sarti da dlaig nǝ duniya, badzǝga ǝrivǝɗmahuɗaruwa da nǝg kǝ dlaiga.
\v 21 Akwama tsugwgharaatsug kungula yiig kǝ uusa mbǝkǝnmbǝg nǝ dlaɗ ba vaivaiya, aɗaba sart yigaan ɓagaaɓaga. Ma yaayig kǝ zǝra, kaa vigaraaviig kǝ dlaɗan aa mbakǝnmbǝgǝna aɗaba dlaiga kwakyarvad yaayig kǝ zǝr sama duniya.
\v 22 Bandkwaha vakaruwa. Ndakwana am badzǝga ǝrivǝɗa, amaa am da gwiya nǝghǝkwanǝghǝga dlaɓa tǝhala kwaha am da dlaiga, maay wa da kǝskurvakǝssǝg kǝ dlaigaru biya.
\v 23 Ma kwahiin kǝ sarta kwahiina am da maay ghalgaan aanji ndau vakar biya. Bak jiir ǝn tagkurtaga, Daada da vǝllǝkurvǝllǝg baɗǝm kǝ dǝgit am ghallǝga nǝ uuram ma ɗagaara.
\v 24 Gwasǝtaan ghalamai aanji ndauw ma ɗagara biya. Ghalamghalǝga, am da tlǝkǝnatlǝga, aɗaba dlaigaruwa aandz ba righǝgharighaana.”
\s1 Zanuzǝg kǝ fiir tǝghǝr kǝ duniya
\p 
\v 25 “Aanji tagankur bad ǝlbǝg dǝghur kǝ ǝlbǝga. Da sagau nǝ sarta kwan da madlaiy batlǝr dǝ hulfa kǝ ghaiy biya. Dlakulǝva kwaha, ǝn da tagkurtag bat Ballaɓala tǝghǝr kǝ daadara.
\v 26 Ma kwahiina kǝ am da ghalǝg ma ɗaagara. Kai bi wada ghallǝgaan kǝ Daada ma guufkaru biya.
\v 27 Aɗaba Daadiin dǝ ghǝraana waiyakurwaiyga, kwakyarvad waiyamkutwaiyǝg kǝskaya, dlaɓa famdǝghǝrǝtfǝga taakiya sanhi vak Dadamazhǝgǝl naiya.
\v 28 Sanhi vak Daadiin naiya, dlaɓa sanhisǝg sama duniya, ndakwan dlaɓa ǝn ɗuugaan kǝ duniya ǝn gwiiya daddavak Daddina.”
\v 29 Aiyam mbǝrzahaana, ndakwan wagha tag nǝng kǝ tsalal ǝlbǝg bat ɓallaɓalla maay dǝ ǝlbǝg dǝghur biya.
\v 30 Ndakwana nǝghamndakanǝghǝg taakiya agha sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ dǝgitah baɗǝma. Agha sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ ngugǝg ba kalkal lakwati ndavakndavǝg kǝ uuda. Kwanǝn waa fakǝmndafǝg kǝ fadǝghǝr taakiya sǝghi vak Daadamazhigǝla.”
\v 31 Kaa Nguwatǝrangug nǝ Yesu taakiya, “Kats! famdghǝrǝtfǝg ndakwanna?
\v 32 Sagau nǝ sarta, bak jirra ɓagaaɓaga kwamda kwazǝg nǝ uuram aanji kwararu da ǝmdrǝg daa da vǝgyaana am da ɗuukus kǝskai ba daavara. Bakǝvakwaha ǝn davar biya, aɗaba ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kai nǝ Daada.
\v 33 Tagaankurdatag kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitah, aɗaba ma kaiya am tlǝkǝna kǝ gabǝrǝra. Mahuɗa duuninna hǝbamuhǝɓǝg kǝ dlaɗa, ndzamandzǝg dǝ fǝrivǝɗ mahuɗa aɗaba zaanuzǝg kǝ firr tǝghǝr kǝ duniya.”
\c 17
\s1 Dzugharadzug Yesu kǝ zhigǝl kǝ ghǝraana
\p 
\v 1 Tǝhala kwa tagada Yesu kǝ kwannahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, kaa dzǝgant kǝ ghǝraan daa kǝ ghǝrazhigǝl dzǝgwa kǝ zhigǝla amaa, “Daada, ɓagaaɓag sarta. Faarafǝg kǝ Zǝragh kwakyarvad iin ndakwi fǝkaarana.
\v 2 Kwakyarvad vǝlghavǝlǝg kǝ ndzǝɗ kǝ Zǝr tǝghǝr kǝ uudah baɗǝmma, aɗaba vǝlda kǝ shiifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝra kǝ lii vǝllǝgha nǝnga.
\v 3 Shiifǝga tangw damma zǝrazǝra iin taakiya, sǝrak nǝ uudaha, kǝgh Daadamazhigǝla jiira palba nǝnnga, dlaɓa ar sǝran kǝ Yesu Tlǝkatǝga kwa ɓǝlghǝdi nǝnnga.
\v 4 Fankaarafǝg ma duniya ghyinganaghyǝng tsau kǝ tlǝr vǝlghwa nǝnnga kǝ ɓagaana.
\v 5 Ndakwan ciya, fǝkwaraafǝg Daada dǝ ndangǝri ndzan dǝ dǝvakaiy nai vakagh lakwti fǝvarzhafǝg nǝ duniya.
\s1 Dzugwatǝraadzugw nǝ Yesu kǝ zhigǝl kǝ mbǝrzahaana
\p 
\v 6 Marankadamarǝg vak lii vǝlghwa nǝng ma duniya. Ba gwil wur ndzar ba dǝgagha, vǝlghwavǝlǝg nǝnng kǝ iitǝra, dlaɓa fararfǝg kǝ ǝlbǝgagha.
\v 7 Ndakwana ar sǝrǝggasǝrǝg taakiya baɗǝm nǝ dǝgit vǝlghwa nǝngga sǝghal vak agha.
\v 8 Kwakyarvad ǝlbǝgahaan tagghwa nǝngǝna tagantǝrtaga, dlaɓa dlǝgharadlǝga. Sǝraraakasǝrǝg bak jiijiira sanhi vakagha, dlaɓa fardǝghǝrǝtfǝg bakǝgh pal wa ɓǝlghkwadiɓǝlǝga.
\v 9 Ən dzǝgwazhǝgǝl kwakyarvad iitǝra. Kwakyarvad uudaha duni biya, amaa kwakyarvad uudahi vǝllǝghwa nǝnnga, aɗaba ar dǝgha.
\v 10 Baɗǝm nǝ dǝgit ǝn dǝvakai naiya ba dǝgagha, dlaɓa baɗǝm nǝ dǝgit agha dǝvakai nǝnnga dǝgara. Dlaɓa maravdamarǝg nǝ ndangǝrara tǝdǝvad iitǝra.
\v 11 Ndakwana ǝn da madlai ndzǝga ma duni biya, amma iitǝra ar bamma duniya, kai dlaɓa ǝn daas da vakagha. Daad Caccuwanacaccuwananna, katǝrkatǝg tǝdvad ndzǝɗa ɗaagagha, ɗaaga kwa vǝllǝghwa nǝngga, aɗaba ar nal kǝ palla, band kwa ki pal nǝmi dǝ kǝgha.
\v 12 Ma sartǝn ndzan ǝmtaɗ dǝ iitǝra, katanrǝtkatǝg dǝ ndzǝɗa ɗaagagha, ɗaagǝn kwa vǝlghwa nǝngna. Katantrǝtkatǝga, maay wa zaazǝg aanji pal biya, ba kwapakǝna, aɗaba righǝvant nǝ ǝlbǝga Daadamazhigǝl viindaviinda.
\v 13 Ndakwana ǝn daa da vakagha. Amaa ǝn ghala kwanǝn kǝ dǝgitah bamma sarti ǝn ba ndzǝgaan ma duniya kiyava righǝgh kǝ hwaɗagar ba vaivai ma ǝrivɗmahuɗaruwa.
\v 14 Tagaantǝrdatag kǝ ǝlbǝgha. Gwiyatǝrdagwig duni kǝ ilga, aɗaba ar dǝga duni biya, bandkwa kwan ǝn dǝga duni bi nai biya.
\v 15 Ghalgaara iin bi taakiya agha hutsǝtǝrda dagal ma duuniyin biya, amaa ǝn ghalgara iin taakiya magha katǝrǝt vak tlǝkǝlaadǝna.
\v 16 Iitǝra ar dǝga duni biya, bandkwa kai ndakwi ǝn dǝga duni biya.
\v 17 Pǝshtǝrapǝshig tǝdǝvad jiira, aɗaba ǝlbǝgaha iin jiira.
\v 18 Bǝlantǝrǝtɓǝlǝg damma duniya, bandkwa ɓǝlghkwadi nǝng kǝskaiya.
\v 19 Ən pǝshig kwakyarvad iitǝra kǝ ghǝrara, aɗaba iitǝr ndakwi pǝshivtǝra bak jiira.”
\s1 Dzugwadzug w Yesu kǝ zhigǝl kwakyarvad lii fadghǝr baɗǝmma
\p 
\v 20 “Ghalgara kwakyarvad iitǝr kalti biya. Ən dzǝgwazhigǝl dlaɓa kwakyarvad lii fadǝghǝr tǝ kaiya tǝdǝvad ǝlbǝgaatǝra.
\v 21 Aɗaba baɗǝmaatǝra maraa nal kǝ palla, bandkwa agha ma kai nǝnga, kai dlaɓa ǝn ma kǝgha, ǝn ghalga iitǝr ndakwi maraa ndza ma kǝmiya, kwakyarvad uudaha duniya ar fǝdǝghǝrǝta taakiya kǝgh wa ɓǝlghkwadibǝlga.
\v 22 Kaiya vǝllantǝrvǝllǝg kǝ uudah kǝ ndangǝr kwa vǝllǝghwa nǝngga, aɗaba ar nal kǝ pal band kwakǝyi pal nǝmiya.
\v 23 Kai ma iitǝra, kǝgh dlaɓa ma kaiya, aɗaba ar nal kǝ pal ba vaivaiya, aɗaba sǝran nǝ duni taakiya kǝgh wa ɓǝlghkwadiɓǝlga, dlaɓa ar sǝran waightǝrantwaiga bandkwa waighkut nǝnnga.
\p 
\v 24 “Daada, manaa naagaan maraa ndza nǝ uudahaan vǝlghwa nǝnngǝn ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kai vakavaki dǝ kaiya, ǝn naagaan maraa nǝgha kǝ ndangǝragha, kwa vǝlghwa nǝnnga kwakyarvad agha waikwawaig lakwati virɗyav duniya.
\v 25 Daada, dadda jirra, uudaha duniya ar sǝrak biya, kaiya ǝn sǝraksǝrǝga, kwanǝn kǝ uudah dlaɓa ar sǝrǝgasǝrǝg taakiya kǝgh wa ɓǝlkwadiɓǝlǝga.
\v 26 Marantǝrdamarǝg kǝ ɗagagha, dlaɓa ǝn da zaavukw dǝ maratǝrmaraga, kwakyarvad waiyav kwa agha ɓagwa nǝng aa ndzan ma iitǝra, kai dlaɓa ǝn ndza ma iitǝra.”
\c 18
\s1 Viyavǝtviig Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Ghyǝnga ba Yesu dzǝgwazhigǝla, kaa dzǝva dlara Kidron kǝ iin ǝmtaɗ dǝ mbǝrazahaan da tǝ kwah ghyaba. Gyilga dlariina ndza mǝng ɗyaghaara guuha, kaa daas kǝ iin ǝmtaɗ dǝ mbǝrzahaan damma vakaiya.
\v 2 Sǝrgasǝrǝg Yahud kwa vǝlǝt Yesu kwahiin kǝ vakavaka, aɗaba nǝtnǝg Yesu kǝ dzahav dǝ mbǝrzahaan vakwahiina.
\v 3 Kaa sagau kǝ Yahud dǝ dakwala tlauja ard lii uufakyawa Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl kwa ɓǝlartǝrǝt mallaha zhiilakǝsuufah ard Farisiyaha, kaa dagal kǝ iitǝr damma ɗyaghaara guhiina, ar hakyahakya dǝ kaara jahuramba, ard zadah ard kadlanga ghwaava.
\v 4 Sǝrgasǝrg tsau Yesu kǝ dǝgitahi da dzǝgaar dǝ iin baɗǝmma, kaa sagal kǝ iina, amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “War wam gatǝg nǝ uurami?”
\p 
\v 5 Kaa ngwangug kǝ iitǝr, taakiya, “Yesu zhiila Nazaret.”
\p Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Kai nǝ iina.”
\p (Yahuda kwa vǝlǝt Yesu ndakwi ghacǝga ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ iitǝra.)
\v 6 Tagatǝr ba Yesu taakiya, “Kai nǝ iina,” kaa hazha da tǝ hal kǝ iitǝra, ar mɓǝɗa da tǝ haaya.
\v 7 Kaa gwiya ndavǝtǝrundavǝg Yesu, amaa, “Am gata wari?”
\p Aiyam nǝ iitǝr taa kǝ iina, “Yesu zhiila Nazareta.”
\p 
\v 8 Kaa ngugangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Ən naa ndza tagkurtag taakiya, ba kai nǝ iina. Akwamam gata ba kaiya, ɗuwamtǝrǝsɗug kǝ uudahaan dagala.”
\v 9 Dzǝghaar kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ ǝlbǝgi tagada Yesu taakiya, “Ma uudahaan vǝlǝghwa nǝnngna, maay wa zaazǝg aanji pall biya.”
\p 
\v 10 Siman Bitrus kwa ndza dǝ katsakara, tǝɗadatǝɗǝg kǝ katsakar ghudarda kǝ hyimiya dǝvakaf kǝ kwatǝnaha maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufaha. Ɗaaga kwanǝn kǝ kwatǝnaha Malkus.
\v 11 Am Yesu taa kǝ Bitrusa, “Gwidaagwig kǝ katsakaragh damma kumbǝghaana. Ən maay da hǝɓǝgaan ma kuwǝn kwa vǝlǝghwa Daad ǝn hǝɓu biya?”
\p 
\v 12 Kaa vigǝtviig dakwala tlauja ard tlǝvukwatǝra, ard lii uufakyawa Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla Yahudah kǝ Yesu, ar nguɗǝnana.
\v 13 Kaa lanngaan kǝ iitǝr ba zunngw da vak Hannana, dadda uusa Kayafa. Kayafa wa ndza maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufah ma kwahiin kǝ viiga.
\v 14 Kayafa wa ɗiyatǝra sawari kǝ Yahudah taakiya, ngulǝm ǝmǝtsa nǝ uud pall dlakulva kyalǝma uudaha.
\s1 Ɓalaaɓalǝg Bitrus kǝ agajauwa sǝra Yesu
\p 
\v 15 Kaa gata Yesu kǝ Siman Bitrus ard kwatlǝrǝn kǝ mbǝrz tǝ halaa. Kwanǝn kǝ mbǝrza, sǝrǝgasǝrǝg maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufahǝn kǝ iina, kaa daas kǝ iin damma huɗa gaagazaiya vǝgya maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufahǝn ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ Yesu.
\v 16 Kaa ghacǝgaghacǝg kǝ Bitrus tǝ ghaiya wakyagha. Kaa gwiya sagal kǝ mbǝrzǝn kwa sǝrǝgasǝrǝg maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufahǝn da taa ghai dǝ dǝghwa hǝnyaha zhiilakǝsuufǝn tǝ ghaiya wakyagha, tǝhala kwaha, sǝdaa kǝ Bitrusa.
\v 17 Aiyam nǝ dǝghwǝn uufa wakyaghǝn kǝ Bitrusa, “Agha maay kwan nǝnng pall ma mbǝrzaha uudanǝn biya?”
\p Ngwangug nǝ Bitrus amaa, “Ən maay ma iitǝr biya.”
\p 
\v 18 Ndza akuhy vakka, kaa mbiigantmbiig kǝ kwatǝnahah ard lii uufakyawa kǝ kaara ghuvǝr ar ghacaraan ar cinnga hurfakaana, Bitrus ndakwi ndza ghacǝgan ǝmtaɗ dǝ iitǝra.
\s1 Ndavǝgharundavǝg maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufah kǝ Yesu kǝ ndavǝgaha
\p 
\v 19 Kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufah kǝ Yesu tǝghǝr kǝ mbǝrzahaana ard tsagaanana.
\v 20 Kaa ngughwarangug Yesu taakiya, “Tagandatag kǝ ǝlbǝg ba tǝ ɓalaɓal tǝvukwa uudah baɗǝmma, dlaɓa tlakwatlǝg tsagaan ma guda dzahavaha ard Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝla, vakavaki dzahavǝt Yahudah baɗǝmma. Tappana bi kǝ taa dǝgiti shǝɓashǝɓan biya.
\v 21 Iyau, agha ndavǝgwa da ɓaw kaci kǝ ndavǝgahi? Ba agha ndavtǝru kǝ lii cinngaracinng kǝ dǝgiti tagantǝr nai kǝ ndavgahaana, aɗaba ar sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ dǝgiti taganda naiya.”
\p 
\v 22 Tagada ba Yesu kǝ kwaha, kaa tsǝgaan kǝ pall ma lii uufakyau kwa ghacǝganǝn dǝ mahupeng kǝ Yesu, amaa, “Agha ngugugar ndkwan kǝ maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufaha?”
\v 23 Kaa ngwangug kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Akwama mǝng dǝgiti kwa naa tagǝda nai ghwaɗa, marwadamarǝg kǝ ghwaɗǝraana. Akwama ba jiir nǝ dǝgiti naa tagda naiya, aujilbǝg kaci agha tsa kaiyi?”
\p 
\v 24 Kaa ɓǝlgantɓǝlǝg Hannana kǝ uudah dagal dǝ Yesu nguɗanguɗan da vak Kayaf maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufaha.
\s1 Gwiya ɓalaaɓalǝg Bitrus kǝ agajauwa sǝra Yesu
\p 
\v 25 Gwastaan ba ndzǝganaan Bitrus ba ghacǝga vakwah tǝghǝr kǝ kaara cinnga hurǝfaka. Kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg kǝ kyalmah taakiya, “Aayaa, agha maay nǝnng kwan pall ma mbǝrzahaan biya?”
\p Kaa ɓala gajau kǝ Bitrus amaa, “Ən maay ma iiter biya.”
\p 
\v 26 Am pall ma kwatǝnaha maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufaha. Yiiga kwa ghudǝgharda Bitrus kǝ hyimi na, amaa taa kǝ Bitrusa, “Mbats nǝghankak bi ǝmtaɗ dǝ iin ma guhiin kwan biya?”
\p 
\v 27 Kaa gwiya ɓala gajau kǝ Bitrusa. Tǝhala kwaha, kaa wiig kǝ ghwatkala.
\s1 Yesu tǝvuukwa gumna Bilatusa
\p 
\v 28 Kaa sǝdasǝg kǝ tlǝvuukwa Yahudah kǝ Yesu sagal ma vǝgya Kayafa da vǝgya gumǝna Roma. Ma sartǝn lanngar nǝ iitǝrna, cagaacag nǝ kǝsa. Kaa lǝwalǝg kǝ iitǝr daa damma huɗa gaagazaiya, hai kǝ ndzǝgana kwadlambǝr kǝ iitǝr tǝvuukwa Daadamazhigǝl kwa da tsava iitǝr kǝ zaa kafa hwaɗaga haarakǝsa dzava hǝnnyaha.
\v 29 Mbakyarvad kwaha, kaa sǝgalsǝg kǝ Bilatus saa vakaatǝr gyimala, amaa, “Hulfa kwar kǝ ɗiya ghunj wa maa sǝdǝv nǝ uuram tǝghǝr kǝ kwan kǝ uudi?”
\p 
\v 30 Kaa ngugwangug kǝ iitǝr taakiya, “Akwama dadda haip bi nǝ iin biya, ma kǝmnda maay lanngaan saa vakagh biya.”
\p 
\v 31 Am Bilatus taa kǝ iitǝra, “Lanngamlanng dagal ba dǝ ghǝraruwa, am ghudarda kǝ sharri kalkal dǝ adzahadzaharuwa.”
\p Aiyam Yahudah taa kǝ iina, “Vǝlakǝmnd bi nǝ uud kǝ ndzǝɗa ghudǝgarda tsa shifǝg kǝ uud biya.”
\v 32 Dzǝghaar kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ ǝlbǝgi tagada Yesu tǝghǝr kǝ hulfa ǝmtsǝgi da ǝmtsǝg nǝ iina.)
\p 
\v 33 Kaa gwiya daas kǝ Bilatus daa damma gaagazaiya tlǝkǝsa, tǝhala kwaha kaa ɗagantɗaag kǝ iin kǝ Yesu ndavaru amaa, “Kǝgh Tlǝkǝsa yaa Yahuda?”
\p 
\v 34 Kaa ngugwarangug Yesu amaa, “Kwan kǝ ndavǝg aa sǝgal ma ghǝragh nii, uudahi tlǝrn ha wa tagakaktag kǝ ǝlbǝg tǝghǝr kǝskaiyi?”
\p 
\v 35 Kaa ngungangug Bilatus amaa, “Ən zhiila Yahudah naiya? Sarkadǝv zarabahagh Yahudah ard maal ba tingting ma zhiilakǝsuufah saa vakara. Au waghaa ɓaga nǝnngi?”
\p 
\v 36 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Tlǝkǝsǝrara dǝga kwan kǝ duni biya. Akwama dǝga kwan kǝ duni tlǝkǝsǝrara, maraa ɓagaan kwatǝnahar kǝ ghwaav maa hai kǝ vikwaviig kǝ Yahudaha. Amma tlǝkǝsǝrar vakavaki tlǝrna.”
\p 
\v 37 Aiyam Bilatus taa kǝ iina, “Kats agha tlǝkǝsa?”
\p Kaa ngugwarangug kǝ Yesu amaa, “Kǝgh dǝ ghǝragh waa tagda taakiya ǝn tlǝkǝsa. Yaakwi kwakyarvad kwan nǝ uuda, dlaɓa sanhi kwakyarvad kwan sa ma duniya, aɗaba ǝn ɓaga kǝ shiida jiijiira. Dlaɓa baɗǝm daddakwa dǝga jiira, cinngaan kǝ ǝlbǝgara.”
\p 
\v 38 Kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg kǝ Bilatus amaa, “Au jiiri?”
\p Ndavǝgharu ba nǝ iin kwan kǝ ndavǝga, kaa gwiya sagal kǝ iin sa vak Yahudaha amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Viyanǝt bi nai dǝ haip biya.
\v 39 Amma mǝnng nǝ dǝga daadijaharuwa, akwama ɓagaaɓag sarta hwaɗaga haarakǝsa dzǝva hǝnnyaha, ǝn ɓǝlkursɓǝlg kǝ uud pall ma guda bǝrfǝnga. Am naagaan ǝn ɓǝlkurnǝs kǝ tlǝkǝsa Yahudaha?”
\p 
\v 40 Kaa gwiya ngugǝg kǝ iitǝra, ar ɗiyaru kǝ cauw ar taakiya, “Maaya kwan biya, Barabbas wa kǝm naag nǝmnda.” (Barabbas ndza dadda zaaɗuula.)
\c 19
\s1 Ghudavardaghudǝg shariya hǝrtǝg kǝ Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Kaa vǝldavǝlǝg Bilatus kǝ Yesu kiyava kalǝga.
\v 2 Kaa faɗgafaɗǝg tlaujah kǝ dzakwa tlǝkǝs kwa ɓagava dǝ dǝva taka ar tsǝgwardǝm maghǝr kǝ Yesu, tǝhalakwah ar tsǝgwardǝm kǝ sǝɗav kyanng hulfa dǝga tlǝkǝssaha.
\v 3 Ar gwayashig sa vakaana, ar ɓalgar mahupennga, ar taakiya, “Kǝm ma barkagha, tlǝkǝsa Yahudaha!”
\p 
\v 4 Kaa gwiya sagal kǝ Bilatusa, amaa kǝ Yahudahi faɗǝga vakwahiina, “Waiyam ciya ǝn lanngkurlanng kǝ Yesu sagala, kwakyarvad ǝn naagaan am sǝra taakiya viyanǝti dǝ haip biya.”
\v 5 Kaa sagal kǝ Yesu dǝ dzakwa tlǝkǝs dzakwa tak ma ghǝraan dlaɓa dǝ sǝɗav kyannga. Aiyam Bilatus taa kǝ iitǝra, “Waiyam nǝ uuda nǝ iina.”
\p 
\v 6 Nǝghǝghaara ba maalah ma zhiilakǝsuufah ard lii uufakyawa Vǝgya Daadamazhigǝl kǝ Yesu, kaa ɗiya cau kǝ iitǝr ar taakiya, “Aa hǝrtǝvǝthǝrtǝga! Aa hǝrtǝvǝthǝrtǝga!”
\p Am Bilatus taa kǝ iitǝra, “Damdagal am hǝrtǝt bad ghǝraruwa, aɗaba tlankǝna bi nai kǝ iin dǝ haip biya.”
\p 
\v 7 Kaa ngugarangug kǝ Yahudah taakiya, “Kǝm da adzahadzaha, dlaɓa tǝdvad adzahadzahamnda, barari tsǝvana, aɗaba nadalnǝg kǝ ghǝraan kǝ Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla.”
\p 
\v 8 Cinngha ba Bilatus kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa gwiya gǝdzǝg kǝ iina.
\v 9 Kaa gwiya daas kǝ iin damma huɗa vǝgyaana, ndavaru kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Agha sagal vakwari?” Amma lawalǝg Yesu kǝ ngugarngugga.
\v 10 Aiyam Bilatus taa kǝ iina, “Lǝghwalǝg kǝ taa ghai dǝ kaiya? Agha sǝrǝgai taakiya ǝn dǝ ndzǝɗa ɓǝlǝkǝsɓǝlǝga ard ndzǝɗa hǝrtǝkǝthǝrtǝg biya?”
\p 
\v 11 Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Agha maay dǝ ndzǝɗ tǝghǝr kǝskai akwama vǝllakaki nǝ uud sii ma ghǝrazhigǝl biya. Kwakyarvad kwaha daddakwa fakwadǝm ma dǝvvagha jakujig dǝ haipa.”
\p 
\v 12 Tǝhala kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa ba gata ɗuula ɓǝlgaars Yesu nǝ Bilatus, amma Yahudaha ar za ba vukw dǝ ɗiya cau ar taakiya, “Akwama ɓǝlgharǝsɓǝlǝg kǝ kwan kǝ uuda agha madlai tsaghwa Kaisar biya. Baɗǝm daddakwa nadalnǝg kǝ ghǝraan kǝ tlǝkǝsa, ciigar hǝnkal kǝ Kaisara.”
\p 
\v 13 Cinngha ba Bilatus kǝ dǝgiti tagar nǝ iitǝra, kaa sagal kǝ iin dǝ Yesu, kaa cǝhurgacǝhurǝg Bilatus tǝ avǝda shari tǝ akur hahaana. Dǝ ghaiya Yahudaha ɗahav dǝ Gabbata.
\v 14 Daghuvala kwahina, ndza faciya ɓadlava hwaɗaga haarakǝsa dzava hǝnnyaha, tamaha faci tǝghǝra.
\p Aiyam Bilatus taa kǝ Yahudaha, “Waiyam Tlǝkǝsaruwa!”
\p 
\v 15 Kaa ɗiya cau kǝ Yahudaha ar taakiya, “Aa tsǝvatsǝɡa! Aa tsǝvatsǝga! Aa hǝrtǝvǝthǝrtǝga!”
\p Kaa ndavtǝrundavǝg kǝ Bilatus amaa, “Am naagaan ǝn hǝrtǝt kǝ Tlǝkǝsaruwa?”
\p Kaa ngugangug kǝ maalah zhiilakǝsuufaha, am nǝ iitǝra “Kǝm maay dǝ kwatlǝrǝn kǝ tlǝkǝs biya, ba Kaisara.”
\p 
\v 16 Tǝhala kwaha, kaa vǝldavǝlǝg Bilatus kǝ Yesu kiyava hǝrtǝga.
\s1 Hǝrtavǝthǝrtǝg Yesu
\p Kaa daddǝg kǝ tlaujah kǝ Yesu.
\v 17 Tǝghǝrdǝga sagal Yesu ma kǝsiin kǝsa tlaɓa hǝrtǝgaan ba dǝ ghǝraan da vakavakǝn kwa ɗahav dǝ kuwa ghǝra. (Dǝ ghaiya Yahudaha ɗahav dǝ Golgota nǝ wanǝn kǝ vakavaka.
\v 18 Hǝrtavǝt vaakwahiin Yesu, ǝmtaɗ dǝ uudah buwa, pal tǝ dǝvva kafaana, pal dlaɓa tǝ dǝvva ghyaɓaana, iin ma taataka.
\v 19 Vindavindǝg Bilatus kǝ ǝlbǝga, kwa favva tǝ tlaɓa hǝrtǝga. Dǝgiti vindavana, iin taakiya “YESU ZHIILA NAZARET, TLƏKƏSA YAHUDAHA.”
\v 20 Karantarakarantǝg Yahudah ba ɗyak kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga aɗaba vakavakǝn hǝrtavǝt dǝ Yesu na, ba hyaf dǝ kǝs ɗyaka. Kwanǝn kǝ vindǝg dlaɓa vindava ma ghaiya Yahudaha, ard ghaiy Romaha, ard Heleniyaha.
\v 21 Aiyam maalah ma zhiilakǝsuufaha Yahudah taa kǝ Bilatusa, “Vind bi taaki, ‘Tlǝkǝsa Yahudah,’ biya, vindavindǝg taakiya, ‘Am nǝ uudanǝnna, ǝn Tlǝkǝsa Yahudaha.’ ”
\v 22 Kaa ngutǝranngug Bilatus taakiya, “Dǝgiti naa vinndǝga naiya, ndzandzǝga.”
\p 
\v 23 Hǝrtarǝt ba tlaujah kǝ Yesu, ar hutsu kǝ sǝɗavahaana, ar tagwnan hutsǝg uufaɗa, aanji kwar kǝ tlauja kǝsuukǝsǝg kǝ hutsǝg palla. Ar kǝsuu baz sǝɗavaani tlaɗ kwama huɗmahuɗa, kwa havǝt dǝ hǝgga ciigǝt ma ghǝr ba dǝtl da tǝ haaya.
\v 24 Aiyam nǝ iitǝr kǝ ghǝrahaatǝra, “Tahǝyamna bi kǝ sǝɗavǝn biya, tsǝyamtsǝg kǝ tsats tǝghǝra, kiyam vazǝgaan kǝ dadakwa da zǝgaana.” Dzǝghardzǝg wannǝn kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ dǝgiti vindava ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝla taakiya,
\b
\q1 “Tagwarutagw kǝ sǝɗavahar ma taatakaatǝra,
\q2 ar tsak kǝ tsats tǝghǝr kǝ sǝɗavahara.”
\b
\m Dǝgiti ɓagara tlaujah waha.
\p 
\v 25 Lii ghacara tǝvǝgh kǝ tlaɓahǝrta Yesu, iitǝr naz Babbaana, batlǝrɗaana, ard Maryam uusa Kilobas, ard Maryamu Magadala.
\v 26 Nǝghǝgha ba Yesu kǝ babbaana ard mbǝrzǝn kwa waig nǝ iin ghacǝga ba hyafa, aiyama taa kǝ babbaana, “Uusǝna, wan zǝragha!”
\p 
\v 27 Aiyama kǝ mbǝrzǝn tǝ hala kwaha, “Nalnǝg nǝ uusǝn kǝ baabagha!” Ciigǝt ma kwahiin kǝ sarta, kaa lanngaan kǝ mbǝrzǝn kǝ babba Yesu da vǝgyaana.
\s1 Əmtsǝga Yesu
\p 
\v 28 Sǝrghasǝrǝg Yesu taakiya, ma kwahiin kǝ sarta ghyǝnnghanaghyǝnng kǝ ɓa dǝgitah baɗǝmma, kwakyarvad righǝvant nǝ dǝgiti vindava ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝla, aiyama, “Njakwanjiig nǝ andǝlla.”
\p 
\v 29 Vakwahiin ndza mǝng nǝ ɗagw righarighaan dǝ yuwa inabi kwarekrekka fǝgana. Kaa rǝmnarǝmng kǝ iitǝr kǝ abarabar ma yuwa inabi kwarekrekka, ar fǝt tǝ zadda izob ar kapanta ar farǝt tǝ ghai kǝ Yesu.
\v 30 Dlǝghaa ba Yesu kǝ yuwǝn kwarekerek na, amaa, “Ghyǝnngaghyǝnnga!” Tǝhala kwaha tsǝdi kǝ ghǝraana, vǝlda kǝ shifǝgaana.
\s1 Ghwavaghug Yesu dǝ guupa
\p 
\v 31 Ndza daghuvala ɓadlav tsauwa, dlaɓa dlakadurana faciya ngiiga kwa shah dǝ kyalma faciya ngiiga. Aɗaba ar naay tlǝvuukwa Yahudah kǝ ɗuwa tluwa vǝghaha uudah tǝ tlaɓa hǝrtǝg daghuvala faciya ngiig biya, kaa ghalla Bilatus kǝ Yahudaha maa kalǝvana shigahaatǝra, dlaɓa maa sǝvdi tluwa vǝghahaatǝr tǝ tlaɓa hǝrtǝga.
\v 32 Kaa sagau kǝ tlaujah ar kalna kǝ shigaha uuda zunngw kwa hǝrtavǝt ǝmtaɗ dǝ Yesu, ard shigaha daddakwa pallǝna.
\v 33 Amma sarǝv ba nǝ iitǝr da vak Yesu, kalarna bi kǝ shǝgaan biya aɗaba tlarara ǝmtsaaǝmǝtsǝga.
\v 34 Kaa ghwugaan kǝ pal ma tlaujah kǝ Yesu dǝ guup ma dlǝmbǝla, kaa sagal kǝ avǝz ard yu ba watswatsa.
\v 35 Daddakwa nǝghǝghanǝghǝga kǝ dǝgitahi dzǝghaardzǝg wa vǝlada shiida, shiidi vǝlada nǝ iinaa ba jiira. Ba Iin dǝ ghǝraan ndakwi sǝrǝgasǝrǝg taakiya jiir wa tag nǝ iina, vǝlada kwakyarvad am fǝdghǝrǝta.
\v 36 Dzǝghaar kwakyarvad rǝghǝvant nǝ dǝgitahi vindava ma Kakkaɗa Dadamazhǝgǝla, “Maay aanji pal ma tlatlaan wa da kǝlav biya.”
\v 37 Band kwa vindava vakavaki tlǝrǝn ma Kakkaɗa Dadamazhigǝl taakiya, “Ar da vazǝgaan kǝ daddakwa ghwara nǝ iitǝra.”
\s1 Hǝɗɗa Yesu
\p 
\v 38 Tǝhala kwaha, am nǝ Isuvu zhiil Arimatiya mbǝrza Yesu, amma shǝɓashǝɓan kwakyarvad gǝdza tlǝvuukwaha Yahudaha, kaa ghala Bilatus maa vǝlar kǝ tluwa vǝgha Yesu. Haigharanthaig Bilatusa, kaa dagal kǝ iin kǝssant kǝ tluwa vǝgha Yesu.
\v 39 Nikodimus kwa tapghana sa vak Yesu kavǝɗa, daral ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ Isuvu, sadǝvsǝg kǝ tǝrshana mur ard alos\f + \fr 19:39 \fk mur ard alos\ft Kwanahaan kadlannga tǝrshan bǝtbǝta kwa kutav tǝ vǝgha uud ǝmtsaaǝmtsana.\f* uushauushana, tamaha kilo kulhǝkǝrɗa.
\v 40 Kaa kǝsǝgantkǝsǝg kǝ uudahaan buwǝn kǝ tluwa vǝgha Yesu ar ngwaɗnan ma kǝlǝpakan ard kadlannga tǝrshǝn bǝtbǝta kwakyarvad dǝga daadijatǝr kǝ Yahudah akwa mar hǝɗa uuda.
\v 41 Vakavakǝn hǝrtavǝt nǝ iinna, ndza mǝnng ɗyaghaara guuha, ma ɗyaghara guuhiina dlaɓa ndza mǝng nǝ daalla gǝtl kwa tapavnai hǝɗa uud ma vakaiy biya.
\v 42 Ndza daghuvala faciya ɓadlava Yahudah tsauwa, dlaɓa ba hyaf gǝtl dǝ iitǝra, ar fǝdǝm kǝ tluwa vǝgha Yesu ma vakaiya.
\c 20
\s1 Ciiga Yesu ma gǝtla
\p 
\v 1 Dlakadur ba wur daghuvala hǝnnga zunngw ma maaka, lakwti cag kǝsa, kaa ba dagal kǝ Maryamu magadala damma gǝtlaha, nǝghǝgha ba tlǝgavarwatlǝg nǝ akur tǝ ghaiya gǝtla Yesu.
\p 
\v 2 Kaa ǝmndǝra saas kǝ iin da vak Siman Bitrus ard mbǝrz kwa waig Yesu, amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Kǝsavdakǝsǝg Yazhigǝl sagal ma gǝtla, kǝm sǝrga bi kǝ vakavaki araa fǝga nǝ iitǝr biya.”
\v 3 Kaa sagal kǝ Siman Bitrus ard mbǝrzǝn ar viyǝt kǝ ɗuula dagal damma gǝtla.
\v 4 Kaa ǝmndǝra dagal kǝ iitǝr ba bǝrkuɗaatǝra, jighaarajig mbǝzǝn pallǝn kǝ Siman Bitrus dǝ ǝmndrǝga, dlaɓa dagha nǝ iin tǝghǝr kǝ Siman Bitrus da vaka gǝtla.
\v 5 Ngǝghǝra kǝ iin vazanan damma vakaiya, kaa nǝghǝghgaanǝghǝg kǝ iin kǝ kǝlpakan ɓǝlgana, amma dagha bi damma gǝtliin biya.
\v 6 Kaa sagau kǝ Siman Bitrus tǝ halaana, kaa ba daas kǝ iin damma gǝtla, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iin kǝ kǝlpakan ɗiigana.
\v 7 Nǝghǝghanǝghǝg dlaɓ kǝ sǝɗavǝn kwa faɗavan dǝ ghǝra Yesu ɗiigaan vakavaki tlǝrǝn shah dǝ kǝlpakana.
\v 8 Kaa dǝgaadǝg baz mbǝrzǝn kwa tsugwa ba zunngw tǝghǝr Siman Bitrus damma vakaiya. Nǝghǝgha ba nǝ iina, kaa fǝdǝghǝrǝtfǝga.
\v 9 (Gwaastǝn nǝgharaaka bi kǝ dǝgiti vindava ma kakkaɗa Daadamazhigǝl kwa taakiya, barari da ciig Yesu dǝ shifǝga.)
\v 10 Kaa gwiya daas kǝ mbǝrzahaan da vaka ndzǝganaatǝra.
\s1 Tsugwaatsugw Yesu vak Maryamu Magadala
\p 
\v 11 Ghacaghacǝg Maryam tǝ ghaiya gǝtl gyǝmala, tuuga. Ba tuug nǝ iina, kaa ngǝghǝrangǝg zhara damma gǝtla,
\v 12 Kaa nǝghǝghgaanǝghǝg kǝ inn kǝ zarha ɓǝlg buw ar ma sǝɗav maɗǝkw ar cǝhurgan vakavaki ndza dǝ tluwa vǝgha Yesu. Zǝrɓǝlǝg palla cǝhurga vaka ghǝra, kwah dlaɓ cǝhurga vaka shǝgahaana.
\v 13 Kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg kǝ Zǝrha ɓǝlgah taakiya, “Uusǝna, au wagha tuug nǝngi?” Aiyama taa kǝ iitra, “Kǝsavuukǝssǝg Yaazhigǝlara, ǝn sǝrǝgai kǝ vakavaki aa fǝvva dǝ iin biya.”
\v 14 Tagada ba nǝ iin kǝ ǝlbǝgna, kaa gwivǝtgwiga nǝghǝgha ba Yesu ghacǝgana, amma nǝghǝghaaka bi taakiya iin biya.
\v 15 Kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Uusǝna, aaujilǝbǝg kǝskǝgh tuugi? War wagha gatǝg nǝnngi?” Ma tlǝg nǝ iin daddakwa ɓa tlǝr ma ɗyaghaara guhiina, aiyama taa kǝ iina, “Dadda hǝnnyaha, akwama kǝgh wagha kǝsǝgantkǝsǝga, tagwatag kǝ vakavaki agha fǝga nǝnnga, kwakyarvad ǝn kǝsanta.”
\v 16 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Maryama!” Kaa gwivǝt kǝ iin da vak Yesu amaa kǝ iin dǝ ghaiya Yahudaha, “Rabboni!” Dǝgiti tuuk vakaiya nǝ iina, dadda tsaga dǝgita.
\v 17 Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Hǝkykwa biya, aɗaba danǝti davak Daad ndan biya. Amma dǝg davak zaraabahar tagtǝrtag taakiya, ǝn dagat da vak Daadara, dlaɓa Daadaruwa, Daadamazhigǝlara, dlaɓa Daadamazhigǝlaruwa.”
\v 18 Kaa dagal kǝ Maryam Magadala da tagtǝr kǝ mbǝrzaha, amaa “Nǝghananǝghǝg kǝ Yaazhigǝla.” Tagtǝr dlaɓ kǝ dǝgiti taghar Yesu.
\s1 Tsugwatsugw Yesu vak mbǝrzahaana
\p 
\v 19 Ɓǝlaa ba hwaas daghuvala hǝnnga zǝngw ma maaka, kaa dzahvǝtdzahǝg kǝ mbǝrzaha vak palla, dlaɓa ar ngahant kǝ ghaiya gudah mbakyarvad tlǝvuukwa Yahudaha. Kaa tsugwatsugw kǝ Yesu ma taatakaatǝr amaa, “Gabǝr tǝghǝr kǝskurama.”
\v 20 Tǝhala kwa tagada nǝ iin kǝ kwanǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga, kaa martǝrdamarǝg kǝ iin kǝ dǝvvahaan ard dlǝmbǝlaana. Kaa dlaiga kǝ mbǝrzah nǝghǝghara ba nǝ iitǝr kǝ Yazhigǝla.
\v 21 Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iitǝr gwiya daala, “Gabǝr tǝghǝr kǝskurama! Bandkwa ɓǝlakut Daada, kai ndakwi ǝn ɓǝlkur bandkwaha.”
\v 22 Tagada ba nǝ iin kwaha, kaa fǝrtǝrdǝm kǝ shifǝgaana, amaa taa kǝ iitǝra, “Dlǝghamdlǝghǝg kǝ Shǝɗkwa Daadamazhigǝla.
\v 23 Baɗǝm dadda kwam ɓǝshgarnaa nǝ uuram kǝ haipahaana, ɓǝshavarnaɓǝshiga, dlaɓa baɗǝm dadda kwa ɓǝshamarnaa biya, ɓǝshvarnaa biya.”
\s1 Tsugwatsugw Yesu vak Tuma
\p 
\v 24 Tuma kwa ɗahav dǝ ghwalaha, pall ma mbǝrzah kǝlaawa tar buwa, ndza, maay ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ iitǝr ma sartǝn sagha Yesu biya.
\v 25 Am kyalǝma mbǝrzahan taa kǝ iina, “Nǝghamdanǝghǝg kǝ Yaazhigǝla!” Aiyam Tum taa kǝ iitǝra, “Akwama nǝghana bi kǝ ɗuula amsams ma dǝvvahaan biya, ǝn fǝm kǝ zǝra dǝvvar ma ɗuula amsams biya, dlaɓa ǝn fǝm kǝ dǝvvar ma dlǝmbǝlaan vaka ghuga guup biya, ǝn fǝdǝghǝrǝt biya.”
\v 26 Tǝhala maaka, kaa gwiya dzahvǝtdzahǝg kǝ mbǝrzaha vak palla ma hǝnnyahiina, dlaɓa Tuma ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ iitǝra. Ghaiya gudah ndakwi ngahangahana, kaa tsugwatsugw Yesu ma taatakaatǝr amaa, “Gabǝr tǝghǝr kǝskurama.”
\v 27 Tǝhala kwah amaa taa kǝ Tuma, “Faffǝg kǝ zǝra dǝvvagh vaakwana, vazǝg kǝ dǝvvahara. Vǝlǝg kǝ dǝvvagh faffǝg damma dlǝmbǝlara. Ɓag bi kǝ ndaundau biya, fǝdǝghǝrǝtfǝga.”
\v 28 Am Tum taa kǝ iina, “Yaazhigǝlara ard Daadamazhigǝlara!”
\v 29 Kaa tagartag Yesu taakiya, “Aɗaba aghaa nǝghǝkwadnǝghǝg iin wagha fǝghǝdǝghǝrǝt nǝnnga. Bark kǝ lii nǝgharkwa biya dlaɓa fardǝghǝrǝtfǝga.”
\s1 Dǝgiti tuuk vakai kakkaɗa
\p 
\v 30 Ɓagaaɓag Yesu kǝ dǝga sǝrgah ba ɗyak ma gyiyaha mbǝrzahaana, kwa viindava bi ma kwanǝn kǝ kakkaɗ biya.
\v 31 Vindavavindǝg wanahaan kwakyarvad am fǝdǝghǝrǝt taakiya Yesu iin Kǝristi, Zǝra Daadamazhigǝla. Dlaɓa tǝdvad fadghǝr ma ɗagaana am tlǝkǝna kǝ shiifǝga.
\c 21
\s1 Tsǝgwatsǝgw Yesu vak Mbǝrzahaan uuɗiffa
\p 
\v 1 Tǝhala kwaha kaa gwiya tsǝgwatsǝgw kǝ Yesu vak mbǝrzahaan tǝ ghaiya dǝlva Tibariya. Dlaɓa wan ɗuuli marrada nǝ iin kǝ ghǝrana.
\v 2 Siman Bitrus, ard Tum kwa ɗahav dǝ Ghwallaha, ard Nataniyel kwama Kana ma Galili, ard dǝ zarha Zabadi, ard kyalǝma mbǝrzah buwa baɗǝmma ar ǝmtaɗa.
\v 3 Am Bitrusa, “Ən dagal da vaiya kilfa.” Aiyam kyǝlǝma mbǝrzaha, “Kǝmnd ndakwani kǝm dagal ǝmǝtaɗ dǝ kǝgha.” Kaa sagal kǝ iitǝr ar dǝm damma pɛrayuwa, kaa dagal kǝ iitǝra. Amma ma huɗa kwahiin kǝ avǝɗa, viyarǝti aanji ndau biya.
\v 4 Dlakadur ba wurra, ghacǝgan Yesu tǝ ghaiya dǝlva, amma nǝghǝgharaaka bi mbǝrzahaan taakiya Yesu biya.
\v 5 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Daala zarha, tlamkǝnatlǝg kǝ kilfa?” Kaa ngugwanguw kǝ iitǝr taakiya “Maaya.”
\v 6 Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Ɓǝlamɓǝlǝg kǝ amshi damma dǝvvaa kaffa pɛrayuwa, am da tlǝkǝnatlǝga.” Kaa ɓǝlgaan kǝ iitǝr bandkwa tagatǝr Yesu, ar vaiyit kǝ kilf ba ɗyaka, pelatǝrvaapelǝg baz tǝɗa amshi damma pɛrayuwa.
\v 7 Am mbǝrzǝn waig Yesuwǝn taa kǝ Bitrusa, “Abi Yaazhigǝla!” Cinngha ba Siman Bitrus taakiya Yaazhigǝla, kǝsant kǝ sǝɗavan tsǝgwǝvva, aɗaba ndza ba dǝ kusǝgha. Tǝhalakwa, kaa dzǝva daay kǝ iin damma yuwa.
\v 8 Kaa ba sagau kyalǝma mbǝrzah da tǝ ghaiya dǝlǝv ma pɛrayuwa, ar tǝɗa amshiya vaiya kilf righarighaan dǝ kilfa. Aɗaba ndzar maay bǝtky dǝ ghaiya dǝlviin biya, tamaha shig dǝrǝmǝk hǝkǝrɗa.
\v 9 Ba dǝ sagalaatǝr wah sa tǝ ghaiya gardza, nǝghara ba ghuvǝra kaar dǝ kilf ɓǝlga tǝ vakai ard bruudiya.
\v 10 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Anaagham kǝ kyalǝma kilf ma kwanahaan amaa vaigǝt nǝ uuram ndakwanǝnna.”
\v 11 Kaa ba daas kǝ Siman Bitrus damma pɛrayuwa, tǝɗda kǝ amshiya vaiya kilf da tǝ ghaiya gardza. Amshiya vaiya kilfǝn dlaɓa righarighaan dǝ maandala kilf dǝrmǝk dǝ kuldlǝɓ tar hǝkǝrɗa. Bakǝvakwaha, ndzǝgana ɗyakǝra kilfǝna, tǝhghana bi kǝ amshiya biya.
\v 12 Am Yesu taa kǝ iitǝra, “Asamasǝg naa ziyamzǝg kǝ kaffa dlakaduura.” Maay wa shughana gyi ma mbǝrzahaan kǝ ndavǝgarundavǝg taakiya ma war nǝ iin biya, aɗaba ar sǝrgasǝrǝg taakiya Yaazhigǝla.
\v 13 Kaa sagau kǝ Yesu kǝssant kǝ bruudiyin vǝlǝtǝra, ɓagaa band kwah dlaɓ dǝ kilfa.
\v 14 Dǝga hǝkǝrɗ wan kǝ Yesu tsugwatsug vak mbǝrzahaan tǝhala ciigaan ma gǝtlaha.
\s1 Taghǝghartag Yesu kǝ Bitrus taaki gǝlǝg kǝ tuughahara
\p 
\v 15 Ghyǝnngara ba nǝ iitǝr za kaffa, kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg Yesu kǝ Siman Bitrus taakiya, “Siman zǝra Yuhwanna, agha waikwawaig juujig kǝ kwannahaana?” Kaa ngwarangug kǝ Bitrus amaa, “Aana, Yaazhigǝla, agha sǝrǝgasǝrǝg taakiya ǝn wayakwaiga.” Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Gǝlǝg kǝ tuughahara.”
\v 16 Kaa gwiya ndavǝgarundavǝg Yesu kǝ dǝga buwa amaa, “Siman zǝra Yuhwanna, agha waikwawaiga?” Kaa ngugarangug kǝ iina, “Aana, Yaazhigǝla agha sǝrǝgasǝrǝg taakiya ǝn waiyakwaiga.” Am nǝ Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Faffǝg kǝ hyimi tuuk kǝ tuughahara.”
\v 17 Kaa gwiya ndavgarundavǝg Yesu kǝ dǝga hǝkǝrɗ amaa, “Siman zǝra Yuhwanna, agha waikwawaiga.” Kaa badza huɗvǝg kǝ Bitrusa, aɗaba kwa ndavgharu Yesu kǝ dǝga hǝkǝrɗǝn taakiya, “Agha waikwawaiga?” Iin dlaɓ ngugharangug taakiya, “Yaazhigǝla, agha sǝrgasǝrǝg kǝ dǝgitah ba ɗǝmma, agha sǝrgasǝrǝg taakiya ǝn waiyakwaiga.” Am Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Gǝlǝg kǝ tuughahara.
\v 18 Bak jiijiira, ǝn tagaktaga, ma sartǝn agha daalla zǝra agha fǝgaan kǝ sǝɗɗav bad ghǝragha agha dagal da vakavaki agha naaga nǝnnga, amma ma nǝghalnǝg kǝ malaha, agha talgaan kǝ dǝvvagh uudi tlǝrǝn wa fak sǝɗava, dǝkada da vakavaki agha naay kǝ dagal biya.”
\v 19 Tagadatag Yesu kwannǝn kǝ ǝlbǝga kwakyarvad marvǝda hulfa ǝmǝtsǝgi da ǝmtsǝg Bitrus kwa da saa dǝ ndanngǝr kǝ Daadamazhigǝla. Tǝhala kwan kǝ ǝlbǝga, am Yesu taa kǝ Bitrus, “Gatǝkwagatǝga.”
\s1 Yesu ard mbǝrz kwa waig nǝ iina
\p 
\v 20 Kaa gwivǝtgwig kǝ Bitrus vaza da tǝ halla, kaa nǝghǝganǝghǝg kǝ iin kǝ mbǝrzǝn kwa waig Yesu gata iitǝr tǝ halla. Kwan kǝ mbǝrz wandza dǝngǝzhiga tǝ Yesu ma sarta za kaffa hwaɗaga haarakǝssa dzava hǝnnyaha. Iin wa ndavǝgharu kǝ Yesu taakiya, “Yaazhigǝla, war wa da vǝla kǝghi?.”
\v 21 Nǝghǝgha ba Bitrus kǝ iina, kaa ndavǝgarundavǝg kǝ iin kǝ Yesu amaa, “Yaazhigǝla, uudanǝn mi?”
\v 22 Aiyam Yesu taa kǝ iina, “Akwaman naagaan ndzan dǝ shiifǝga bamma gwiyanghǝragwig saaya, auw lambaghi? Gatǝkwagatǝg aska nǝnnga.”
\v 23 Aɗabad kwaha, kwannǝn kǝ ǝlbǝg kutalkutǝg ma yaa dadda gata Yesu taakiya, kwan kǝ mbǝrz da maay ǝmtsǝg biya. Amma tagada bi Yesu taakiya, da maay ǝmǝtsǝg biya, tagada ba taakiya, “Akwaman naagaan ndzan dǝ shiifǝg bamma gwiyanghǝragwig saaya, au lambaghi?”
\v 24 Kwan kǝ mbǝrz wa ɓaga shiid tǝghǝr kǝ kwanahaan kǝ dǝgitaha, iin dlaɓ wa vindavindǝga. Kǝm sǝrgasǝrǝg taakiya shiidaana ba jiijiira.
\v 25 Mǝng nǝ dǝgitah ba ɗyak kwa ɓaga Yesu, akwama taakiya aa vindavvindǝg baɗǝmma, man tlǝg naiya aanji duni dǝ ghǝraana ma kǝssgant bi kǝ kakkaɗahaan akwama viindav biya.
